	text = text.replace("Farkin\' hell. A man in battle with nothing on him is more naked than the day he\'d done been born!", "扯蛋。一个身无分文的人在战斗中会比他出生的那天更一丝不挂！");
	text = text.replace("I s\'pose the irony is that if we - and I mean anybody-we - come find ya dead in the fields, then we\'ll probably dress ya better for the grave than you dress yourself now.", "我觉得讽刺的是，如果我们－我是说任何人－我们－发现你死在田野里，我们会把你打扮的更体面然后下葬，绝对比你现在要体面。");
	text = text.replace("Which shan\'t be hard, seeing as how you\'ve dressed yourself none at all.", "这并不难，因为你以后不会再有衣服穿了。");
	text = text.replace("With a bit of a wave, you thank the traveler for his kind words before continuing your merry march.", "你挥了挥手，感谢旅行者的忠言，然后继续愉快的行程。");

//apprentice_learns_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/The apprentice (.*?) has apparently become a ward to (.*?)\. While the swordmaster is long in the tooth, he seems quite eager to help the young man become a better fighter\./, "学徒 $1 似乎已经成为 $2 的老人看护员。虽然这位剑术大师年事已高，但他似乎很想帮助这位年轻人成为一名更好的战士。");
	text = text.replace("The apprentice uses a real sword, the swordmaster but a wooden one.", "学徒用的是真剑，剑术大师用的是木剑。");
	text = text.replace("It is in this rather large difference of chosen weaponry that the swordmaster displays the usefulness of positioning, finding openings, and getting out of the way of danger.", "剑术大师正是在这种武器的巨大差距下，展示如何有效地走位，发现弱点和避开危险。");
	text = text.replace("Even in his old age the man twirls and whirls, becoming impossible for the apprentice to hit.", "甚至在他年老的时候，这个人还在不停地闪转腾挪，使学徒根本打不动他。");
	text = text.replace("In one particularly brilliant trick, the swordmaster senses that he is about to be struck so he closes distance with the apprentice and steps on his foot.", "一个巧妙的假动作，剑术大师看起来要被击中了，因为他离学徒很近，几乎要踩到脚了。");
	text = text.replace("When the apprentice tilts back to give himself space, his foot does not go with him.", "当学徒向后倾斜以给自己空间时，他的脚步乱了。");
	text = text.replace("The sudden imbalance brings the trainee tumbling to the ground wherein he looks up to find a wooden sword prodding his neck.", "突然的拌蒜导致学员摔倒在地，他抬头发现一把木剑已经戳到了他的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("You find the man patting the dirt off himself pretty often, but he is at least getting up for more.", "你发现这小子拍拍自己身上的泥土，现在至少能站起来继续拍泥土了。");
	text = text.replace("Let\'s just say he is improving one splinter at a time.", "我们只能说他这次小有提升吧。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the unretired soldier has taking a liking to (.*?)\. You find the two practicing their craft whenever possible\./, "$1 这位未退役的士兵很欣赏 $2。你就会发现他们俩抽空就在练习他们的武艺。");
	text = text.replace("The old grunt believes in the value of the offensive, showing the apprentice how to turn a blade, axe, or mace in such a manner that it inflicts the most damage.", "这老战士熟知进攻的技巧，教学徒如何舞动刀刃，斧头或狼牙棒，使之造成最大的伤害。");
	text = text.replace("Unfortunately, they are using the company dining equipment to set up little dolls to beat up.", "不幸的是，他们继续使用战队的餐具作为练习的武器战斗。");
	text = text.replace("The young lad has certainly made a mess of those pots and pans in his continuous pursuit of being a better fighter.", "这个年轻的小伙子为了继续追求成为一个更好的战士，把那些锅碗瓢盆都弄得一塌糊涂。");
	
	text = text.replace(/It appears as though (.*?) the ol\' sellsword has a little bird following him around: young (.*?)\. Now in the company of mercenaries, the apprentice must want to learn from those with plenty of experience on the road earning blood money\./, "看起来好像 $1 这个老佣兵有一只跟着他的小鸟：年轻的 $2。现在，在这个雇佣兵组成的团队，学徒必须要向那些有丰富经验的人学习，赚取血汗钱。");
	text = text.replace("While they train, you notice that the sellsword puts most of his emphasis on exercising one\'s body.", "当他们训练的时候，你会注意到佣兵把大部分的重点放在体能训练上。");
	text = text.replace("Being faster than your opponent and outlasting him are just as important as putting a blade through his brainbox.", "比你的对手跑得快，比他更持久，就像把利刃刺穿他的大脑一样重要。");
	text = text.replace("The earnest lad seems increasingly sturdy, earning some sense of vigor you did not notice before.", "这个认真的小伙子似乎越来越健壮了，获得了一些前所未有的活力。");
	
	text = text.replace(/A couple of times now you\'ve caught (.*?) watching (.*?) from a distance\./, "有几次你发现 $1 在远处观望 $2。");
	text = text.replace("The young apprentice seems rather enraptured by the hedge knight\'s brute violence.", "年轻的学徒似乎被雇佣骑士的暴力美学折服了。");
	text = text.replace("After a few days, the knight relents, asking the lad to come and have a chat.", "过了几天，骑士改变了主意，让小伙子过来和他聊聊天。");
	text = text.replace("You know not what they say, but now you\'ve noticed they have been training together.", "你不知道他们在说什么，但现在你已经注意到他们一直在一起训练了。");
	text = text.replace("The hedge knight is not a kind trainer, either.", "雇佣骑士可不是一个慈祥的教官。");
	text = text.replace("He beats the boy frequently, toughening him up.", "他经常暴打那个男孩，使他坚强起来。");
	text = text.replace("At first, the apprentice flinches before every strike, but now you see that he is showing a little more resolve in the face of such towering adversity.", "起初，学徒在每次训练前都会退缩，但现在你可以看到，面对如此巨大的逆境，他表现出了更强的决心。");
	text = text.replace("The hedge knight is also showing the man how to kill fast and efficiently.", "雇佣骑士也在向他传授如何快速有效地杀人。");
	text = text.replace("Little mind is paid to defense in these talks you overhear, but who needs to defend themselves from a dead opponent?", "在你无意中听到的这些谈话中，很少有人提及防御方面的内容，但是谁需要防御一个被杀死的对手呢？");

//archery_stunt_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Something of a commotion draws you from your tent.", "一阵骚动把你从帐篷里吸引出来。");
	text = text.replace("Men are sitting on a few stumps or on the ground, eagerly watching something in the distance.", "人们坐在几根树桩上或地上，急切地望着远处的什么东西。");
	text = text.replace(/With squinting eyes, you spot (.*?) and (.*?) doing something odd\./, "眯着眼睛，你看到 $1 和 $2 正在做一些奇怪的事情。");
	text = text.replace("An apple rests on one man\'s head, while the other is walking away - a bow in hand.", "一个苹果放在一个人的头上，另一个人拿着弓走开了。");
	text = text.replace(/You ask (.*?) what is going on and he explains that the two men are going to try some sort of stunt or trick that involves shooting a piece of fruit off a man\'s head\./, "你问 $1 这是怎么回事，他解释说，这两个人要尝试一些高端或奇葩的玩法，包括从一个人的头上射下一只水果。");
	text = text.replace("Shocked, you exclaim that\'s not safe at all, to which the brother grins and explains that is the point.", "震惊之余，你惊呼这根本不安全，那个队员笑着解释说，这才是重点。");
	
	text = text.replace("You mull the situation over.", "你仔细考虑了一下形势。");
	text = text.replace("The brothers look to you, expecting a stoppage, but instead you take a seat amongst them.", "队员们望着你，以为你会制止，但你却坐在他们中间。");
	text = text.replace(/This spurs a brief cheer from the crowd which quickly quiets to hushed whispers as (.*?) and (.*?) get ready\./, "人群中爆发出一阵短暂的欢呼声，但很快就静了下来，低声耳语起来，因为 $1 和 $2 已经准备就绪了。");
	text = text.replace("Make sure to hit the apple!", "射中那个苹果十拿九稳！");
	text = text.replace("One brother shouts. Laughter ripples through the group.", "一个兄弟高声尖叫。笑声在人群中荡漾。");
	text = text.replace(/From that distance (.*?)\'s nose kinda looks like an apple to me\./, "从那么远的距离看，$1的鼻子都有点像苹果。");
	text = text.replace("More laughter, but it is ever nervous as the stunt is about to unfold.", "更多的笑声传来，但你终究有点紧张，因为表演即将开始。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) angles his shoulders to (.*?) and draws his bow, the silhouette of the man but a crescent of wood, string, and arm\./, "$1 把肩膀对着 $2 拉起他的弓，可以看到他的轮廓是一个由木头，绳子和手臂组成的月牙形。");
	text = text.replace(/You can\'t see (.*?)\'s face, but you assume his eyes are closed\./, "你看不到 $1的脸，但你认为他是闭着眼睛的。");
	text = text.replace("The shot is released.", "他射击了。");
	text = text.replace(/It zips. It disappears\. (.*?) rocks backward, clutching his face\./, "箭呼啸而过。然后就看不到了。$1 向后摇晃着，捂着脸。");
	text = text.replace("This isn\'t looking good.", "这看起来不太好。");
	text = text.replace(/The man screams\. The crowd oohs\. (.*?) slowly lowers his bow and looks at it as though it is at fault\./, "这个人的尖叫着。众人惊呼。$1 慢慢地放下他的弓，看着它，好像它有毛病似的。");
	text = text.replace(/Eventually, (.*?) is carried past you, a shaft of an arrow sticking out of his head\./, "最后，$1 从你身边经过，箭划伤了他的头。");
	text = text.replace("Another brother lingers behind, quietly eating an apple in the wake of the chaos.", "另一个兄弟在后面徘徊，在混乱中安静地吃着苹果。");
	
	text = text.replace("The men cheer as you give an affirming nod.", "当你点头表示肯定时，人们欢呼起来。");
	text = text.replace(/You take a seat amongst them as (.*?) and (.*?) get ready, the former nocking an arrow while the latter balances an apple atop his head\./, "你坐在他们中间，$1 和 $2 也做好了准备，前者整理弓箭，而后者把苹果在头上放平。");
	text = text.replace("When the fruit is good and steady, the archer draws back his bow, forming but a silhouette of man, wood, and string, a crescent of determination as he aims downfield.", "当水果摆稳后，弓箭手将弓向后拉开，当他瞄准时，形成了一个人，木头和绳子的构成的月牙形轮廓。");
	text = text.replace("The men are exchanging bets on whether or not he misses.", "这些人在打赌他是否会失手。");
	text = text.replace("You want to look away, but the spectacle truly is too much.", "你想把目光移开，但场面实在太壮观了。");
	text = text.replace("A great gasp follows the arrow\'s release, as though some ominous event long foretold had finally happened.", "随着箭的释放，队员们发出了一声惊叹声，仿佛某种长久以来预言的不祥之兆终于发生了。");
	text = text.replace("Men reel back in their seats, wincing and gritting their teeth.", "男人们蜷缩在座位上，皱着眉头，咬紧牙关。");
	text = text.replace(/The apple is shot off (.*?)\'s head, fruit and arrow spinning away\./, "苹果被从 $1的脑袋上打落了，果实和箭旋转着飞走了。");
	text = text.replace(/After a brief silence, the men erupt in cheers\. (.*?) takes a bow, while (.*?) slackens his draw and looks a bit relieved\./, "短暂的沉默之后，人们爆发出欢呼声。$1 鞠了一躬，而 $2 放松了下手腕，看起来长舒一口气。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You shake your head \'no\' as you walk out into the field and step between the two men\./, "你摇头说“不”，然后走到那两个人中间。");
	text = text.replace("If y\'all wanted to play tricks, you should\'ve joined a circus.", "如果你们都想耍把戏，应该去参加马戏团。");
	text = text.replace("Now get back to work before someone gets seriously hurt.", "在有人受重伤之前马上回去工作。");
	text = text.replace("A wave of disappointment washes over the men.", "一股失望的情绪席卷了这些人。");
	text = text.replace("A few even boo and give you a thumbs down or other, rowdier, gestures.", "有些人甚至会喝倒彩，少数人对你竖起大拇指，其他人也许做出了更粗暴的手势。");

//bad_curse_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) enters your tent with hat in hand\./, "$1 走进你的帐篷手里拿着帽子。");
	text = text.replace("The rim of it turns round and round in his fingers as though he were plucking feathers from it.", "帽子的边缘在他的手指间一圈又一圈地转着，好像他在拔帽子的羽毛。");
	text = text.replace("Even though you haven\'t said a word the man\'s head nods furiously and his eyes jet around as if looking for the words to say.", "即使你一个字也没说，那个男人还是狂怒地点头，他的眼睛扫视四周，好像在寻找要说的话。");
	text = text.replace("You put your quill pen down and ask what the issue is.", "你放下羽毛笔，问是什么问题。");
	text = text.replace("Licking his lips, he nods again and begins to explain his predicament.", "他舔了舔嘴唇，又点头，开始解释他的困境。");
	text = text.replace("The words come fast, but the general gist of it seems to be that a local witch has cursed the man to be incapable of some sexual export, as it were.", "他说得很快，是当地的一个女巫诅咒他，说他是性无能，大概意思就是这样。");
	text = text.replace(/You shake your head and ask what it is the witch wants and (.*?) says (.*?) crowns, lest the curse be on him for life\./, "你摇着头，问那女巫想要什么，$1 说 $2 克朗，以免自己一辈子都受到诅咒。");
	
	text = text.replace("Thumb and finger pinching your eyes shut, you wonder if maybe this wasn\'t the life for you.", "你用拇指和手指夹住自己的眼皮，你想知道这是不是你想要的的生活。");
	text = text.replace("Killing\'s easy, but this? Whatever.", "杀人很容易，但是这个事？无所谓吧。");
	text = text.replace("You throw your hands up and get out of your chair to retrieve a satchel of crowns.", "你把手举起来，从椅子上站起来，拿起一个装着克朗的袋子。");
	text = text.replace("The superstitious man totters up on the tips of his toes.", "那个迷信的人用脚尖蹒跚着站起来。");
	text = text.replace("Please count it out!", "请把它数出来！");
	text = text.replace("It mustn\'t be a crown short!", "一定不要少克朗了！");
	text = text.replace("You begrudgingly set the satchel on the table and begin counting.", "你不情愿地把袋子放在桌子上，开始数钱。");
	text = text.replace(/Once the appropriate number is had, you shuffle it into a purse and toss it to (.*?)\. He bows, thanking you and your mercy\./, "一旦有了合适的数目，你就把钱放到钱包里，然后把它扔给 $1。他鞠躬，感谢你和你的仁慈。");
	text = text.replace("You wave the man off to quickly get him out of your tent.", "你挥手示意他赶快离开你的帐篷。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You further muddy (.*?)\'s poor countenance with some bad news: you\'re not paying any witch anything\./, "你很快用一些坏消息把一脸可怜相的 $1 弄糊涂了：你没有给任何一个女巫任何东西。");
	text = text.replace("A few farcical words from some strange woman in the woods is no basis for an exchange of business.", "这是一些奇怪女人在森林里的玩笑，不能作为一场生意的依据。");
	text = text.replace("What you\'ve heard is a tramp\'s attempt to get at you, mercenary.", "你所听到的是一个婊子企图骗你呢，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("You cannot listen to such tripe, especially a tramp\'s tripe for a tramp\'s tripe is always in pursuit of one\'s coin.", "你不能听这种废话，尤其是一个婊子的废话，因为婊子的废话就是为了某个人的硬币。");
	text = text.replace(/None of these words help (.*?) for he quickly runs out of the tent, perhaps in pursuit of another mercenary who will give him a loan\./, "这些话对 $1 毫无用处，因为他很快就逃出了帐篷，也许是去找另一个可以借给他钱的雇佣兵。");
	
	text = text.replace(/Wondering if maybe (.*?) the monk could help, you go and fetch the holy man\./, "想到 $1 这个僧侣可能会帮上忙，你马上去找这个圣徒。");
	text = text.replace("He says he can indeed lend a hand for the old gods are always at war with the evils of witchcraft and other sorcery.", "他说他确实能帮上忙，因为古老的神明们总是与魔鬼和其他邪恶的巫师战斗。");
	text = text.replace(/Before he goes off on a long monologue about this old god or that one, you dip away and send him (.*?)\. For a few minutes, there is peace and quiet in your tent\./, "在他开始长篇大论这个古老神明或另一个之前，你溜走了把他留给 $1。有几分钟的实践，你的帐篷里宁静又祥和。");
	text = text.replace("But you know it can\'t last, for you are like a man beneath a rockslide, awaiting the tumbling stone with his name on it.", "但是你知道这不会持续太久，因为你就像一个人在岩石下呼吸，等待着刻着他名字的滚落的石头。");
	text = text.replace(/However, (.*?) doesn\'t return\./, "然而，$1 没有回来。");
	text = text.replace("After a few minutes more you realize he still hasn\'t made a disruptive entrance.", "又过了几分钟，你才意识到他还没有来捣乱。");
	text = text.replace("In fact, his absence altogether has you on edge, as though silence itself might be haranguing.", "事实上，他的缺席让你感到不安，仿佛沉默本身也可能是一种长篇大论。");
	text = text.replace("You leave the tent to find the monk and so-called cursed man deep in religious talks.", "你离开帐篷，发现僧侣和所谓的被诅咒的家伙正在进行宗教谈话。");
	text = text.replace("Smiling, you return to your tent.", "微笑着，你回到了你的帐篷。");
	text = text.replace("If there\'s one thing the holy men are best at, it\'s maintaining a sense of tranquility.", "如果有一件事是圣徒们所擅长的话，那就是营造一种宁静的氛围。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You snap your fingers, suddenly remembering (.*?), the so-called sorcerer\./, "你打着响指，突然想起 $1，这个所谓的巫师。");
	text = text.replace(/Wanting to not spend another minute being a part of this bizarre affair, you refer (.*?) to the sorcerer\./, "你不想再多花一分钟来参与这件荒谬的事情，就向巫师提及 $1。");
	text = text.replace(/He is quick to leave, but unfortunately returns a few minutes later, explaining that (.*?) has set him free from his curse\./, "他很快就离开了，但不幸的是几分钟后他又回来了，解释说 $1 已经帮他解除了诅咒。");
	text = text.replace("All I had to do was...", "我力所能及的做了…");
	text = text.replace("You hold your hand up, stopping the man\'s story right where it be.", "你举起手，让他的故事就此打住。");
	text = text.replace("He asks if you want to hear the rest of it and you give a firm no.", "他问你想不想听剩下的部分，你坚决地拒绝了。");

//bad_omen_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Cries whip through the party like the howls of the wind.", "哭喊声像狂风的怒号一样从人群中呼啸而过。");
	text = text.replace("There is not an enemy in sight so you\'ve no idea what is causing this.", "在视野里没有一个敌人，所以你不知道是什么发出的声音。");
	text = text.replace(/You walk the ranks to find (.*?) practically sobbing on the ground\./, "你走在队伍里，发现 $1 几乎趴在地上哭泣。");
	text = text.replace(/He is clutching his chest with one hand while the other points to the sky, the finger shaking in pointed fear\. (.*?) explains that the man saw a great blaze of fire cross by the stars\./, "他一只手抓着胸口，另一只手指向天空，手指因恐惧而颤抖。$1 解释说，这家伙看到了星星旁边燃起熊熊大火。");
	text = text.replace("Apparently this pathetic fool takes it for an omen and, of course, it isn\'t a good one.", "很明显，这个可怜的傻瓜把它当成了一个征兆，当然，这不是一个好兆头。");
	text = text.replace("Whatever it is, it isn\'t going to get you where you need to be so you order the men to march.", "不管它是什么，它不会把你带到你需要去的地方，所以你命令队员们继续行军。");
	text = text.replace("Shadows begin to fold in and on themselves in strange ways.", "他们的影子开始以奇怪的方式向外和向内呈现。");
	text = text.replace("You turn around to see the sun darkening, a great rim of black moving over it.", "你转过身去，看到太阳正在变黑，一个巨大的黑环在它上面移动。");
	text = text.replace(/Soon there is no sun at all\. (.*?) cries out that the end times are coming, but before his wailing can find a grip on the rest of your men, the great shade unveils the sun once more and there is light again as though nothing happened at all\./, "很快就没有太阳了。$1 哭着说世界末日就要到了，但是在他的号啕大哭能够传染你的其他队员之前，巨大的阴影再次遮蔽了太阳，光明又出现了，就好像什么都没有发生一样。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the pathetic fool to get to his feet.", "你叫那个可怜的傻瓜站起来。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve places to march and tears sure as hell won\'t get you there.", "你有行军的目的地，眼泪肯定屁用没有，不会带你到达目的地。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) is poking his sword into a warren when he suddenly cries out\./, "$1 他正在把剑刺入一个兔子洞时突然大哭起来。");
	text = text.replace("He leaps away from the rabbit hole and screams that there is a two headed bunny within.", "他从兔子洞里旁边跳起来，尖叫着说里面有一只双头兔。");
	text = text.replace("Apparently this is a bad omen of things to come.", "显然这是一个不好的兆头。");
	text = text.replace("All you can think is that two heads just means more meat for the stew.", "你所能想到的是，两个脑袋只是意味着有更多肉可以炖。");
	text = text.replace(/You pass beneath a tree whose branches are occupied by both a black cat and an albino crow\. (.*?) cries at the sight of it, saying that this is surely a sign of the end times\./, "你从一棵树下经过，那棵树的树枝上既有一只黑猫，也有一只白乌鸦。$1 一看到就开始哭，说这肯定是世界末日的前兆。");
	text = text.replace("Why yes, of course it is.", "为什么是，因为它就是。");
	text = text.replace("These things are never a sign of good things, right? Yeesh.", "这些都不是好事的征兆，对吧？是的。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a deer skull.", "你偶遇到一个鹿的头骨。");
	text = text.replace(/At first it means nothing to you, but (.*?) picks it up with earnest\./, "一开始你认为它毫无意义，但是 $1 一脸认真地捡起它。");
	text = text.replace("Muted dust pours out of the cavity as he turns it this way and that.", "当他反复转动鹿头骨的时候，无声的灰尘从里面倾泻而出。");
	text = text.replace("Hands trembling, he throws the head out of his hands.", "他双手颤抖着，把鹿头骨从手里扔出去。");
	text = text.replace("It clatters hollow against the ground, tumbling over onto where the horns should be.", "它在地面上砰砰作响，应该滚到了一个有棱角的地方。");
	text = text.replace("The scared man claims that a soothsayer once told him that he would come across a skull such as this.", "这个吓坏了的人说，曾经有一个预言家告诉他，他会遇到这样一个头骨。");
	text = text.replace("There are many skulls out here, you argue, because things have a tendency to die.", "这里有很多这样的头骨，你争执道，因为事物都会走向死亡。");
	text = text.replace("Your words do nothing for the man as he slowly, and nervously, shuffles back into the marching rank.", "你的话对他毫无用处，因为他慢慢地，紧张地，拖着脚步回到了行军的行列。");
	text = text.replace("Marching along, a few of the men take up a game of finding shapes in the clouds.", "在行军途中，几个人玩起了在云中寻找形状的游戏。");
	text = text.replace(/They banter back and forth about dogs and fat women and even of home, but the fun takes a wild turn when (.*?) sees one odd-shaped cloud that brings him to his knees\./, "他们来来回回地开着狗和胖女人的玩笑，甚至开着关于家的玩笑，但是当 $1 看到一朵奇形怪状的云后跪下来的时候，乐事就发生了疯狂的转变。");
	text = text.replace("He cries out that it is a bad omen, this cloud, and that doom will soon be upon the company.", "他哭着说，这团乌云是个不祥之兆，厄运很快就会降临到战队头上。");
	text = text.replace(/Thankfully, the fear does not grip the rest of the company who, instead of trembling, soon start bickering over whether or not the cloud is truly representative of (.*?)\'s impressive endowment\./, "值得庆幸的是，这种恐惧并没有影响到战队的其他成员，恰恰相反，他们很快开始争论这朵云是否真的代表 $1的惊人天赋。");

//ball_on_roof_event.nut
	text = text.replace("The company comes across a small boy who has climbed up a tree and out to the edge of a branch.", "战队遇到一个小男孩，他爬上了一棵树，爬到了树枝的边缘。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s reaching for a ball that\'s gotten stuck on the roof of his home.", "他伸手去拿一个卡在他家屋顶上的球。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s not a parent in sight to help him.", "没有一个家长能帮助他。");
	text = text.replace("When he sees you, he asks if you can help get the ball. Seems simple enough.", "当他看到你时，他问你是否可以帮忙拿球。似乎非常简单。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You send (.*?) to try and retrieve the ball\./, "你派 $1 去尝试取回球。");
	text = text.replace(/Using (.*?) as a stepstool, he launches himself onto the roof and gets the toy\./, "他把 $1 当做梯子，爬上屋顶，拿到了玩具。");
	text = text.replace("The boy is ecstatic and the smile on his face warms even the most cynical of your mercenaries.", "男孩欣喜若狂，他脸上的笑容甚至温暖了你们最愤世嫉俗的雇佣兵。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You send (.*?) to try and retrieve the ball\./, "你派 $1 去尝试取回球。");
	text = text.replace("He climbs the tree and jumps across a branch to land atop the roof.", "他爬上树，跳过树枝落在屋顶上。");
	text = text.replace("Mission complete, he tosses the ball to the kid.", "任务完成后，他把球扔给孩子。");
	text = text.replace("Unfortunately, the boy lets go of the tree branch to try and catch it.", "不幸的是，男孩放开了树枝，试图抓住球。");
	text = text.replace("He slips off the branch and falls a good fifteen feet to the earth.", "他从树枝上滑下来跌到地上，足足有十五英尺高。");
	text = text.replace("The wallop of his landing has the whole company cringing.", "他落地时的冲击力使整个战队都战战兢兢。");
	text = text.replace(/When you check on him he isn\'t moving and his back has taken a new shape\. (.*?) yells at the idiot still standing in shock on the roof\./, "当你检查他的时候，你发现他并没有动，而且他的背部已经变了形。$1 对那个仍然震惊地站在屋顶上的白痴大喊大叫。");
	text = text.replace("What the hell were you thinking? Holy shit, man!", "你到底怎么想的？你个白痴！");
	text = text.replace("The mercenary climbs down off the roof.", "这个雇佣兵从屋顶上爬了下来。");
	text = text.replace("He looks at the kid and then nervously looks around.", "他看了看孩子，然后紧张地环顾四周。");
	text = text.replace("Well he, uh, he\'s got the ball.", "好吧他，呃，他拿到了球。");
	text = text.replace("Let\'s get the hell out of here.", "让我们离开这个鬼地方吧。");
	text = text.replace("Our... our work here is done.", "我们的…在这儿的工作已经完成了。");
	text = text.replace("What a goatfuck of a situation.", "真他妈是个糟糕的情况。");
	text = text.replace("You and the company quickly leave the scene before the parents get back.", "你和你的战队在他家长回来之前迅速离开现场。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) clears his throat and steps forward\./, "$1 清了清嗓子，迈步向前。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll be your hero, kid.", "我会成为你的英雄，孩子。");
	text = text.replace("He opens his arms and the kid jumps down into them.", "他张开双臂，孩子跳了进去。");
	text = text.replace("The boy is set aside and the sellsword points a finger to the earth.", "那个男孩被安放在一边，佣兵用手指着地面。");
	text = text.replace("Stay down here.", "呆在这里。");
	text = text.replace("The surefooted mercenary easily clambers up the tree and jumps over to the roof.", "这个步伐沉稳的佣兵轻易地爬上树，跳到屋顶。");
	text = text.replace("He picks the ball up and spins it on a finger before he pirouettes off the eave like a tornado, landing right on his toes with rather feminine grace.", "他捡起球，用手指旋转，然后像龙卷风一样旋转着离开屋檐，用脚趾着地，像女人那样优雅。");
	text = text.replace("The boy claps excitedly and takes the toy and even the most cynical of men in the company are warmed by his happiness.", "孩兴奋地拍手拿走了玩具，连战队里最愤世嫉俗的人都被他的快乐所温暖。");

//bastard_assassin_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Under the cover of night, a man slips into your tent beneath the folds wafting just over the ground.", "在夜幕的掩护下，一个男人溜进了你的帐篷，而帐篷的帘子仅仅在地上飘了几下。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s masked with a black cloak and noble pauldrons.", "他披着一件黑斗篷，戴着高贵的宝龙面具。");
	text = text.replace("You arm yourself, but he holds a hand out.", "你自己武装自己，但他伸出手来。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t bother, sellsword, for I am not here for you.", "不必麻烦了，佣兵，因为我不是为你而来的。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s not good enough for you.", "那对你来说不够好。");
	text = text.replace("The second the man takes another step, you charge and plant him on your table and with your free arm put a dagger to his neck. He grins.", "那人再走一步，你就冲过去把他按在你的桌子上，用你那只空着的手把匕首刺向他的脖子。他笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("I already told you that I am not here for you.", "我已经告诉过你，我不是为你而来。");
	text = text.replace(/I am here for (.*?)\./, "我来是为了 $1。");
	text = text.replace("The bastard nobleman? You ask what the stranger wants with him.", "那个贵族私生子？你问这个陌生人想对他怎么样。");
	text = text.replace("Well, that depends, are you willing to talk?", "好吧，那要看情况，你愿意谈谈么？");
	
	text = text.replace("You lift the dagger from his neck.", "你把匕首从他脖子上拿下来。");
	text = text.replace("He straightens up on the table and glances at the map.", "他在桌子上直起身子，瞥了瞥地图。");
	text = text.replace(/I see the (.*?) has marched far and wide\. (.*?) chose wisely to fit himself into its ranks\./, "我看到 $1 已经声名远扬了。$2 明智地选择了适合自己的行列。");
	text = text.replace("When a drop of blood spatters the paper, he pauses to scratch a small nick you left on his neck, pursing his lips as though he had done it to himself in a morning shave.", "当一滴血溅到纸上时，他停下来，去抓你留在他脖子上的一个小伤口，噘起嘴唇，仿佛他是在早晨刮胡子时给自己留下的。");
	text = text.replace("Anyway, let\'s get down to business.", "不管怎样，我们谈谈生意吧。");
	text = text.replace(/My benefactors want (.*?) dead\./, "我的雇主要 $1 死。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing as how I\'ve been paid a large sum of coin, I am obligated to see this ambition to its end. Or... maybe not.", "既然我已经得到了一大堆硬币，我就有义务把这个野心坚持到底。或者…也许不。");
	text = text.replace("When he raises a playful eyebrow, you tell him to spill what he\'s thinking.", "当他挑起有趣的眉毛时，你告诉他说出他的想法。");
	text = text.replace("He stiltwalks a sexton across the map as he talks.", "他指着地图上我们的行军路线说道。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) has an army waiting for him if he so chooses\./, "$1 有一支军队等着他，如果他愿意。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s why the nobles want him dead, because he stands as a real and viable threat to the status quo and this he does not yet know.", "这就是为什么这些贵族们想要他死，因为他现在是一个真正的和可怕的威胁，而这一点他还不知道。");
	text = text.replace("I suppose he doesn\'t have to, either, but it\'d be a nice send off, no?", "我想他也不需要，但这将是一次愉快的送别，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("You get to see to it that his place in this world is justified and that he isn\'t some accident gliding through a world he believes to hate him.", "你要确保他在这个世界上的地位是正当的，他不是在一个他认为恨他的世界里偶然地飘过。");
	text = text.replace("But what about me, a grossly talented assassin with a perfect streak of kills, hm?", "但是我呢，一个非常有天赋的杀手，有着完美的杀人记录，嗯？");
	text = text.replace("What about me? Well, I don\'t want this life anymore.", "关于我的什么？好吧，我不想再过这种生活了。");
	text = text.replace("So here\'s my offer: I take his place.", "所以我的提议是：我来代替他。");
	text = text.replace("He goes home, I go with you.", "他走了，我跟你。");
	text = text.replace("He goes and conquers, my benefactors are nonethewiser and for all they know, I simply disappeared. Sounds good, no?", "他去征服别人，我的雇主并不比他聪明，他们只知道我消失了。听起来不错，不是吗？");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) deserves better\. Not that the (.*?) is beneath him, but he is a man who has spent his whole life seeing himself as an outsider, a blight upon his own family name, a threat to those he love merely because they carry a finer bloodline than he\./, "$1 理应得到更好的待遇。并不是 $2 对他不好，而是他一生都把自己看成一个局外人，是自己家族姓氏的污点，是他所爱的人的威胁，仅仅是他们的血统比他好。");
	text = text.replace("You agree to the assassin\'s demand and send for the bastard to enter your tent.", "你同意刺客的要求，让那个私生子进入你的帐篷。");
	text = text.replace("When he does, you quickly explain the situation.", "当他这样做的时候，你迅速地解释一下情况。");
	text = text.replace(/He asks for proof that an army is awaiting him and the hired killer quickly complies, producing a stamped scroll with a sigil and signature only the bastard could recognize\. (.*?) reads it carefully\./, "他要求出示证据，证明有一支军队在等着他，雇佣的刺客迅速答应了他的要求，拿出了一份盖有图章和签名的卷轴，只有那个私生子能认出来。$1 仔细地读了它。");
	text = text.replace("He lowers and looks to you.", "他低头看着你。");
	text = text.replace("And you are alright with this?", "你已经同意这事了？");
	text = text.replace("The destiny is mine to take, but you have my sword and allegiance for as long as you want.", "命运掌握在我自己手中，但只要你愿意，我的剑和忠诚将永远属于你。");
	text = text.replace("You clap the man on the shoulder and tell him to go forge his path.", "你拍拍他的肩膀，告诉他继续走他该走的路。");
	text = text.replace("The assassin tells him if he is to do it then he should do it quickly.", "刺客告诉他如果他要这么做，那么他应该尽快行动。");
	text = text.replace(/A little tearful, and not at all trying to hide it, (.*?) thanks you for at the very least believing in him even if only for the short time he was with the (.*?)\. And then he leaves\./, "流着泪，一点也想不掩饰的 $1 感谢你至少相信他，即使他只是在 $2 很短的时间。然后他离开了。");
	text = text.replace("Turning around, you find the assassin bowing.", "转过身，你发现刺客在鞠躬。");
	text = text.replace("And just like that, you have my sword, captain.", "就这样吧，我为你而战，队长。");
	text = text.replace("This will take some explaining to the other men, but they\'ll be sure to trust your intuition here.", "这需要向其他队员做一些解释，但是他们一定会相信你的直觉。");
	
	text = text.replace("Before you decide anything, you ask the assassin how much was offered to slay the bastard.", "在你决定任何事之前，你问刺客收了多少钱来杀死这个杂种。");
	text = text.replace("He weighs the numbers by tilting his head side to side.", "他左右摇晃着脑袋来计算数字。");
	text = text.replace("Well, it was... and then, deducting travel time, equipment costs, the time it took to find the damn sod, and the time it took scouting your encampment and figuring out whether you\'d be open to dialogue I\'d say... five-thousand crowns.", "好吧，是…然后，扣除旅行时间，装备成本，找到那块该死的草皮的时间，以及侦察你的营地，确定你是否愿意接受对话的时间…五千克朗。");
	text = text.replace("If you\'re thinking of matching that, it\'s going to be a bit more.", "如果你想更相称的话，那要再多一点。");
	text = text.replace("About one-thousand more, so that\'d be six-thousand crowns on your bill.", "再多给一千克朗吧，这样你的帐单上就有六千克朗了。");
	text = text.replace("You still up for that sort of \'discussion\', hm?", "你还在等着刚才那种“讨论”，哼？");
	
	text = text.replace(/While the (.*?) is doing well, it could be doing the best in the world and six-thousand crowns would still be a lot to ask for\./, "虽然 $1 运转的很好，它可能是世界上最好的，但六千克朗仍然是一个很高的要求。");
	text = text.replace("But... you agree. The assassin hears your words and sits there for a moment.", "但是…你同意了。刺客听到你的话，坐了一会儿。");
	text = text.replace("You agree? You\'ll pay six-thousand crowns, really?", "你同意了？你愿意出六千克朗，真的吗？");
	text = text.replace("You nod. He mulls the words over for another moment, a slight break in an otherwise stalwart presentation he has been putting on.", "你点头。他把这些话又想了一会儿，这是他进行一场持续而坚定的演讲前的一个小停顿。");
	text = text.replace("Gotta be honest, didn\'t think you\'d do that.", "老实说，我没想到你会那么做。");
	text = text.replace("But a deal is a deal, and I am not one to playfully waste words.", "但协议就是协议，我不是那种会开玩笑而浪费言语的人。");
	text = text.replace("He jets his hand out and you take it with a firm shake - just in case it is a ruse.", "他伸出手来，你坚定地握了一下－以防这是他的诡计。");
	text = text.replace("He bows gracefully, no doubt something he learned in the halls of the noblemen that had sent him here in the first place.", "他优雅地鞠躬，毫无疑问，这是他从最初派他来这里的贵族们那里学到的。");
	text = text.replace(/Captain of the (.*?), you have my blade!/, "$1 的队长，我为你而战！");
	text = text.replace("It\'ll take some explaining as to how a random man slipped into the company overnight, but the men have enough faith in your command that you could have recruited a sword-wielding goat and they would go along with it.", "这需要解释一下，一个路人是如何在一个夜晚溜进战队的，但这些队员对你的指挥有着足够的信心，就算你招募一只挥舞着剑的山羊，他们也会追随你。");
	
	text = text.replace("You refuse the assassin\'s offer. He nods.", "你拒绝了刺客的提议。他点头。");
	//text = text.replace("Alright.", "好的。");
	text = text.replace("The dagger comes quick, faster than you thought it would have.", "匕首来的很快，比你想象的要快。");
	text = text.replace("Your hand rises to deflect, but it\'s a moment too slow.", "你举起手来格挡，但速度太慢了。");
	text = text.replace("A knife\'s edge clips your cheek and draws blood.", "刀子的一边划过你的脸颊让你流血。");
	text = text.replace("By the time you draw your sword, the assassin has already leapt out of the tent.", "当你拔出剑的时候，刺客已经跳出了帐篷。");
	text = text.replace(/You hear a commotion outside and rush to it\. (.*?) the bastard is laying on the ground, a few other brothers beside him\. (.*?) comes over to ask if you\'re okay\./, "你听到外面一阵骚动，就冲过去。$1 这个私生子躺在地上。他身边还有几个队员。$2 过来问你有没有事。");
	text = text.replace("He says a man in black tried to kill the bastard.", "他说一个穿黑衣服的人想杀了私生子。");
	text = text.replace("I think we mortally wounded him, but I don\'t know where he went.", "我想我们使他受了致命伤，但我不知道他去哪儿了。");
	text = text.replace("Farker slashed the lot of us.", "那个混蛋被我们砍中不少下。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, you\'re bleeding.", "先生，你流血了。");
	text = text.replace("You tell him you know and that the priority right now is to take care of the bastard and the rest of the men.", "你告诉他你知道，现在的首要任务是照顾好私生子和其他队员。");
	
	text = text.replace("You put a hand to the pommel of your sword and decline the assassin\'s request.", "你把手放在剑柄上，拒绝了刺客的请求。");
	text = text.replace("He claps his hands.", "他鼓起了掌。");
	text = text.replace("Alright, sellsword. Fair enough.", "好吧，佣兵。足够好了。");
	text = text.replace("And don\'t bother with the theatrics there.", "不要在那里浪费时间。");
	text = text.replace("He nods to your sword-hand.", "他向你拿剑的手点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("If I really wanted the bastard dead, do you think I\'d be standing here?", "如果我真想让那个私生子死，你认为我还会站在这里么？");
	text = text.replace("I came to talk, and talk we did.", "我是来谈的，我们谈过了。");
	text = text.replace("The killing life has left me and with it, apparently, so too did my poker face.", "杀戮的生活离我而去，显然，我的扑克脸也是如此。");
	text = text.replace("You called my bluff and I suppose that\'s that. Good evening, mercenary.", "你向我虚张声势，我想就是这样。晚上好，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("Before you can say another word, the assassin ducks out of the tent.", "在你说出话之前，刺客就从帐篷里钻了出来。");
	text = text.replace(/You rush to see where he\'d gone to, but all you find is the dark of night\. (.*?) the bastard spies you peering around and asks what you\'re up to\./, "你冲过去看他去了哪里，但你发现的只是黑夜。$1 这个私生子看到你四处张望，还问你在干什么。");
	text = text.replace("You smile and tell him to get some rest for he truly deserves it.", "你微笑着告诉他休息一下，因为这对他来说绝对是值得的。");
	text = text.replace("Confused, the man shrugs.", "满脸疑惑，他耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Well, uh, I guess so. Thanks, captain.", "好的，呃，我想是的。多谢，队长。");
	
	text = text.replace("You refuse the assassin\'s offer.", "你拒绝了刺客的提议。");
	text = text.replace("He nods, coursing a hand over a candle.", "他点了点头，把一只手放在蜡烛上。");
	text = text.replace("Well then. I guess our talk has come to an end and so something else must begin.", "好吧那么。我想我们的谈话该结束了，所以必须开始别的事情。");
	text = text.replace("His face turns to you. He winks.", "他的脸转向你。他眨眨眼。");
	text = text.replace("The dagger comes quick, its sheen flashing as it slashes just before your face.", "匕首来的很快，它的光泽闪烁着，就在你的面前。");
	text = text.replace("You reach for your blade but the man kicks your hand, slamming the sword back into its scabbard.", "你伸手去拿你的利刃，但那个人踢了你的手，把剑猛地甩回鞘中。");
	text = text.replace("A second dagger comes - this one yours, unsheathed from behind your back and launched forward with murderous intentions.", "第二把匕首来了－从你背后抽出来，带着杀人的意图向前刺去。");
	text = text.replace("The assassin\'s dagger pops open into a trident into which your blade gets caught.", "刺客的匕首突然打开，变成一个三叉戟，你的利刃被勾住了。");
	text = text.replace("He twists his hand, disarming you in an instant, then twists his hand back around, closing the dagger into one blade again. Sonuvabitch...", "他扭转他的手，在一瞬间解除你的武装，然后再扭转他的手，再次把匕首合成一个刀片。婊子养的…");
	text = text.replace("The man goes for a stab, but you catch his arm.", "那人想捅一刀，但你抓住了他的胳膊。");
	text = text.replace("He shushes you with his free hand before retrieving another blade which you\'ve no means to stop.", "他用空着的那只手虚晃你一下，然后又拿起另一把利刃，你无法阻止他。");
	text = text.replace("He whispers with disturbing calmness.", "他以令人不安的平静低声说话。");
	text = text.replace("Die with grace, captain.", "优雅地死去吧，队长。");
	text = text.replace("As his hand goes backward, it suddenly disappears in a glint of metal.", "他的手向后一伸，突然消失在金属的闪光中。");
	text = text.replace("All that remains is a nub spewing crimson.", "剩下只是一片喷涌而出的红色粘稠物。");
	text = text.replace(/The assassin looks at the stump and screams\. (.*?) is standing there, weapon in hand\./, "刺客看着树桩尖叫起来。$1 站在那里，手里拿着武器。");
	text = text.replace("Another flash of metal and the assassin\'s head rolls off his shoulders.", "又一道金属闪光，刺客的脑袋从肩膀上滚落下来。");
	text = text.replace("A gush of blood pours out of the hole as his torso slams into your table and back against the ground.", "当他的躯干撞到你的桌子上并撞到地上时，血从洞里涌出。");
	text = text.replace("The bastard hurriedly asks.", "私生子急切地问。");
	text = text.replace("Are you alright? Who in the fark was that?", "你还好吗？那个混蛋是谁？");
	text = text.replace("More sellswords enter the tent to see what the commotion was.", "更多的佣兵进入帐篷，看看发生了什么骚乱。");
	text = text.replace("You let them know an assassin had come for the bastard, but you weren\'t going to give him over that easy.", "你让他们知道一个刺客来此刺杀私生子，但你没有让他轻易得手。");
	text = text.replace("The men applaud your defense of the mercenary.", "队员们为你保护雇佣兵的行为而喝彩。");

//beat_up_old_man_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across an old man hobbling along the road.", "你碰到一个老人在路上蹒跚而行。");
	text = text.replace("He settles himself against his walking stick and awaits your approach.", "他靠在手杖上，等候你的来临。");
	text = text.replace("His eyes are grey, but he tilts his head as though to see you with his ears.", "他的眼睛是灰色的，但他歪着头，好像在用耳朵看你。");
	text = text.replace("Chinking armor. Heavy footsteps. Steady breaths.", "裂缝的盔甲。沉重的步伐。稳定的呼吸。");
	text = text.replace("More warriors for a land of war.", "越来越多的勇士在大陆上征战。");
	text = text.replace("The man straightens up as though to say \'am I right?\'.", "这个人直起身子，好像在说“我说得对吗？”。");
	text = text.replace("You tell him that you\'re not here to harm him.", "你告诉他你不是来伤害他的。");
	text = text.replace("So yes, I am right, as usual.", "所以，是的，我是对的，和往常一样。");
	text = text.replace("It wouldn\'t be too much of a bother to run me through, though.", "不过，给我讲讲也不会太麻烦。");
	text = text.replace("My hearing\'s going and I suppose once it is gone so shall I be.", "我的听力正在消失，我想一旦它消失了，我也会消失的。");
	text = text.replace("He pauses and turns his head.", "他停顿了一下，转过头去。");
	text = text.replace("Did you say something?", "你说了什么吗？");
	text = text.replace(/You notice the man\'s got a nice jeweled ring on one of his bony fingers\. (.*?) sidles up to you\./, "你注意到他瘦骨嶙峋的手指上戴着一枚精美的宝石戒指。$1 悄悄走近你。");
	text = text.replace("We could take that... you know, like taking a tart from a baby.", "我们可以拿到它…你知道，就像从婴儿手里拿走蛋挞。");
	text = text.replace("A really blind, more helpless than usual baby.", "一个真正的瞎子比正常的婴儿更无助。");
	text = text.replace("An old man with a walking stick is found resting against a stone wall.", "人们发现一位拄着拐杖的老人靠在石墙上。");
	text = text.replace("His hand caresses the stones with a familiar touch.", "他的手以似曾相识的方式抚摸着石头。");
	text = text.replace("He stares at you, a jeweled ring glistens on one of his bony fingers.", "他凝视着你，骨瘦如柴的手指上戴着一枚闪闪发光的宝石戒指。");
	text = text.replace("Evening, sirs. What a fine day, no?", "晚上好，先生们。多好的天气啊，不是么？");
	text = text.replace("Getting a good look at him, you realize he is a blind man.", "仔细看他，你发现他是个瞎子。");
	text = text.replace("You come to an old man standing in the middle of the road, his body leaning against a walking stick.", "你看到一位老人站在路中间，身体靠在拐杖上。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s staring up at a road sign.", "他抬头盯着一个路标。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("I know there is a sign here.", "我知道这里有个路标。");
	text = text.replace(/I think (.*?) is that way, if I recall correctly\./, "我想 $1 在那条路上，如果我没记错的话。");
	text = text.replace("He turns to you grinning.", "他笑着转向你。");
	text = text.replace("His eyes glint white, blinded by old age.", "他因年老而双目失明，眼睛闪着白光。");
	text = text.replace("A very nice, very expensive looking jeweled ring glistens on one of his bony fingers.", "他瘦骨嶙峋的手指上戴着一枚非常漂亮，非常昂贵的宝石戒指。");
	
	text = text.replace("You approach the man.", "你走近那个老人。");
	text = text.replace("His head tilts up.", "他的头抬了起来。");
	text = text.replace("That is a quickened pace, stranger, but I do not hear the sound of a sword, instead...", "这是变快的步伐，陌生人，但我没有听到剑的声音，相反…");
	text = text.replace("With a sudden push you knock the man to the ground.", "你猛地一推，把老人撞倒在地。");
	text = text.replace("He clutches his walking stick, the end of it pointed upward as though you might impale yourself on its rounded tip.", "他紧握着手杖，手杖的末端向上翘着，仿佛要把自己刺进手杖的圆形尖端。");
	text = text.replace("You kick his hand out of the way and step on his wrist, bending down to take the ring.", "你把他的手踢开，踩在他的手腕上，弯下腰去拿戒指。");
	text = text.replace("Put steel through my heart while you\'re at it, ya bastard!", "当你这么干之时，把钢铁穿透我的心脏，你个混蛋！");
	text = text.replace("You let off the man and hand him back his stick, even helping him to his feet.", "你放开老人，把棍子还给他，甚至扶他站起来。");
	text = text.replace("No hard feelings, old man.", "别生气，老先生。");
	text = text.replace("You kick the man down.", "你把他打倒。");
	text = text.replace("He grunts as though you\'d just punted a pregnant boar.", "他呼噜呼噜地叫着，就好像你在一头怀孕的野猪身上踢了一脚。");
	text = text.replace("Turning over and clutching his stomach, he asks why, but you only kick him again to get him on his back.", "他翻了个身，捂着肚子，问为什么，但你只会再踢他一脚，让他仰面躺下。");
	text = text.replace("From there you easily rob him of the jeweled ring and make your leave.", "从那里你很容易就抢了他的珠宝戒指，然后离开。");
	text = text.replace("The man smacks his old-man lips, that disgusting, crackling dry-mouth noise.", "那人咂咂他那老年人的嘴唇，那种令人作呕的干裂的声音。");
	text = text.replace("In return, you rear back and throw a punch right into his stomach.", "作为回报，你后退一步并一拳打在他的肚子上。");
	text = text.replace("Not seeing it coming, the elder eats it in full, blowing the air out of his lungs and bowling over.", "老人没有看到拳头来了，就重重的吃了一击，呼出肺里的空气，滚了过去。");
	text = text.replace("As he gasps for breath, you relieve him of the ring and leave.", "当他喘不过气来的时候，你把戒指从他手指上拿下来，然后离开。");
	text = text.replace("The old man stands and leans against his walking stick.", "那位老人靠在手杖上站着。");
	text = text.replace("He raises his head up.", "他抬起头。");
	text = text.replace("Hmm, silence. The sound of ill intent between strangers.", "哼，沉默。这是陌生人之间的恶意声音。");
	text = text.replace("I stand in the dark, and you in the light, but where are we soon to be?", "我站在黑暗中，而你站在光明中，但我们会走向何方？");
	text = text.replace("You kick the man\'s walking stick out from him and he topples over in a bumbling heap, his bony frame collapsing like a rickety hut.", "你把那人的拐杖踢了出去，他就一瘸一拐地倒在地上，骨瘦如柴的身体就像一间摇摇欲坠的小木屋。");
	text = text.replace("He rolls over and espouses some wisdom about violence between men.", "他翻了个身，对男人之间的暴力行为表示赞同。");
	text = text.replace("You boot him in the chest and tell him to shut up.", "你朝他胸口踢了一脚，叫他闭嘴。");
	text = text.replace("The ring comes free of his finger with ease and you make your leave.", "把戒指轻轻松松地从他的手指上取下，你离开了。");
	text = text.replace("You crack your knuckles.", "你掰指关节发出响声。");
	text = text.replace("The old man leans back.", "老人向后靠了靠。");
	text = text.replace("Surely violence is not the answer?", "难道暴力能解决问题吗？");
	text = text.replace("This world doesn\'t need more of it.", "这个世界不需要更多。");
	text = text.replace("With a swift punch, you knock him down and he crumples into a dry heaving mess.", "你一拳把他打倒在地，他瘫成一团。");
	text = text.replace("Taking the ring, you respond.", "拿起戒指，你回应道。");
	text = text.replace("I don\'t give a damn what this world needs or doesn\'t.", "我他妈不在乎这个世界需要什么或不需要什么。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m my own world and you yours.", "我有我的世界，你有你的。");
	text = text.replace("They just happened to cross paths, that\'s all.", "它们只是碰巧相遇，仅此而已。");
	text = text.replace("And guess what, old man?", "你猜怎么着，老头？");
	text = text.replace("My world is bigger.", "我的世界更大。");

//beggar_begs_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/As you take stock of the inventory, you can\'t help but notice (.*?) lingering in your peripheral\./, "在你拿取清单上的货物的时候，你不禁注意到了 $1 逗留在你附近。");
	text = text.replace("Sighing, you finally turn to the former beggar and ask what he wants.", "叹息着，你终于看向了从前的乞丐并且问他，他想要什么。");
	text = text.replace("Like the poorest of the poor he holds a hand out, asking if maybe you could spare a few crowns.", "就像穷人中最穷的的人一样，他伸出了一只手，问你能不能给他一些克朗。");
	text = text.replace(/With practiced theatrics, (.*?) approaches you and lets loose a long tale of troubles and squabbles and empty bottles\./, "像提前练习过的舞台表演一样，$1 接近了你并且讲了一个很长的关于麻烦、斗嘴、和空瓶子的传说。");
	text = text.replace("The former beggar is down on his luck, apparently, and just needs a few extra crowns to get by.", "曾经的乞丐的运气已经很少了，显然的，他只需要多几枚克朗来勉强过活。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) tells you that (.*?) is going around the camp asking for crowns\./, "$1 告诉你那个 $2 正围绕着营地转悠乞讨一些克朗。");
	text = text.replace("Apparently the former beggar just needs a little more, expressing a longwinded sob story to anyone who\'ll listen.", "显然的，那个曾经的乞丐只需要一点点更多的东西，他期待能呜咽着给任何会听的人说一个漫长的故事。");
	text = text.replace("Hearing this news, you go to see the man yourself but before you can even get a word out the man lets loose his long narrative.", "听到了这个消息，你自己去会了会那个人，但是在你能说出一个字之前，那个人就开始了他的叙述。");
	text = text.replace("Finished, he looks you in the eye, trying to gauge whether or not you\'ll give him something.", "完成了以后，他直视着你，试着判断出你会不会给他些东西。");
	text = text.replace(/Apparently (.*?) the former beggar needs some help\./, "显然的，$1 曾经的乞丐需要些帮助。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s come to you, begging for a few crowns to help him get by.", "他来到了你的面前，祈求几枚克朗来让他过活。");
	text = text.replace("The man looks like he\'s in a poor state, but he\'s had plenty of practice of actually being poor so it\'s hard to tell if he\'s being honest or not.", "那个男人他看起来像是在贫穷状况下，但是他已经大量地练习过了假装真的贫穷，所以很难说他是真的贫穷，还是假的。");
	
	text = text.replace("You tell the beggar you\'ll cross his hands with a sword if he doesn\'t get back to work.", "你告诉那个男人你会用一把剑穿透他的手如果他不回去工作的话。");
	text = text.replace("The man shrugs and pretty much does as told.", "男人耸耸肩，并且真的如你所说的那样做了。");
	text = text.replace("That was easier than expected.", "这比想的要容易。");
	text = text.replace("The beggar\'s shoulders sag as you tell him to get back to work.", "乞丐的肩膀在你告诉他回去干活儿的时候垂了下来。");
	text = text.replace("You feel a little bad, but then remember that\'s how they get ya.", "你感到有一点不好，但是想起来了他们就是这样得到你的同情的。");
	
	text = text.replace("The beggar takes the crowns and with a smile gets right back to work.", "乞丐拿了克朗，笑了出来，并且马上回去工作了。");
	text = text.replace("Tired of his games, you give the beggar a few crowns and tell him to get back to work.", "对他的这种游戏感到厌烦，你给了乞丐一点克朗并且告诉他回去干活儿。");
	text = text.replace("He bows and thanks you and, surprisingly, actually gets back to work.", "他鞠了个躬，并且感谢了你，而且令人惊讶的，他真的回去干活儿了。");

//bowyer_crafts_masterwork_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the bowyer comes to you with a bit of request: he wishes to build a weapon for the ages\./, "$1 这个弓匠带着小小的请求走到你面前：他希望为这个时代制造一件武器。");
	text = text.replace("Apparently, the man has been attempting to build a bow of legendary qualities for many years, but now that he has been on the road he\'s picked up a few things to fill in his gaps of knowledge.", "显然，这个人多年来一直试图建造一个具有传奇品质的弓，但是现在他已经在路上了，拣起了一些东西来填补他的知识空白。");
	text = text.replace("Truly, he believes he can get it right this time.", "说真的，他相信这次他能做好。");
	text = text.replace("All he needs is a few resources to help procure the elements needed to construct it.", "他所需要的只是一些资源来帮助他获得制作弓所需要的材料。");
	text = text.replace("A sum of 500 crowns is what he humbly requests, and the quality wood you carry.", "他谦卑要求给他五百克朗，并要你运来上等的木料。");
	
	text = text.replace("The bow isn\'t quite legendary, but it is quite good.", "这把弓不是很有传奇色彩，但是很不错。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s light in the grip, easily spun from side to side with the air whistling as it whirls.", "它握起来很轻，很容易使射击方向从一边转向另一边，伴随着空气的尖啸声射击。");
	text = text.replace("You test the draw.", "你测试弓弦。");
	text = text.replace("A strong man will be required to wield it that is for sure.", "需要一个强壮的人来驾驭它，这是肯定的。");
	text = text.replace("When you loose an arrow, the shaft travels unbelievably straight and the shot almost seems to aim itself.", "当你射出一支箭时，箭轴会令人难以置信地对正，而箭几乎是自动瞄准的。");
	text = text.replace("A brilliant weapon if you ever saw one!", "这是你见过的最厉害的武器！");
	text = text.replace("The bow was constructed with a mix of woods whose names you do not know.", "弓是用你不知道名字的木头混合而成的。");
	text = text.replace("Colors of this tree and that spiral through the curve of the weapon, looking arboreally damascened.", "这棵树和那棵树的颜色螺旋穿过武器的弓背，看起来像是树的颜色真的变深了。");
	text = text.replace("Testing the draw, the string proves itself mighty.", "测试弓弦，就能证明它的威力。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re no marksman, but when you loose an arrow it almost seems to guide itself to its target.", "你不是神射手，但当你射出一支箭时，它似乎能自动指向目标。");
	text = text.replace("A terrific weapon, if for no other reason it made you look better than you really are.", "一个可怕的武器，如果没有其他原因，它使你看起来比你实际上射击技术更好了。");
	text = text.replace("You congratulate the bowyer.", "你向弓匠表示祝贺。");
	
	text = text.replace("Is this thing a wild experiment?", "这是一个疯狂的实验吗？");
	text = text.replace("The wood cricks and cracks when bent, the string frizzes and goes wiry every time you draw it back, and you swear you saw a termite poking its head out of the shaft.", "木头弯曲时就会出现弯曲和裂缝，每次你把它拉回来，绳子就会卷曲和变硬，你发誓你看到一只白蚁从轴中探出头来。");
	text = text.replace("Every tested arrow goes haywire, skirting this way or that, anywhere but its supposed target.", "每一支经过测试的箭都乱了套，绕着这个或那个方向飞，除了它应该射到的地方。");
	text = text.replace(/You ease the bowyer\'s pain by blaming yourself for how inaccurate the weapon is, but (.*?) and (.*?) both give it a try and come to even worse results\./, "你通过责备自己来缓解弓匠制作武器不准确的痛苦，但是 $1 和 $2 都试过了，得出了更糟的结果。");
	text = text.replace("The bowyer eventually shuffles off, cradling his construction in his arms before tossing it onto the stockpile of weapons where you\'d wish it\'d look just like any other bow, but its obscene ugliness makes it stick out like a hot coal on a haystack.", "弓匠最终拖着脚走开了，他怀里抱着自己的弓，然后把它扔进了武器库，在那里你会希望它看起来和其他弓一样，但它丑陋的样子让它像干草堆上的热煤一样突出。");
	text = text.replace("Surely no man will be accidentally wielding that thing!", "当然没有人会不小心挥舞着它！");
	
	text = text.replace(/You tell the bowyer that the (.*?) has no resources to spare\./, "你告诉弓匠，$1 没有多余的资源。");
	text = text.replace("The man grinds his teeth, and apparently whatever words he had to say, for he says nothing and turns on his heels and stomps off.", "那人牙齿打颤，显然无论如何他得说点什么，但他什么也没说，他转过身跺着脚走掉了。");
	text = text.replace("In the distance you finally hear what kindness he had in store for you - a litany of swearing and cursing and eventually moaning disappointment.", "在远处，你终于听到了他为你准备的善意－一连串的咒骂和诅咒，最后是失望的低语。");

//brawler_teaches_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A shadow crosses over you from behind.", "一个影子从你背后穿过。");
	text = text.replace(/When you look back, (.*?) is standing there with a rather distant look in his eyes\./, "当你回头看时，$1 正站在那里，眼中带着深邃的目光。");
	text = text.replace(/He cracks his knuckles in one long staccato before asking if he can train up (.*?)\. You ask why\./, "他断断续续地敲了很久的指关节，然后问他是否可以训练 $1。你问为什么。");
	text = text.replace("The brawler looks down at you.", "打手俯视着你。");
	text = text.replace("Because he is weak.", "因为他弱呗。");
	text = text.replace("Hmmm, good enough.", "哼，这很好。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) and (.*?) are found in a mudpit with their hands wrapped in cloth and leaves, padding for the knuckles and to keep them from cutting one another with every punch\./, "$1 和 $2 被发现在一个坭坑里，他们的手被布和树叶包裹着，用来垫在指关节上，以防止他们每次出拳都互相擦伤。");
	text = text.replace("The brawler has his trainee bouncing counter-clockwise along the ring of the fighting circle, punching the air as he goes, and with his trainer hitting or kicking him every time he passes by.", "打手让他的受训者沿战圈逆时针方向跑跳，一边走一边挥拳打在空中，每次他经过时，他的训练者都会打他或踢他。");
	text = text.replace("The men glisten with sweat as they work.", "这两个人工作时时满脸是汗。");
	text = text.replace(/When (.*?) begins to slow, (.*?) hits him as though a jockey would a sluggish horse\./, "当 $1 动作开始变得缓慢，$2 击打他，就像骑师对一匹缓慢的马。");
	text = text.replace(/After an hour of this, (.*?) steps back and invites his trainee to attack him\./, "一小时后，$1 后退一步，并让他的受训者攻击他。");
	text = text.replace("Predictably, the assault is aimless and pitiful.", "可以预见的是，这种攻击是漫无目的和令人遗憾的。");
	text = text.replace("Long, looping punches are thrown with no energy behind them.", "漫长而循环的出拳没有任何能量。");
	text = text.replace("The brawler ducks and weaves out of the way, punching every attempted strike with a counter-punch of his own.", "打手躲闪并反击受训者的每一次进攻。");
	text = text.replace("See what happens when you are tired?", "看看在你累了的时候会发生什么？");
	text = text.replace("This is why we must train.", "这就是我们必须训练的原因。");
	text = text.replace("Even the most able and deadly are worth nothing without air in their lungs and fresh legs beneath them.", "即使是最能干、最致命的人，如果肺里没有空气，脚下没有有力的双腿，也一文不值。");
	
	text = text.replace(/The brawler has (.*?) stand completely still\./, "打手让 $1 完全静止不动。");
	text = text.replace("He circles about the man, cracking his knuckles as he sizes him up.", "他绕着那个人转了一圈，一边掰着指关节，一边打量着他。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, he lets his intentions be known.", "最后，他让大家知道他的意图。");
	text = text.replace("I am going to beat you until you break.", "我要打你直到你崩溃。");
	text = text.replace("A moment is given to the trainee to acknowledge what is about to happen.", "给受训者一点时间来了解将要发生的事情。");
	text = text.replace(/He sucks in a great gulp of breath and then nods\. (.*?) wastes no time wheeling a bola punch right into the man\'s chest\./, "他深深地吸了一口气，然后点了点头。$1 毫不犹豫地挥拳猛击那人的胸部。");
	text = text.replace("He bowls over at which point he is kicked in the shoulder repeatedly until he stands back up.", "他滚了过去，肩膀被踢了好几次，直到他再次站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("There the brawler continues to circle and deliver blows.", "打手继续绕圈和打人。");
	text = text.replace("Not every strike is thrown with conviction: most are meant to inflict pain, but not what could be called irreversible damage.", "并不是每一次打击都是令人信服的：大多数打击都是为了造成痛苦，但不是所谓的不可逆转的伤害。");
	text = text.replace("The brawler, if he wanted to, could kill this man with his bare fists, but that is not the purpose of this training.", "打手，如果他想，他完全可以赤手空拳杀死这个人，但这不是训练的目的。");
	text = text.replace("You realize that this mode of \'toughening up\' probably happened to the brawler himself at some point or another.", "你意识到这种“强硬起来”的方式可能在某个时候发生在打手自己身上。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the heavy-handed-rough-and-tumble brawler is found leaning over, his arms fenced out before himself in a defensive posture, and (.*?) is standing adjacent, trying to mimic the stance\./, "$1 这个重磅的－有一手的－粗暴的－而且－会翻跟头的打手身体前倾，双臂在身前呈防御姿势，而 $2 站在旁边，试图模仿这个姿势。");
	text = text.replace(/The brawler drops his body low and shoots in under (.*?)\'s arms, there wrapping both hands around the man\'s waist and lifting him up in the air before dumping him on his back\. (.*?) steps away, cracking his knuckles and telling (.*?) to get up\./, "打手把身体放低，朝 $1的腋下冲去，双手搂住他的腰，把他举在空中，然后把他扔到地上。$2 走开了，掰着指关节，叫 $3 站起来。");
	text = text.replace("You need to be ready for two things: me coming in low, and me coming in high.", "你需要做好两个准备：我在低处，和我在高处。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) dusts himself off then complains a little\./, "$1 掸去身上的灰尘，然后抱怨了一下。");
	text = text.replace("How can I possibly do both?", "我怎么可能两全其美呢？");
	text = text.replace(/The brawler ignores the question and simply asks the man to attack him\. (.*?) obliges, coming in high with a hurled fist\. (.*?) deflects the blow with a shoulder-roll before throwing a cross-counter that has (.*?) spinning on his feet\./, "打手忽视了这个问题，只是要求这个人攻击他。$1 被迫强起打出一记重拳。$2 扭肩躲闪并交替出拳反击，将 $3 击倒。");
	text = text.replace("The fist-fighter cracks his knuckles again and spits.", "这个拳击手又掰响了指关节并开始吐口水。");
	text = text.replace("Practice. That\'s how. Now get back up and let\'s go again.", "练习。就是这样做。现在站起来，让我们再来一遍。");

//brawler_vs_brawler_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/As you sit with the men around the fire, a discussion across the flames starts to get a little loud\. (.*?) the brawler stands up and points at his own chest with a hearty laugh\./, "当你和男人们围坐在火堆旁时，一场火焰边的讨论开始变得有些喧嚣。$1 这个打手站起来，指着自己的胸膛，发出一声爽朗的笑声。");
	text = text.replace("You? You think you could take me?", "你？你觉得你能摆平我么？");
	text = text.replace(/The other brawler, (.*?), jumps to his feet\./, "另一个打手，$1，一跃而起。");
	text = text.replace("Take you? I could put ya under the ground ya farkin\' pillowfisted fool!", "摆平你？我能让你躺地上，你个娘娘腔的蠢货！");
	text = text.replace(/The slightest suggestion that (.*?)\'s fists weren\'t made of jaw-demolishing bricks kicks off a brutal fight\./, "哪怕是最轻微的暗示，说 $1的拳头不是由能把人的下巴震碎的砖块构成的，都会引发一场凶残的打斗。");
	text = text.replace("The brawlers grab one another and swing their free hands in looping undercuts.", "两个打手彼此抓住对方，绕着圈挥拳相向。");
	text = text.replace("Each punch lands with cracking ferocity.", "每一拳都异常猛烈。");
	text = text.replace("Surely no man could take so much damage and stay on his feet, but here you\'re witnessing two fellas doing just that.", "当然没有人能承受这么大的伤害后还能站起来，但在这里，你正在目睹他俩这么干。");
	text = text.replace("You order the company to break up the fight.", "你命令队员们阻止这场争斗。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) pinches a nostril and shoots blood out of the other\. He shrugs\./, "$1 捏着一个鼻孔，从另一个鼻孔里喷出血来。他耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Just havin\' a bit o\' a scrap, sir.", "刚才只是小打小闹，先生。");
	text = text.replace(/Popping a shoulder back into socket, (.*?) nods\./, "把肩膀复位后，$1 点头。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, no harm no foul.", "是啊，不打不成交。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as the two men shake hands and clap one another on the shoulder, each congratulating the other on how nasty their punches were.", "你看到这两个人握手，拍拍对方的肩膀，互相祝贺对方的拳头有多狠。");

//bright_vs_dumb_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) is perhaps one of the dumbest individuals you\'ve ever met but, for a brief moment, it does appear that (.*?) gets through and teaches him a thing or two about critical thinking and memorization\./, "$1 可能是你见过的最笨的人之一，但是，有那么一小会儿，似乎 $2 做到并教会了他一些关于批判性思维和记忆的东西。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as the two sit together and look over some scrolls.", "你看着这两个人坐在一起看一些卷轴。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re not sure where the smart man got such papers, but the unlearning oaf is certainly paying a lot of attention to them.", "你不确定聪明的人是从哪儿弄到这些文件的，但这个不懂事的笨蛋显然对这些文件很感兴趣。");
	text = text.replace(/As you watch, (.*?) is asking rather deep, profound questions\./, "正如你所看到的，$1 正在问一些相当深刻又深奥的问题。");
	text = text.replace("Questions about the land and its relationship to people, and the sky and its relationship to the birds.", "关于土地和它与人的关系，天空和它与鸟的关系的问题。");
	text = text.replace(/You slowly realize the idiot is merely glancing around and describing what he\'s seeing in the sort of \'inquisitive\' language (.*?) has taught him - namely by attaching a smarmily-intoned question to the end of every sentence\./, "你慢慢地就会意识到，这个白痴只不过是在东张西望，而且用 $1 教授的那种“好奇”的语言描述他所看到的东西－就是在每句话的后面加上一个带有阿谀口吻的问句。");
	text = text.replace(/When the two finish up, (.*?) comes to you with a grin\./, "当这两人结束谈话时，$1 笑嘻嘻地向你走来。");
	text = text.replace("I think we\'re really getting somewhere with him.", "我想我们真的让他进步了。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s learning, you know?", "他在学习，你知道吗？");
	text = text.replace("With students like that, all you gotta do is be patient and take your time.", "有这样的学生，你要做的就是耐心一点，慢慢来。");
	text = text.replace(/A little ways away, (.*?) is pounding ants with a rock\./, "不远处，$1 正在用一块石头砸蚂蚁。");
	text = text.replace(/You simply nod and let (.*?) live out every teacher\'s biggest fantasy\./, "你只是点头，让 $1 实现每个老师的伟大梦想。");

//broken_cart_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While marching down the road, you find a man with a broken cart by the side of the path.", "当你沿路行进时，你在路边发现一个人，他的货车坏了。");
	text = text.replace("By the wagon there is a donkey standing idle and as defeated as a donkey can look.", "载重货车旁边站着一头无所事事的驴子，它看上去已经疲惫不堪了。");
	text = text.replace("The trader looks a little better than that and your appearance seems to have scared him.", "商人似乎看起来比较好一点，你的出现似乎吓了他一跳。");
	text = text.replace("He rears up, backing away momentarily.", "他向后仰起身子，立刻向后退去。");
	text = text.replace("Have you come to take my things?", "你们是来拿我的东西的吗？");
	text = text.replace("If so, you needn\'t kill me.", "如果是这样，你就不必杀我了。");
	text = text.replace("Take what you want.", "拿走你想要的。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You disarm the man from his fears and order a few of the (.*?)\'s finest to get the wagon back on the road\./, "你消除了他的恐惧，并命令 $1 中最好的队员让载重货车重新上路。");
	text = text.replace("They make short work of it, the trader looking rather impressed by their efficiency.", "他们很快完成了，商人对他们的效率印象深刻。");
	text = text.replace("With his wares back on the road, he offers a few tokens of gratitude right off the wagon itself.", "随着他的财产重新回到道路上，他从载重货车里取出一些物品的作为感谢。");
	text = text.replace("These provisions will be useful in the days to come.", "这些补给品在未来的日子里会很有用。");
	
	text = text.replace("The merchant is scared in your presence, but you quickly disarm him of his fears.", "商人在你面前很害怕，但你很快消除了他的恐惧。");
	text = text.replace("A few brothers are ordered to get the cart back onto the path.", "几个队员奉命把货车拉回到小路上。");
	text = text.replace("They do it as fast as hardy men can, but when it\'s over one of them cries out and doubles over.", "这些吃苦耐劳的人尽可能快的去完成，但是当快要完事的时候，他们中的一个人大声惨叫而且声音越来越大。");
	text = text.replace("The trader, eyes wide with renewed horror, quickly offers you some provisions as a token of his gratitude.", "商人瞪大了眼睛，眼中充满了新的恐惧，他迅速地给你提供了一些补给品，以表示他的感激之情。");
	text = text.replace("Maybe he thinks you\'ll punish him for the injuries?", "也许他认为你会因为队员受伤而惩罚他？");
	text = text.replace("Regardless, the supplies will be a welcome addition for the days to come.", "无论如何，在未来的日子里，这些补给品将是一个很好的补充。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You order the men to search the cart and take what they can\. (.*?) draws his sword and looks ready to slay the donkey, the animal looking stupidly at its own mortality in the reflection of the blade\./, "你命令队员们搜查货车，尽可能能拿走一切。$1 拔出他的剑，看起来准备杀死驴，动物愚蠢地在锋刃的反光中看着自己的死亡。");
	text = text.replace("The merchant cries out and you hold your hand out, staying the execution.", "商人哭了出来，你伸出手，制止了对驴子的行刑。");
	text = text.replace("Leave the draught animal where it stands.", "把这个拉稀的动物留在原地。");
	text = text.replace("The trader offers meager thanks as a line of your men walk behind him, his very goods in their hands.", "商人苦着脸表示了感谢，因为你的队员正排成队列走在他身后，手里拿着他最好的货物。");

//broken_wagon_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You find an abandoned wagon amongst some tall reeds\. (.*?) checks it out and barks back\./, "你在高高的芦苇丛中发现了一辆废弃的载重货车。$1 检查它，并吼叫回答。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s broke as shit, but I think we can salvage parts of it.", "它破的像坨屎，但我想我们可以挽救回一部分。");

//broken_wagon_in_swamp_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Swamps are no safe place for a man\'s travels.", "沼泽对于旅行者来说不是安全的地方。");
	text = text.replace("Judging by the neverending smog and the way the trees bend, there\'s little doubt that it\'s a bubbling domicile for all things demonic.", "从没完没了的雾霾和树木弯曲的方式来判断，毫无疑问，这里是恶魔出没的地方。");
	text = text.replace("At least that\'s what the druids of these parts like to say.", "至少这一带的德鲁伊们好像是这么说的。");
	text = text.replace(/All you find is a couple of dead horses drowned in the mire and a wagon crushed by the mud which has seeped over its wheels and bed\. (.*?) rifles through the remains and manages to recover some items\./, "你所能找到的只是几匹淹死在泥里的马和一辆撞坏的载重货车，车轮和车座上沾满了泥浆。$1 仔细地检查残害，并努力尝试找到一些物品。");
	text = text.replace("Well, it\'s something. Whoever left this here left a short while ago.", "好吧，有一些东西。不知道是谁不久前把它扔在这。");
	text = text.replace("Probably spooked by whatever the hell lives out here in the day-to-day.", "可能是被每天在这里出没的什么恐怖生物吓到了。");
	
	text = text.replace("Sir, wait.", "先生，等一下。");
	text = text.replace(/The former butcher, (.*?), says\./, "队伍中的屠夫，$1，说道。");
	text = text.replace("He moves on ahead and starts hacking at the corpse of a horse.", "他继续前进，开始切割马的尸体。");
	text = text.replace("He cuts out a series of chunks, wraps them in large leaves, dries them with a bit of dirt and salt, and hands them over.", "他切下一堆块状物，用大叶子包裹起来，用一点泥土和盐把它们弄干，然后递过来。");
	text = text.replace("No reason in leaving behind what can be used.", "没理由丢下我们还能用的东西。");

//butcher_gives_pointers_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You find (.*?) the butcher tracing a finger along (.*?)\'s unclothed back\./, "你发现 $1 这个屠夫在 $2 裸露的后背上用手指划着什么。");
	text = text.replace("He finds a point between the sinews and scars and taps it.", "他在肌肉和伤疤之间找到一个点，然后轻敲它。");
	text = text.replace("Here. If you strike yourself here, the largest amount of meat - I mean muscle, I will be hit.", "这里。如果你击打自己的这个地方，肉最多的地方，我是说肌肉，我认为会很爽。");
	text = text.replace("The flagellant looks up.", "苦修者抬起头。");
	text = text.replace("Will it be painful?", "那会痛么？");
	text = text.replace("A grin crosses the butcher\'s face.", "屠夫的脸上露出了笑容。");
	text = text.replace("Oh yes, very much so.", "噢，是的，非常爽。");
	text = text.replace("It appears the man is giving the flagellant pointers on how to mark himself up.", "似乎这个家伙在给苦修者指点，如何放飞自我。");
	text = text.replace(/Before you can step in, (.*?) takes up a whip and hits himself right where (.*?) had directed him to\./, "在你能插话之前，$1 拿起鞭子，打在 $2 之前指给他的地方。");
	text = text.replace("The tendrils of leather, glass, and sharpened bone snap against the man\'s back, dig in, and then upon retrieval tear his flesh asunder.", "皮革，纤维和嶙峋的骨头在他背上劈啪作响，抽到肉里去了，然后他皮开肉绽了。");

//butcher_vs_wardog_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You hear a yelp and quickly rush to the noise.", "你听到一声尖叫，迅速冲到噪音的方向。");
	text = text.replace(/When you get there, you\'re not sure whether it was man or dog that produced it\. (.*?) the butcher is holding a cleaver up and a wardog is rearing beneath him, both sides ready to lunge\./, "当你到达那里时，你不确定是人还是狗制造了噪音。$1 这个屠夫手里拿着一把菜刀，一条战犬在他身前直立着，双方都准备扑上去。");
	text = text.replace("The man sees you and quickly sweeps the weapon behind his back.", "屠夫看见你，迅速地把武器藏在背后。");
	text = text.replace("The hound takes a squat and throws some puppy eyes your way.", "这条猎犬蹲了下来，可爱地看着你。");
	text = text.replace("Raising an eyebrow, you try not to make sense of the scene.", "扬起眉毛，你试着不去思考这个场景。");
	text = text.replace("Play nice now.", "你们玩的挺好啊。");
	text = text.replace("The butcher scoffs.", "屠夫嘲笑道。");
	text = text.replace("Oy\', me and the bitch were just having a talk that\'s all.", "噢，我就和那个贱人唠唠嗑，就是这样。");

//butcher_wardogs_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You open a crate of food to find the last of your reserves.", "你打开一箱食物来寻找你最后的储备。");
	text = text.replace("An apple rolls across the bottom, sounding not unlike the grumble of an empty stomach as it totters about.", "一个苹果滚过底部，听起来和摇摇晃晃的空腹咕噜声没什么两样。");
	text = text.replace("A few loaves of bread give it some company and there is a piece of meat wrapped in a thick leaf. That\'s it.", "几条面包给了它一些陪伴，还有一块用厚叶子包着的肉。就这样了。");
	text = text.replace(/When you close the lid and turn around, (.*?) the butcher is standing there\./, "当你关上盖子转过身来时，$1 就站在那里。");
	text = text.replace("Hey there boss. I see we got a problem.", "嘿，老板。我知道我们有麻烦了。");
	text = text.replace("So how about I... fix it?", "所以我…摆平它？");
	text = text.replace("Just then, he thumbs over his shoulder, right in the direction of two war dogs chained up to a stake.", "就在这时，他用拇指搭在肩膀上，朝着拴在木桩上的两只战犬的方向。");
	
	text = text.replace("The dogs are sitting rather studiously, panting and looking pretty content, so durable is their sense of happiness.", "这些狗很老实地坐着，气喘吁吁，看起来很满足，所以他们的幸福感是持久的。");
	text = text.replace("But you\'ve mouths to feed and battles to fight.", "但你有嘴要喂，有仗要打。");
	text = text.replace(/You give (.*?) the go ahead to do what is right for the company\./, "你让 $1 去做对战队有益的事。");
	text = text.replace("The butcher meanders his way toward the mutts, holding out one hand to pet them as the other clutches a knife behind his back.", "屠夫弯弯曲曲地走向那些狗狗，伸出一只手来抚摸它们，另一只手在背后抓着一把刀。");
	text = text.replace("You do not stick around to watch what happens next, but a short yelp quickly followed by another turns your already empty stomach.", "你不忍站在那里看接下来会发生什么，但是尖锐的声音已经从你空空的胃里传出来了。");
	
	text = text.replace("You shake your head no.", "你摇头表示反对。");
	text = text.replace("Absolutely not. They are as part of the company as any man, and certainly some men would rather starve than eat their own.", "绝对不行。他们和任何人一样是战队的一员，当然有人宁愿饿死也不能吃自己的战友。");
	text = text.replace("The butcher shrugs.", "屠夫耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re just dogs, sir. Mutts. Mongrels.", "它们只是狗，先生。野狗。杂种狗。");
	text = text.replace("Ain\'t nothing but a beast that knows its name and little else.", "只不过是一只知道自己名字的野兽。");
	text = text.replace("There are plenty of pups to find when we need them.", "当我们需要它们的时候，有很多只小狗可以找到。");
	text = text.replace("Again, you shake your head.", "再一次的，你摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace(/We\'re not killing the dogs, (.*?)\. And don\'t think I don\'t see the glint in your eye\./, "我们不是在杀狗，$1。别以为我看不到你眼中的凶光。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s more to slaughtering them animals than just feeding a few mouths.", "屠杀这些动物意味着很多，不仅仅是喂了几口而已。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) can only shrug again\./, "$1 只能再次耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("I can\'t pick and choose what gives me pleasure, sir, but I\'ll follow yer orders.", "我不能挑选和选择什么给了我快乐，先生，但我听从你的命令。");

//caravan_guard_vs_raider_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While you expect the men you hire to leave their old lives behind, sometimes it is not so.", "虽然你期望你雇佣的人会抛弃过去的生活，但有时情况并非如此。");
	text = text.replace(/It appears that (.*?) and (.*?) are well acquainted: the caravan hand once dealt with the raider personally in some sort of battle that ended with no victors\./, "似乎 $1 和 $2彼此非常熟悉：商队成员在曾经在某种没有胜利者的战斗中亲自对付过掠夺者。");
	text = text.replace("Now they seek to finish what they\'d started long ago, the two tumbling about on the ground, throwing punches and elbows and some spit if an eye or cheek calls for it.", "现在，他们试图完成他们很久以前就开始的事情，他们在地上打作一团，挥拳和肘击着对方，向对方的眼睛和脸颊吐口水。");
	text = text.replace("You separate the two yourself, pulling them apart and making it quite clear that they are sellswords now, not enemies.", "你亲自把他们分开，把他们推到两边并让他们清楚他们现在是佣兵，不是敌人。");
	text = text.replace("You force the two to shake hands and they do so.", "你强迫他们握手，他们听从了。");
	text = text.replace("The caravan hand nods.", "商队成员点头。");
	text = text.replace(/Nice left, (.*?)\./, "身手不错，$1。");
	text = text.replace("The raider nods back, wiping away a bit of blood running clear of his nose.", "掠夺者也点头，擦去一点从鼻子里流出的血。");
	text = text.replace("Yer stronger than I remember.", "你比我想象中的要强壮。");
	text = text.replace("The two men go off together to get fixed up, going as men do, their troubles so easily left behind.", "两个人一起去接受治疗，像个男人一样，他们的过节很容易抛之脑后。");

//caravan_hand_cart_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You come across the once-caravan hand, (.*?), finicking with the company wagon\./, "你偶然发现曾经的商队成员，$1，正在摆弄战队的载重货车。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s nailing a slat of board to the bed and using pins to put it on a roller.", "他把一块木板固定住，用大头钉把它钉在滚轴上。");
	text = text.replace("The board can then drop down into the belly of the wagon with a little bit of a pull and switch.", "然后，只要轻轻一拉，木板就可以落在载重货车的腹部。");
	text = text.replace("Rather ingenious. This will allow you to load more onto the wagon.", "相当巧妙。这样你就可以在载重货车上装更多东西了。");

//cat_on_tree_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You find a boy and girl looking up a tree.", "你发现一个男孩和一个女孩在向一棵树上看。");
	text = text.replace("The girl throws her hands up.", "女孩举起双手。");
	text = text.replace("Alright, stay there until you die!", "好吧，在那里待到死吧！");
	text = text.replace("See if I care!", "我才不在乎呢！");
	text = text.replace("The boy, spotting you, asks if perhaps you could help them get their cat out of the tree.", "那个男孩发现了你，询问你是否可以帮他们把猫从树上弄下来。");
	text = text.replace("Looking up, you do see a feline flopped over a branch, basking in the sun.", "抬头一看，你确实发现一只猫趴在树枝上，正在晒太阳。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) nocks an arrow and sticks his tongue out as he aims up the tree\./, "$1 搭上弓并且在向树上瞄准时伸出了舌头。");
	text = text.replace("The girl and boy don\'t seem fond of this idea and clap their hands over their eyes.", "女孩和男孩似乎不喜欢这个主意，他们用手捂住眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("The archer looses the shot and it cracks against the cat\'s branch, breaking it and sending the cat cartwheeling down the tree like a game of devil sticks.", "弓箭手松开了箭，打在猫的树枝上咔嚓一响，折断了树枝，猫像玩魔棒游戏一样侧着身子从树上滚下来。");
	text = text.replace("When it hits the ground, the boy and girl lunge on it.", "当它着地时，男孩和女孩猛冲上去。");
	text = text.replace("They pet it and thank you for your troubles.", "他们抚摸着它，感谢你给他们解决麻烦。");
	text = text.replace("The girl squeezes the cat warmly.", "那个女孩温柔地拥抱那只猫。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, we got ourselves something to eat!", "终于，我们有东西吃了！");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) readies himself, nocking an arrow and taking aim\./, "$1 做好准备，搭上弓瞄准。");
	text = text.replace("The cat purrs as it stares down the line of the shot, rather sublime in its suicidal stance.", "这只猫发出咕噜咕噜的声音，向下盯着弓手拉弓，显得视死如归。");
	text = text.replace("Closing one eye, the archer lets the arrow fly.", "闭上一只眼睛，弓箭手让箭飞起来。");
	text = text.replace("There isn\'t much mewling to be had.", "没有什么值得大惊小怪的。");
	text = text.replace("The cat tumbles down the tree like a game of devil sticks and lands on the ground with an arrow shaft halfway out its head.", "这只猫像玩魔棒游戏一样从树上滚了下来，落在了地上，一根箭射入它头的一半处。");
	text = text.replace("The girl crouches down and stares at the slinky bit of brain wobbling off the arrowtip.", "女孩蹲下身子，盯着在箭尖下抽搐的猫头。");
	text = text.replace("She looks up at you, as though it were you who fired the shot.", "她抬头看着你，似乎是你射的那一箭。");
	text = text.replace("That was my friend.", "那是我的朋友。");
	text = text.replace("You tell her you\'re sorry and that she\'ll find more friends.", "你告诉她你很抱歉，她会找到更多的朋友。");
	text = text.replace("As for the boy, he pockets the bit of brain and slings the cat carcass over his shoulder. He bleakly states.", "至于那个男孩，他把猫的大脑装进口袋，然后把猫的尸体扛在肩上。他显得很阴郁。");
	text = text.replace("At least we\'ve somethin\' to eat now.", "至少我们现在有东西吃了。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) snaps his fingers\./, "$1 打了个响指。");
	text = text.replace("Oy, I\'veuhplan! You little runts just wait a moment!", "唔哦，我有个主意！你们两个小鬼等一会儿。");
	text = text.replace("The rat catcher takes a rat out of his pocket you\'d no idea he even had.", "捕鼠者从口袋里掏出一只老鼠，你根本都想不到他会这么做。");
	text = text.replace("Chirping his lips like a mewling cat himself, he holds the little rodent up.", "他鼓唇弄舌就像喵喵叫的猫一样，把小老鼠举起来。");
	text = text.replace("The cat takes notice, perking its ears.", "猫注意到了，竖起了耳朵。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah that\'s right you pussy, c\'mon down, it\'s lunch time.", "是的，这就对了，小猫咪，下来吧，午餐时间到了。");
	text = text.replace("The rat catcher brings the rat to his lips and whispers.", "捕鼠者把小老鼠拿到嘴唇边，并低声细语。");
	text = text.replace("No it\'s not, heheh.", "不，不是的，呵呵。");
	text = text.replace(/As the cat descends, (.*?) holds his friend out a little more\./, "当猫下来时，$1 把他的朋友向外放一点。");
	text = text.replace("It begins to scrape and scuttle against his hands, perhaps not trusting its master to keep it.", "老鼠开始在他的手上刮来刮去，也许是不相信它的主人能留住它。");
	text = text.replace("But the moment the cat lunges for the meal, the rat catcher pockets the rat and snags the cat all in one swift motion.", "但是，当猫扑向食物时，捕鼠者把老鼠装进口袋，然后迅速地把猫抓起来。");
	text = text.replace("The children clap and cheer as he hands the cat over.", "当他把猫递过去时，孩子们鼓掌欢呼。");
	text = text.replace("Even some of the men are impressed by the fella\'s feline-like reflexes!", "甚至有些人也对这家伙像猫一样的反应能力印象深刻！");
	text = text.replace("You bluntly tell the kids they should get a dog and make your leave.", "你直截了当地告诉孩子们他们应该找条狗并让我们走。");

//childrens_crusade_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While on the path, you come across a small army of children.", "在路上，你遇到一小群孩子。");
	text = text.replace("The oldest and biggest amongst them is probably fifteen at most with a tussled crop of orange hair and a spear for a weapon.", "其中最年长的和最强壮的至多十五岁，长着一堆蓬乱的橙色头发，拿着一支长矛当武器。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s leading the troop, a little fighting force provincial to the path more than any town or city.", "他率领着一支部队，一支比任何村子或城镇巡逻队都弱小的杂牌军。");
	text = text.replace("As they cross paths with you, this little leader tips his head at you.", "当他们在路上与你相遇时，这个小领袖抬头看向你。");
	text = text.replace("Make way! We are on a righteous march and shan\'t be stopped!", "让路！我们正在进行正义的行军，不该被阻挡！");
	text = text.replace("Curious, you ask where it is they are off to.", "你很好奇，问他们要去哪里。");
	text = text.replace("The kid answers as though incredulous you don\'t know.", "那孩子回答，好像不相信你不知道似。");
	text = text.replace("Well let me tell you, sellsword.", "好吧，让我告诉你，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("We are heading north through the frozen wastes.", "我们正穿过冰冻的荒地向北行进。");
	text = text.replace("Uncultured and uncivilized tribes need to hear of the old gods, either by the word or by the sword.", "无知的的和未开化的部落需要了解古老的神明，要么用语言，要么用剑。");
	text = text.replace("He lifts the spear. A rather chirpy \'warcry\' is raised from the army.", "一支欢快的“战歌”从这支军队中响起。");
	text = text.replace("It appears some religious fervor has taken ahold of this wandering and harmless, and therefore suicidal, group.", "看来是某种宗教狂热控制了这个流浪的、无害的，因此会自杀的群体。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the kids to go home to their parents.", "你告诉孩子们回家和父母团聚。");
	text = text.replace("The leader laughs and the others follow suit, like little \'uns easily impressed by their big brother.", "小领袖笑了，其他人也跟着笑，就像小朋友很容易被他们的大哥哥打动一样。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Why do you think we\'ve come this far?", "为什么你认为我们已经走了这么远？");
	text = text.replace("Our parents know right where we are, and they know where we are is truthfully right.", "我们的父母知道我们在哪里，他们知道我们在哪里是绝对正确的。");
	text = text.replace("The old gods need to be known throughout the land! Now, make way!", "古老的神明需要在这片土地上被知晓！现在，把路让开！");
	text = text.replace("The kids press forth.", "孩子们向前挤去。");
	text = text.replace("A little banner flaps past you and there is much clinking and clanking of their little weapons, mostly bottles and sling shots and tableware.", "一条小旗帜从你身边飘过，他们的小武器叮当作响，主要是瓶子，弹弓和餐具。");
	text = text.replace("No doubt they are marching toward certain doom.", "毫无疑问他们在自取灭亡。");
	text = text.replace("Raiders and vagabonds are sure to prey upon them, like hawks upon lemmings, and slaves don\'t mind making ostensibly orphaned children \'disappear.\' Were they to get further than those threats, the northern wastes will provide for them a frozen coffin to die in.", "掠夺者和流浪汉会折磨他们，就像老鹰对老鼠那样，奴隶们也不介意让那些表面上是孤儿的孩子们“消失。”他们还面临更大的威胁，北方荒原将为他们提供一个冰冻的棺材，让他们在里面死去。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the monk steps forward and brings the children to a huddle\./, "$1 僧侣走上前，把孩子们拉到一起。");
	text = text.replace("They instantly respect the man, for he represents in part the very cause they wish to promote.", "他们立即尊重这个人，因为他在某种程度上代表了他们希望发扬的事业。");
	text = text.replace("He bends a knee.", "他屈膝。");
	text = text.replace("Was it the old gods who told you to come out and do this?", "是古老神明让你出来做这件事的吗？");
	text = text.replace("The little leader nods.", "小领袖点头。");
	text = text.replace("They spoke to me in my sleep.", "他们在我睡觉时对我说话。");
	text = text.replace("The monk nods back, rubbing his chin and mulling it over.", "僧侣也点了点头，摩挲着下巴沉思着。");
	text = text.replace("He pats the boy on his head.", "他拍了拍男孩的头。");
	text = text.replace("The old gods speak to me and I for them.", "古老的神明对我说话而我是他们的代言人。");
	text = text.replace("Interpreting their message requires years of study, let me tell ya!", "解读他们的信息需要多年的研究，让我告诉你！");
	text = text.replace("Are you certain that it was you, little one, that was meant to carry this burden?", "你确定那就是你，小家伙，注定要担起这个重担吗？");
	text = text.replace("Perhaps you were to be the messenger, no?", "也许你是来送信的，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("See us, we\'re warriors.", "看看我们，我们是勇士。");
	text = text.replace("Fit, fighting men who can kill those who despise and demark the old gods.", "合适的，战士能够杀死那些轻视和亵渎古老神明的人。");
	text = text.replace("You are not yet like us, but you have a strong voice and the command of a true leader yet.", "你现在还不能像我们这样，但是你已经拥有强大的话语权和真正领袖的担当。");
	text = text.replace("I believe the old gods wanted to use you for your charisma, not your muscles.", "我相信古老的神明想运用你的魅力，而不是你的肌肉。");
	text = text.replace("The monk gives the boy a playful push.", "僧侣顽皮地推了一下男孩。");
	text = text.replace("He smiles, realizing the truth of what the friar has to say.", "他笑了，意识到僧侣说的是实话。");
	text = text.replace("The little leader tells his party that they are to return home as the monk is assuredly right.", "小领袖告诉他的军队，他们要回家，因为僧侣肯定是对的。");
	text = text.replace("Some men are thankful that these kids were talked out of going to a certain doom.", "一些队员感到很欣慰，因为这些孩子被从真正的地狱里劝了回来。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) takes his boots off and show the bottom of his feet to the children\./, "$1 脱下靴子，向孩子们展示他的脚底板。");
	text = text.replace("They recoil, gagging and covering their mouths.", "他们向后退缩，作呕或捂住嘴巴。");
	text = text.replace("A little girl lets out a long \'ewww\' to really drive the point home.", "一个小女孩长长的发出“呕”的一声，真正地说明了这一点。");
	text = text.replace("The man wags his foot around, showing off disgustingly calloused skin.", "那人晃着脚，露出令人作呕的长满老茧的皮肤。");
	text = text.replace("I spent years on the road and most of them without a good shoe to step with.", "我在路上花了几年的时间，大部分时间都没有好的鞋可以穿。");
	text = text.replace("I know what it\'s like out there.", "我知道外面是什么样子。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve seen the dangers.", "我已经看到了危险。");
	text = text.replace("People stabbing one another in their sleep.", "人们趁对方睡着的时候捅刀子。");
	text = text.replace("Killing for a bite of a biscuit.", "为了一小口饼干杀人。");
	text = text.replace("Strangers befriend ya so they can betray ya.", "陌生人把你当朋友是为了以后出卖你。");
	text = text.replace("And all that is when it\'s going well!", "这些都算是好的！");
	text = text.replace("When it goes bad, it gets... well, it gets real bad.", "当变得不好的时候，那真是…好吧，那真是糟糕。");
	text = text.replace("You kids got no business being out here.", "你们这些孩子不该来这里。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ll be raped, murdered, enslaved, tortured, fed to dogs, eaten by boars, bears, wolves, all things that look at ya like it\'s lunchtime on two legs.", "你会被强奸、谋杀、奴役、折磨、喂狗、被野猪、熊、狼吃掉，所有这些都让你看起来就像在用两条腿吃午餐。");
	text = text.replace("Go home. The lot of you.", "回家吧，你们作够了。");
	text = text.replace("The band of children murmurs amongst themselves.", "那群孩子在他们中间窃窃私语。");
	text = text.replace("One announces he\'s going back to his mom.", "一个说他要回他妈妈那里去了。");
	text = text.replace("A little girl states that she didn\'t even want to be out here anyway and never got the treats she was promised.", "一个小女孩说她根本就不想出来，也从来没有得到过答应给她的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Sensing a morale break, the little leader tries to corral the children, but it\'s no use.", "感觉到士气受到了打击，小领袖尝试稳住这些孩子，但是没有用。");
	text = text.replace("The group breaks apart and, thankfully, starts going home.", "人群散开了，谢天谢地，他们开始回家了。");
	text = text.replace("Some of the men are relieved as they did not wish to see the little ones continue their doomed journey.", "有些队员松了一口气，因为他们不希望看到小家伙们继续他们地狱般的旅程。");
	text = text.replace("You doubt that you can talk the fervor out of these kids, but if your pop\'s parenting is anything to go by you can probably beat it out of them.", "你不相信你能说服这些孩子，但是如果你爸爸的教育方式可以作为参考的话，你很可能揍他们一顿。");
	text = text.replace("With a swift order, you have the company set upon the kids, knocking them around and taking their stuff.", "你迅速下了命令，让同伴们袭击孩子们，把他们打倒在地，拿走他们的东西。");
	text = text.replace("The little leader tries to spear a sellsword and gets cold cocked for his troubles.", "小领袖试图用长矛刺向佣兵，却因为自己惹麻烦而被打得鼻青鼻肿。");
	text = text.replace("This isn\'t the prettiest of things to do and it\'d look really bad if anyone saw the company beating up children, but this \'end\' to their crusade is preferable to the nastier sorts that await them on the road.", "这不是最好的解决方法，如果有人看到战队打孩子，那真是太糟糕了，但是这样“结束”他们的十字军远征远比他们在路上再遇麻烦要好。");

//cocky_challenges_player_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While joining the company at a campfire, (.*?) stands up and speaks with reddened face\./, "在篝火旁加入战队时，$1 站起来，满脸通红地说话。");
	text = text.replace("I don\'t know about the rest of you sad clods, but I think I could run this camp better than anyone!", "我不知道你们这些可怜虫怎么想，但我想我比任何人都能更好地管理这个队伍！");
	text = text.replace("Especially better than him!", "尤其是比他好！");
	text = text.replace("He points a finger at you.", "他用手指着你。");
	text = text.replace("You take a seat.", "你坐下吧。");
	text = text.replace("The men are staring at you, waiting for a response.", "人们盯着你,等待着你的回答。");
	text = text.replace("You kick your feet out, legs akimbo, and place your hands in your lap.", "你把脚伸前，两腿岔开，双手放在膝盖上。");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you speak to the man.", "点着头，你对那个人说话。");
	text = text.replace(/Alright, (.*?)\. You\'re the man now\./, "好吧，$1。你现在就是那个人。");
	text = text.replace("You gotta count inventory every morning and night.", "你每天早晚都要清点存货。");
	text = text.replace("I know you can\'t count for shite, but you\'ll learn.", "我知道你不是垃圾，但你要学。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t want these fine men going into battle a few arrows short.", "不要让这些优秀的战士上战场的时候少几支箭。");
	text = text.replace("You throw a hand out to a few of the tents.", "你向几个帐篷挥手。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ll also need to keep a steady count on your people.", "你还要对你的队员心里有数。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re not easily controlled, to which you might find some irony - or not.", "他们可不容易控制，你可能会发现有点讽刺－也许不。");
	text = text.replace("Looking at your hands, which have grown calloused and bruised over the days, you keep talking.", "看着你的手，这几天已经满是老茧和擦伤，你继续说。");
	text = text.replace("And you\'ll need to bark orders that aren\'t just there to be heard - but there to keep men alive and breathing.", "你需要发出号令，这不仅是为了让他们听到－也是为了让他们活着和呼吸。");
	text = text.replace("You know, like yourself and those who sit around you.", "你知道，就像你自己和坐在你身边的人。");
	text = text.replace(/So yeah, take the job, (.*?)\. It\'s yours\./, "所以，是的，接受这份工作，$1。它现在是你的。");
	text = text.replace(/As soon as you finish, a group of brothers immediately stands up and begs for you to remain in charge\. (.*?), seeing this, backs down and slinks away as yells of \'you\'re in charge!\' fill the air\./, "演讲一结束，一群兄弟立刻站起来请求你继续领导他们。$1，看到这一切，在“你来负责”的欢呼声中乖乖的退缩了。");
	text = text.replace("The campfire crackles an orange glow across your face.", "营火发出噼啪声，橘红色的火光映射在你脸上。");
	text = text.replace(/Nodding, you stand up and walk up to (.*?)\. He takes a step back, but not before you throw a hand out and grab him by the shoulder\./, "点着头，你站起来走向 $1。他向后退了一步，但你伸出手抓住了他的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("You quickly step forward, scissoring a leg back behind his knee, buckling him and throwing him onto his back.", "你迅速向前一步，把一条腿伸到他膝盖后面，别住他，向后摔倒了他。");
	text = text.replace("You follow him to the ground and there plant one hand around his throat while the other points an accusing finger.", "你跟着他倒在地上，一手掐住他的喉咙，一手伸出手指指责他。");
	text = text.replace(/You\'re a good man (.*?), but a stupid one, too\./, "你是个好人 $1，但也是个蠢人。");
	text = text.replace("Now, I see some of y\'all aren\'t happy about how things are going, but let me remind you that you are all still alive!", "现在，我看到你们中的一些人对事情的进展感到不高兴，但让我提醒你们，你们都还活着！");
	text = text.replace(/If someone like (.*?) was in charge you\'d all be dead in a fortnight!/, "如果有人像 $1 这样夺权，你们都会在两星期内死去！");
	text = text.replace(/Standing up, you actually help (.*?) to his feet\./, "站以来后，你也帮 $1 站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("He sneers at you and takes off, kicking a stack of barrels over as he leaves.", "他对你冷笑了一声，就离开了，离开时把一堆酒桶踢翻了。");
	text = text.replace("A wave of pain eminates from where the arrow hit you not long ago, but you clench your teeth and try not to give away anything as you sit down again.", "一波又一波的疼痛感从你不久前中箭的位置袭来，但当你再次坐下时，你咬紧牙关，尽量不放弃任何东西。");
	text = text.replace("You immediately jump back to your feet and begin shouting.", "你马上跳起来，开始大吼。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m the one in charge here! Me!", "我是这里的唯一领袖！我！");
	text = text.replace("Who has the money? Me!", "谁有钱？我！");
	text = text.replace("If it weren\'t for me, none of y\'all would even be here!", "如果不是我，你们甚至都不会在这里！");
	text = text.replace("You\'d still be in the pits of whatever old lives you had!", "不管你们以前过着怎样的生活，你们都会陷入困境！");
	text = text.replace("You should be groveling before my feet for the opportunities I have provided!", "你们应该在我的领导下，我会为你们找到机会！");
	text = text.replace(/And (.*?), if you contest me again I swear to the gods I will have you flogged and hanged, understand\?/, "而且 $1，如果你再敢和我较劲，我发誓我会用鞭子抽死你，明白吗？");
	text = text.replace(/The outburst instantly quiets the camp\. (.*?) nods and backs away\./, "这次爆发立即使整个营地安静下来。$1 点头，走掉了。");
	text = text.replace("A few of the men murmur between themselves as you take your seat again.", "在你重新坐下时，几个人在窃窃私语。");

//cocky_vs_iron_lungs_event.nut
	text = text.replace("As you roll up some maps and put them back in their panniers, a commotion draws you outside your tent.", "当你卷起一些地图并把它们放回包里时，一阵骚动使你离开了帐篷。");
	text = text.replace(/The men are dragging (.*?) across the ground\./, "这些队员正把 $1 拖拽在地面上。");
	text = text.replace("His clothes are sopping wet and his face one shade short of death.", "他的衣服都湿透了，他的面色看上去像要死了一样。");
	text = text.replace("The men give him some good slaps on the cheeks.", "队员们在他的脸颊上狠狠地打了几下。");
	text = text.replace("Eventually, he wakes up, eyes wild, mouth gargling water like a broken fountain.", "终于，他醒了，眼睛睁得大大的，嘴巴吐着水，就像一个破损的喷泉。");
	text = text.replace("He looks around and asks what you, too, wish to know.", "他环顾四周，询问你也想知道的事。");
	//text = text.replace("What happened?", "发生了什么？");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) walks over, a similarly wet visage, but with a far more colorful complexion\./, "$1 走了过来，同样是湿润的脸，但面色更加红润。");
	text = text.replace("You cocky cunt dared to see which of us could hold their breath the longest.", "你这个嚣张的婊子竟敢比试我们当中谁憋气最长。");
	text = text.replace("You lost because they don\'t call these the iron lungs for nuttin\'.", "你输了，因为他们不会无缘无故地把这些叫做铁肺。");
	text = text.replace(/The men have a laugh as (.*?) boastfully pounds his chest\. (.*?), still wobbly, gets to his feet\./, "队员们笑了起来，当 $1 正在骄傲地捶打者自己的胸膛。$2，仍然摇摇晃晃，站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("Mere moments after being completely unconscious, he\'s already back to his prideful ways.", "仅仅在完全失去知觉的片刻之后，他已经回到了他的高傲模式。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah yeah, you bested me this day, but I shall be the best, just you wait!", "是啊，是啊，你今天打败了我，但是我会是最好的，你等着吧！");
	text = text.replace("Another sellsword whimsically points out that the cocksure fella has a huge string of snot dangling from his nose.", "另一位佣兵异想天开地指出，这个自信满满的家伙鼻子上挂着一大串鼻涕。");
	text = text.replace("He confidently wipes it away despite the roaring laughter of the company.", "他满怀信心地把它擦去，尽管队伍里一阵爆笑。");

//combat_drill_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You step out of your tent to survey the men.", "你走出帐篷去观察那些人。");
	text = text.replace(/A great many of them are freshly hired grunts, nervously buddying up with one another or trying their hand at some of the weapons. (.*?) comes to your side\./, "他们中的许多人是新雇来的菜鸟，紧张不安地尝试结交新朋友或试着用手拿起武器。$1 来到你身边。");
	text = text.replace("I know what yer thinking.", "我知道你在想什么。");
	text = text.replace("Yer thinking you\'d just hired a bunch of meat for a thresher.", "你在想你刚刚雇了一堆小鲜肉来打谷子。");
	text = text.replace("How about I whip these boys into shape so they don\'t eat an orcish blade their first go in the field?", "我该怎么鞭策这些孩子靠谱一些，使他们在第一次上战场的时候不会吃到兽人的利刃？");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) tells the recruits to take up weapons\./, "$1 告诉新兵拿起武器。");
	text = text.replace("When every single one of them picks up a sword, the old guard yells at them, stating that not every foe hankering for you being graveyard dead is gonna be wielding the exact same blade.", "当他们每个人都拿起一把剑的时候，老兵对他们大吼，说不是每一个想让你死在墓地的敌人都会用同样的利刃。");
	text = text.replace("A few nod before hurriedly exchanging their swords for axes and spears.", "他们点了点头，然后匆匆地把剑换成了斧头和长矛。");
	text = text.replace("With the crew equipped, the training begins.", "队员们装备好后，训练就开始了。");
	text = text.replace(/Mostly, (.*?) teaches basics like how a formation makes it easier to defend not only one another, but also yourself\./, "大多数情况下，$1 教授一些基础知识，比如如何让一个阵形不仅能让你更容易地保护队友，还能让你更容易地保护自己。");
	text = text.replace("Ye need not watch corner-to-corner if ya know a brother is by yer side.", "你不需要注视每个角落，如果你的战友在你身边。");
	text = text.replace("But if yer separated, if yer all out there by yer lonesome, then ye might be proper farked lest ye got a heretofore unknown way with a blade which I\'ll go ahead and assume ye don\'t.", "但是，如果你们分开了，如果你们都在外面孤单地呆着，那你们就会被狠狠地揍一场，免得你们用一把刀走到一条未知的路上去，我会继续下去，假设你没有的话。");
	text = text.replace(/The training moves to offense where (.*?) shows a few tricks with various weapons\./, "训练内容变为进攻，$1 用各种武器展示一些技巧。");
	text = text.replace("With swords ye can slash, cut, stab, and riposte.", "用剑你可以砍，切，刺和还击。");
	text = text.replace("Proper-hard to miss with a sword, given every side of it is a killin\' side.", "不错－用剑很难失手，因为它的每一面都是致命的。");
	text = text.replace("If I see any of you trying to cut down an arrow with a sword like the fairy tales told ya I\'mma beat ya down myself.", "如果我看到你们中的任何一个想要用剑砍断一支箭，就像童话里告诉你们的那样，我会亲自揍你一顿的。");
	text = text.replace("It ain\'t true, so stop fancying it!", "这不是真的，所以别胡思乱想了！");
	text = text.replace("Spears are good for keeping distance.", "长矛很适合保持距离。");
	text = text.replace("They won\'t do much to armor, but they\'ll keep ya safe.", "它们不会让你的装甲更厚，但他们会让你更安全。");
	text = text.replace("Just point this sharp-end away from ya.", "把矛尖离自己远点。");
	text = text.replace("If an armored brute gets past this pointy end here then yer probably proper farked so don\'t let that happen.", "如果一个穿护甲的畜生通过了这尖尖的一端，那你可就惨了，所以不要让这种事情发生。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, there\'s the axe.", "最后，该说说斧子了。");
	text = text.replace("Just pretend the other man is a tree and cleave it so.", "只要假装对方是一棵树，然后把它劈成两半就行。");
	text = text.replace("Now let\'s practice!", "现在我们开始练习！");
	
	text = text.replace("The training goes fairly well from there, though the men do come out the other side with a few bumps and bruises.", "从那以后，训练进行得相当顺利，尽管队员们会让对方身上有一些磕碰和瘀伤。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) musters the men together and begins handing them training bows\./, "$1 集合队员，开始训练它们射箭。");
	text = text.replace("Now these ain\'t made for killing unless ye got an axe to grind with a newborn babe, which I\'m some of y\'all do, but for now we\'ll just use them to practice.", "这些不是用来杀人的，除非你拿到一把斧子去折磨一个新生儿，你们现在要按我说的做，这些只是用来练习。");
	text = text.replace("Here\'s how this contraption works.", "这是这个装置的工作原理。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, ye already know?", "噢，你们已经知道了？");
	text = text.replace("Yer not a bunch of fools?", "你们不是一群傻瓜吗？");
	text = text.replace("Well go ahead, then, show me what ye sharpshooters got.", "那好吧，让我看看你们这些神射手有什么本事。");
	
	text = text.replace(/The men take practiced shots downrange, the arrows peppering all around their targets, a scant few lucky ones going where they should\. (.*?) spends the rest of the day exhaustingly having the men shoot and shoot and shoot until luck is squeezed out of the equation altogether\./, "这些人在练习射击靶子，箭在他们的目标周围乱射，少数幸运的人射到了他们应该射的地方。$1 精疲力竭地指导队员们不停地射击，直到他们的运气完全消失为止。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) looses a sharp whistle, gathering the new recruits around him\./, "$1 吹响尖锐的口哨，把新兵召集在他周围。");
	text = text.replace("He looks around, grinning, then nods.", "他环顾四周，咧嘴一笑，然后点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Alright ye limpdick teatsucking noodlearm goatfarkers, we\'re going on a march!", "好了，你们这些笨蛋，乳臭未干的，娘娘腔，蠢货，我们会进行一场行军！");
	text = text.replace("The veteran spends the rest of the day ruthlessly running the recruits as far as he can until the last one drops from exhaustion.", "老兵把剩下的时间都花在无情地驱赶新兵上，直到最后一个人精疲力竭。");
	text = text.replace("Breathe, little babe, breathe! Take it all in.", "呼吸，小宝贝，呼吸！全收进去。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s plenty to go around for the rest of us, don\'t feel bad!", "我们有很多事要做，别难过！");
	text = text.replace("Swallow it like yer mother should\'ve swallowed you.", "就像你妈妈把你吞下去一样。");
	text = text.replace("Now, I\'ve shot stains that ran faster than the lot of ye, so I\'ll be seeing y\'all again tomorrow on good, proper time.", "现在，我己经找到污点了，就是我比你们许多人跑的都快，所以我明天一定会再见到你们的，时间有的是。");
	text = text.replace("That\'d be before the sun rises, shitsticks.", "那是太阳出来之前的事了，蠢货们。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) shows little mercy and has the men running again and again in the days to come\./, "$1 表现的毫无怜悯之心，让这些人在未来的日子里一次又一次奔跑。");
	text = text.replace("After all, he says, it\'s for their own damn good.", "毕竟，他说，这是为了他们自己。");

//come_across_burial_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While on the road, you come across a crowd of people huddled around a mound of earth.", "在路上，你遇到一群人围着一堆土。");
	text = text.replace("Getting closer, you realize that it\'s a funeral.", "走近一点，你发现这是一场葬礼。");
	text = text.replace("One of the attendees turns to look at you.", "一位与会者转向你。");
	text = text.replace("Did you know him?", "你认识他吗？");
	text = text.replace("Did you fight by his side?", "你在他身边打过仗吗？");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head and start cutting into the crowd to see the man himself.", "你摇摇头，开始挤进人群中去看那个人。");
	text = text.replace("You find a man looking about as old as the dead can look.", "你发现这个人的尸体像僵尸一样陈旧。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s got a terrifically sharp and glinting sword running along his chest with his grubby, wormfood fingers clutching the pommel\. (.*?) joins your side and whispers\./, "他的胸前有一把非常锋利闪闪发光的剑，脏兮兮的被虫蛀手指抓着剑柄。$1 来到你的身边耳语道。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s, uh, a pretty nice lookin\' weapon there, just saying.", "那是，呃，一个看起来很不错的武器，我就是说说。");
	
	text = text.replace("You draw out your sword and the rest of the company does the same.", "你拔出你的剑，其他队员也这么做了。");
	text = text.replace("The mercenaries push the crowd back, but there isn\'t as much resistance as you expected.", "雇佣兵们把人群往后推，但没有你想象的那么多阻碍。");
	text = text.replace("One of the attendees steps forward.", "一位与会者走上前。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s the sword you want, isn\'t it?", "这是你要的剑，是吗？");
	text = text.replace("Go on, take it.", "继续，拿去吧。");
	text = text.replace("That there dead man spoke of someone like you.", "那个死者提到了像你这样的人。");
	text = text.replace("Said you\'d need it more than he ever would.", "说你比他更需要这把剑。");
	text = text.replace("Sheathing your sword, you ask him if that\'s why they were all standing around. The man laughs.", "你举起剑，问他这是不是他们都站在周围的原因。那人笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("Naw, he also said he\'d never die, so we were curious to know if that part of his sayings would come true.", "不是的，他还说他永远不会死，所以我们很想知道他说的话是否会成真。");
	text = text.replace("You slowly take the sword, now curious if there was some saying about butchering the man who laid his hands upon it.", "你慢慢地拿起剑，现在很好奇是否有人说过要杀掉把手按在剑上的那个人。");
	text = text.replace("Thankfully, ostensibly, the mighty dead man said no such thing.", "谢天谢地，从表面上看，这个伟大的死人并没有说这样的话。");
	
	text = text.replace("You reach through the crowd and grab the dead man\'s sword.", "你穿过人群，抓起死者的剑。");
	text = text.replace(/One of the attendees screams out\. (.*?) uncorks a punch and sends the peasant astral planing\./, "一名与会者尖叫起来。$1 打开酒瓶塞，把泡沫喷到一个农民脸上。");

	text = text.replace("The rest of the company draw out their weapons to make sure any further protests don\'t get far.", "战队的其他成员拿出了他们的武器，以确保任何进一步的抗议不会发生。");
	text = text.replace("An elderly woman cuts through the crowd as well as an elderly woman can, wobbling and shaking.", "一位上了年纪的妇女从人群中穿过，像老妇人一样，摇摇晃晃的。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, that don\'t belong to you. Put it back.", "先生，那不属于你。还给我们。");
	
	text = text.replace("You tell the old lady to crawl her crotchety ass into a hole and die there.", "你告诉老太太把她那古怪的屁股钻到洞里去然后去死。");
	text = text.replace(/The dead man\'s sword is put in with your inventory and the (.*?) get back on the road\./, "死者的剑进了你的仓库 $1 回到了道路上。");
	text = text.replace("Upset, the peasants cry out that word of what you\'d done would travel the winds like the shitting farts of a thousand cows.", "农民们心烦意乱的叫喊着，说你所做的事将会在风中传播，就像一千头牛在拉屎放屁一样。");
	text = text.replace("You simply laugh and appreciate their imaginativeness.", "你只是大笑，很欣赏他们的想象力。");
	
	text = text.replace("You put the sword back into the dead man\'s hands.", "你把剑放回死者的手里。");
	text = text.replace("The old lady nods.", "老太太点头。");
	text = text.replace("So there are good men who will still listen to the wise.", "所以你们是能够听从良言的好人。");
	text = text.replace("Another peasant hails your honor and others follow suit.", "另一个农民为你的荣誉欢呼，其他人也纷纷效仿。");
	text = text.replace("It appears that simply taking the weapon and then putting it back was enough to warrant a manner of celebratory prestige in the eyes of the laymen.", "在这帮世俗之人看来，仅仅拿走武器再放回去，就足以成为一种值得庆祝的义举。");
	text = text.replace("Perhaps you should feign theft more often.", "也许你应该经常假装偷窃。");

//come_across_ritual_event.nut
	text = text.replace("It\'s not a rare sight to find a dead body on your journey.", "在你的旅途中发现一具尸体并不罕见。");
	text = text.replace(/This one, though, is rather unusual\. (.*?) takes a long look\./, "然而，这一次却不同寻常。$1 看了很久。");
	text = text.replace("What\'s that on his chest?", "他胸前的是什么？");
	text = text.replace("You crouch down and throw back the corpse\'s shirt.", "你蹲下来，把尸体的衬衫扔回去。");
	text = text.replace(/Scars run lengthwise all about his body, drawn in very familiar shapes: forests, rivers, mountains\. (.*?) walks up\./, "他全身的伤疤都是纵向的，排列的形状很熟悉：森林，河流，山脉。$1 走上前。");
	text = text.replace("Ain\'t that a sight.", "这不是一道风景么。");
	text = text.replace("Wolves do that or something?", "是狼干的还是其他什么东西？");
	text = text.replace("You stand back up.", "你站起来。");
	text = text.replace("I think he did it to himself.", "我想是他自己干的。");
	text = text.replace("Bloody footprints lead away from the scene...", "血淋淋的脚印致使我离开现场…");
	
	text = text.replace("As you follow the foosteps, you begin to hear the murmurs of a chant.", "当你跟着脚印走的时候，你开始听到低声吟唱的声音。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the company to rest while you sneak forward, eventually finding a large bonfire with cloaked men circling around it.", "你告诉队员们在你偷偷前进的时候休息一下，最后发现一大堆篝火，附近围绕着穿着斗篷的人。");
	text = text.replace("They stomp their feet and throw their hands up, shouting some token words to their elder god, Davkul.", "他们跺着脚，举起双手，对他们的古老神明达库尔喊着象征性的话。");
	text = text.replace(/It\'s a bestial ceremony, roaring and growling abound, and the men dance about with their oversized clothes like darkly spirits still angry at the world they\'d departed\. (.*?) crawls up beside you and shakes his head\./, "这是一场野蛮的仪式，到处是咆哮和吼叫声，人们穿着超大号的衣服跳舞，如同黑暗的灵魂的怒火，对于这个已经被他们抛弃的世界。$1 爬到你身边，摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Just what is going on down there?", "刚刚下面到底发生了什么事？");
	text = text.replace("What should we do?", "我们该怎么办？");
	
	text = text.replace("You decide to wait it out and see what happens.", "你决定等待看看会发生什么。");
	text = text.replace("Just as you say that, the cultists drag an old man before the fire.", "就像你刚才说的，异教徒们把一个老人拖到火前。");
	text = text.replace("He bows his head before the flames, opens his arms, and then falls in.", "他在火焰前低下头，张开双臂，然后跳了进去。");
	text = text.replace("There are no screams.", "并没有尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("Another man is pulled forward.", "另一个人被拉上前。");
	text = text.replace("He whispers words to a cultist, they both nod, and so too this man puts himself to the flame.", "他对一个异教徒低声耳语，他俩都点头，所以这个人也把自己置身在火焰中。");
	text = text.replace("A third is pushed forth, but unlike the others he is shackled and wild-eyed.", "第三个人被推出去了，但与其他的人不同的是，他被束缚着，眼睛睁得大大的。");
	text = text.replace("He screams at the cultists.", "他对着异教徒们尖叫。");
	text = text.replace("Fark your god, he means nothing!", "我操你们的神，他狗屁不是！");
	text = text.replace("It\'s all a lie!", "他就是个骗子！");
	text = text.replace("A face appears in the flames, its shape bulbous and churning in the smoke and fire.", "一张脸呈现在火焰中，它的形状是球状的，在烟和火中翻腾。");
	text = text.replace("It is cruelty embodied, and could be no better painted by flames than by darkness itself.", "他是残酷的化身，火焰和黑暗本身都不能更好地描绘它。");
	text = text.replace("It turns and grins.", "它转身着咧嘴一笑。");
	text = text.replace("One of the cultist shouts.", "其中一个异教徒大喊。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul awaits you!", "达库尔即将降临到你！");
	text = text.replace("But the prisoner kicks one of his imprisoners and tries to make a run for it.", "但是这个囚犯踢了其中一个看守他的人，试图逃跑。");
	
	text = text.replace("You decide to wait and see what happens.", "你决定等待看看会发生什么。");
	text = text.replace("The bonfire\'s face returns, a great magmatic maw opening up as the chained man is pushed forward.", "篝火的脸转了回来，当这个犯人被推向前的时候，一个巨大的岩浆巨口张开了。");
	text = text.replace("He screams and bends backward, but it\'s no use.", "他尖叫着向后弯腰，但是没有用。");
	text = text.replace("His clothes burn away and the tatters fly backward in flailing orange ruin.", "他的衣服被烧光了，成了一堆橘红色的碎片向后飞扬。");
	text = text.replace("His skin peels as though it were not fire, but a thousand scalpels running across his body.", "他的皮肤开始剥落了，好像不是火干的，而是无数的手术刀在他身上划过。");
	text = text.replace("By sharpened white fire he is flayed.", "他被锋利的白色火焰剥皮了。");
	text = text.replace("His skull is bored out, wriggling and shaking like a snake shedding its skin, and his eyes remain forever seeing though the rest of his body is stripped away by flesh and organs and bones.", "他的头盖骨露了出来，像蛇蜕皮一样蠕动和颤抖。他的眼睛却永远保留着，看着身体的其他部分被剥去，肉，器官和骨头。");
	text = text.replace("When he is but a skull with eyes, the face in the fire closes its mouth and the great howls of the sacrifice come to a snapping silence.", "当他只是一个有眼睛的骷髅时，篝火中的那张脸闭上了嘴，献祭中的巨大哀嚎声一时间沉寂了下来。");
	text = text.replace("The bonfire dies out in an instant, and the man, or what\'s left of him, falls to the earth.", "篝火在一瞬间熄灭了，那个人，或者说他剩下的东西，掉在了地上。");
	text = text.replace("The eyes burn bright, slowly fading like a cooling hot iron.", "那双眼睛里燃烧着明亮的光芒，像滚烫的烙铁一样慢慢消失。");
	text = text.replace("One of the cultists bends down and picks up the skull.", "一个异教徒弯下腰捡起了那个头骨。");
	text = text.replace("He easily cracks it in half, dropping the brainpan while holding onto what used to be a face.", "他轻松把他掰成两半，把这个曾经是一张脸的东西翻转过来，脑壳朝上。");
	text = text.replace("As he holds the remains outward, the bones blacken and invert, creating a cruel visage of utter darkness wreathed by a rim of bone.", "当他把头骨拿向外时，骨头变黑了并倒转过来，形成了一个被一圈骨头环绕着的黑暗残酷面孔。");
	text = text.replace("He puts it on and begins to leave.", "他把他带在头上，开始离开。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You ask (.*?) if he can do anything\./, "你问 $1 他是否能做些什么。");
	text = text.replace("He simply walks past you and down the hill.", "他只是从你身边走过，然后下山。");
	text = text.replace("The group of cultists turn and look to him.", "异教徒们转过身来看着他。");
	text = text.replace("He walks through the crowd to the prisoner.", "他穿过人群走向囚犯。");
	text = text.replace("They talk. He whispers, the prisoner nods.", "他们谈话。他低声耳语，囚犯点头。");
	text = text.replace(/When they finish, the (.*?) nods to the crowd of cultists\./, "当他们谈话结束，$1 向这群异教徒们点头。");
	text = text.replace("One member steps forward, disrobes, and pitches himself into the fire, screamless and without protest.", "一个成员走上前，脱下衣服，把自己扔进火里，没有尖叫，也没有抗议。");
	text = text.replace(/Another cultist pitches a rake into the flames, tearing something out of it and handing it over to (.*?)\. The prisoner, his life ostensibly spared in an exchange, is freed and you watch as (.*?) grabs him and takes him back up the hill\./, "另一个异教徒把耙子伸进火焰里，把什么东西从火焰里扯出来，交给 $1。这个囚犯，他的生命表面上在一场交换中幸免了，被释放了并且你看到 $2 抓着他，把他带回到山上。");
	text = text.replace("He pushes the man forward as he speaks.", "他说话时把这个男人推向前。");
	text = text.replace("You have taken from Davkul, but the debt is paid.", "你已经被从达库尔身边带走了，但你欠达库尔的已经支付了。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what it is he has in his hand.", "你问他手里拿的是什么东西。");
	text = text.replace("The cultist holds up what had been retrieved from the flames.", "异教徒举起从火焰中捡回来的东西。");
	text = text.replace("It is a skull patched over in leathered flesh, and stretched taut over its face is a freshly singed visage, presumably of the man who had tossed himself into the fire.", "那是一个用人品遮盖的头盖骨，紧绷在脸上的是一张新烧焦的脸，大概是那个把自己扔进火里的人的脸。");
	text = text.replace("Slight hints of his face twist and turn, his mouth wringed ajar, misshapen by a cruel and murmuring darkness.", "这张脸轻微地扭曲着，嘴巴半掩着，残酷的黑暗使他看上去奇丑无比。");
	text = text.replace(/Still holding it aloft like a native showing off a prized scalp, (.*?) speaks bluntly\./, "仍然高举着它，像一个土著人炫耀珍贵的头皮，$1 直言不讳。");
	//text = text.replace("Davkul awaits us all.", "达库尔即将降临到我们。");
	
	text = text.replace("You give the order to attack.", "你下令进攻。");
	text = text.replace("Your men arm themselves and rush forward.", "你的人武装起来向前冲去。");
	text = text.replace("The fire dies in an instant, swirling down to nothing but ash which plumes out in a great cloud.", "火瞬间就熄灭了，只剩下滚滚浓烟中的灰烬。");
	text = text.replace("Once it is gone, the eerie crowd opens their arms and speak in unison.", "旦它消失了，诡异的人群张开双臂，异口同声地说道。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul awaits. Come and greet him.", "达库尔即将降临。让我们来迎接他。");
	
	text = text.replace("You won\'t stand for this injustice and decide to charge and save the man.", "你不会容忍这种不公正的行为并决定冲锋去救那个人。");
	text = text.replace("As you stand and raise your sword to give the order, the bonfire whips forth a great magmatic tentacle that grabs the chained man and yanks him into the flames.", "当你站起来举起你的剑下达命令时，篝火喷出一只巨大的岩浆触手，抓住被锁住的人，把他拖进火焰里。");
	text = text.replace("There is but the briefest of screams and then he\'s gone.", "只有很短的尖叫声，然后他就不见了。");
	text = text.replace("The fire condenses into a pillar that quickly collapses.", "大火凝聚成一根柱子，很快就倒塌了。");
	text = text.replace("A plume of ash explodes outward.", "一缕灰烬向外飘散。");
	text = text.replace("The man is gone and it is as if there was no fire at all.", "那个人不见了，就好像根本没有火一样。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s not even smoke in the sky.", "天空中甚至没有烟。");
	text = text.replace("The cultists turn to you and point and speak in unison.", "这些异教徒转向你，指着你异口同声说道。");
	text = text.replace("Bring death, yours or ours, for Davkul awaits us all.", "带来死亡，你们的或者我们的，达库尔即将降临到我们。");
	text = text.replace("You waiver a moment, then give the order to charge.", "你震惊了一会儿，然后下令冲锋。");

//cow_tipping_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While on the march, you come across a lone cow standing in a field.", "行军途中，你遇到一头孤独的奶牛站在田野里。");
	text = text.replace("Not much to it: it\'s just a cow.", "没啥大不了的：它就是一头牛。");
	text = text.replace(/But then (.*?) sidles up next to you\./, "但这时 $1 悄悄靠近你。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s gnawing on some broomstraw and twists it around as he talks.", "他说话时对扫把又咬又扭。");
	text = text.replace("So who do you think can do it?", "你认为谁能做到？");
	text = text.replace("You ask \'do what.\' He smiles.", "你问做什么。他笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Aw, sorry cap\'. Didn\'t realize you hadn\'t heard.", "啊，抱歉。我不知道你没有听说。");
	text = text.replace("We\'re gonna see if someone can knock that cow over!", "我们要看看是否有人能把那头牛撞倒！");
	text = text.replace("Say, seeing as how we can only knock it over once, how about you choose which of us has a go?", "比如说，假如我们只能撞它一次，你来选择我们中的某一个试试怎么样？");
	
	text = text.replace("You tell the men to sort it out themselves.", "你告诉队员们自己选出一个人。");
	text = text.replace(/They quickly choose (.*?) who, after some badgering, agrees to give it a go\./, "他们很快就选择了 $1 这位在一番纠缠之后同意试一试的人。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword carefully steps across the field, trying his best to avoid the cow patties.", "佣兵小心地走过田野，尽量避开牛粪。");
	text = text.replace("The cow itself nonchalantly looks over.", "奶牛满不在乎地看着他。");
	text = text.replace("It moos once before returning its short bovine attention to the grass.", "它先哞哞叫一次，然后短暂地把注意力放回草地上。");
	text = text.replace(/Snickering, the men shoo (.*?) onward, mouthing \'do it!\' and \'what are you waiting for\?\' Finally, standing a few feet from the cow, (.*?) charges\./, "队员们窃笑着，向前嘘着 $1，做着鬼脸说“上啊！”或“你还在等什么？”最后，站在离奶牛几英尺远的地方，$2 冲锋了。");
	//text = text.replace("Yaaahh!", "哇呀呀！");
	text = text.replace("He storms into the cow\'s side and he might as well have run into a house: his feet slip out from beneath him and he goes skidding beneath the animal, a glide well-oiled by fresh shit.", "他一头冲向奶牛的肚子，简直就像跑进了一间房子：他的脚从身体下面滑出来，他在母牛的肚子下面打滑，摔了一跤，新鲜的牛粪给他上了一层油。");
	text = text.replace("The company bursts out laughing.", "大家哄堂大笑。");
	text = text.replace("You can\'t tip a cow ya fool!", "你不能给牛小费你个傻瓜！");
	text = text.replace("They\'re too goddam heavy!", "它们太重了！");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) no doubt has a new beef with these jokers, but his \'sacrifice\' was worth the easy entertainment\./, "$1 毫无疑问成为这帮家伙的新笑料，不过他的“牺牲”还是值得的。");
	
	text = text.replace("You tell the men to sort it out themselves.", "你告诉他们自己选一个人。");
	text = text.replace(/They quickly choose (.*?)\. The sellsword carefully steps across the field, trying his best to avoid the cow patties\./, "他们很快选择了 $1。佣兵小心翼翼地走过田野，尽量避开牛粪。");
	text = text.replace("The cow itself nonchalantly looks over and moos once before returning its attention to the grass.", "奶牛自己则若无其事地看了看四周，然后哞了一声，然后又把注意力转移到草上。");
	text = text.replace(/Snickering, the men shoo (.*?) onward, mouthing \'do it!\' and \'hurry now!\'\./, "队员们窃笑着，向前嘘着 $1，做着鬼脸说“上啊！”和“快点！”。");
	text = text.replace(/Finally, standing a few feet from the cow, (.*?) charges forward\./, "最后，站在离牛几英尺的地方，$1 向前冲去。");
	//text = text.replace("Yaaahh!", "哇呀呀！");
	text = text.replace("The scream spooks the cow.", "他的尖叫吓到了牛。");
	text = text.replace(/She dips her withers and kicks, catching (.*?) with a bit of hooved heel\./, "牛沉下肩蹄子刨地，用沉重的后蹄追逐着 $1。");
	text = text.replace("He violently spins on his feet and twists right into the grass.", "他拼命地挪动着双脚，在草地上转来转去。");
	text = text.replace("The men laugh for a moment, then realize it\'s serious.", "队员们笑了一会儿，然后意识到问题很严重。");
	text = text.replace("As the cow moos and trots away, the sellsword is \'rescued.\' Though badly hurt, he\'ll survive this near-bovine homicide.", "当牛哞哞叫着跑开时，佣兵获救了。虽然伤得很重，他还是幸免于这场牛蹄边缘的杀戮。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You figure the strong and burly (.*?) could give the cow a good tipping/, "你认为强壮而魁梧的 $1 会给奶牛很好的上一课。");
	text = text.replace(/Your awkward wording alone has the men laughing, but (.*?) respectfully bows\./, "你笨拙的措辞引得队员们哈哈大笑，但是 $1 却毕恭毕敬地鞠了一躬。");
	text = text.replace("I am honored, sir.", "我很荣幸，先生。");
	text = text.replace("He rolls up his sleeves and strolls across the field, striding over cow patties like a merchant stepping over the homeless.", "他卷起袖子，在田野里踱来踱去，跨过牛粪，就像一个商人跨过无家可归的人。");
	text = text.replace(/The cow looks over, raising a curious eyebrow. (.*?) nods\./, "奶牛看了看，好奇地扬了扬眉毛。$1 点头。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s right, I\'m coming.", "就是这样，我来了。");
	text = text.replace("More phrasing issues abound.", "更多的措辞问题比比皆是。");
	text = text.replace(/Despite the laughter of the company, (.*?) charges the cow\./, "不理会嘲笑他的队员们，$1 冲向了奶牛。");
	text = text.replace("At first, he simply presses against its side, muscled and heaving with breath.", "起初，他只是简单地按压它的侧面，青筋暴起，呼吸急促。");
	text = text.replace("The men laugh as his efforts get him nowhere, but they quickly quiet down when the cow slides across the mud and grass.", "队员们嘲笑他的努力是徒劳的，但是当奶牛徐徐穿过泥地和草地时，他们很快就安静下来了。");
	text = text.replace(/With a mighty roar, (.*?) surges forward and the cow goes falling sideways with a confused moo\./, "伴随着一声巨大的轰鸣，$1 向前猛冲，而那头牛则一头栽到一边，发出一阵疑惑的哞哞声。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) stands there, slackjawed\./, "$1 站在那里，目瞪口呆。");
	text = text.replace("It was a joke...", "这是个笑话…");
	text = text.replace("I didn\'t think it was actually possible...", "我认为这在现实中是不可能的…");
	text = text.replace("The company erupts in cheers for the strong man\'s incredible feat!", "队伍里爆发出一阵欢呼声，为这个强壮男子的惊人壮举而喝彩！");
	
	text = text.replace(/Before you can even finish your sentence, (.*?) beats his chest and steps forward\./, "还没等你说完，$1 就拍着胸脯向前走了一步。");
	text = text.replace("I will fell that petty cow!", "我要打倒那头小母牛！");
	text = text.replace("You remind him that the company has no beef with the bovine creature and that this is all for fun and games.", "你提醒他战队和奶牛没有任何关系，这只是为了好玩和游戏。");
	text = text.replace("He stands there, arms tent-poled with his fists at his hips.", "他站在那里，双臂隆起肌肉双拳击打屁股。");
	text = text.replace("Nonsense. The company laughs and thinks this an impossibility, but I\'m here to show them all just how wrong they are!", "无稽之谈。队友们嘲笑我认为这是不可能的，但是我在这里要让他们知道他们是多么的错误！");
	text = text.replace("The cocksure sellsword steps into the field and immediately cuts his boot across a cow patty.", "那个自信满满的佣兵一脚跨进地里，立刻就踩到了一块牛粪饼。");
	text = text.replace("He sidewinders forward, arms flailing for balance, but it\'s all for naught as he slams to the ground.", "他侧着身子向前走，为了保持平衡而挥舞着双臂，但当他重重地摔在地上时，这一切都化为乌有。");
	text = text.replace("The men burst into laughter.", "队员们哄堂大笑起来。");
	text = text.replace(/The cow glances over before simply walking off\. (.*?) cleans himself up\./, "这头奶牛只是瞥了一眼就走开了。$1 把自己弄干净后站起来。");
	text = text.replace("A minor misstep. But look!", "一个小小的失误。但是，看吧！");
	text = text.replace("The cowardly cattle wants no part of me!", "这个懦弱的畜生根本不敢与我一战！");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) laughs and points at the sellsword\'s stained garb\./, "$1 大笑并指着他的脏衣服。");
	text = text.replace("Maybe, but it looks like you got a little part of her.", "也许吧，你对它还有那么点胜算。");
	text = text.replace("The cocky sellsword quickly swipes the shite off his shirt.", "这个嚣张的佣兵马上擦去衣服上的牛屎。");
	text = text.replace("Despite the failure, he is undeterred and the men are almost passing out they\'re laughing so hard.", "尽管失败了，但他没有被吓倒，队员们几乎要晕过去了，因为他们笑的太多了。");

//creepy_guy_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While walking the streets of (.*?), you come upon a crowd standing around a hanged man\./, "当你走在 $1 的街道上时，你看到一群人围着一个被绞死的人。");
	text = text.replace("He must have been of some notoriety: the folks are muscling one another to try and get a turn to cut a toe or finger off as a sort of hanging-heirloom.", "他一定是出了什么名：人们互相推搡，试图轮流把一个脚趾或手指割下来，作为一种值得悬挂的传家之宝。");
	text = text.replace("An old man is quickly elbowed out of the mob.", "一个老人很快被挤出了人群。");
	text = text.replace("He turns to you, voice raspy, his bony fingers tented like sickly ribs.", "他转向你，声音沙哑，瘦骨嶙峋的手指像烂排骨一样耷拉着。");
	text = text.replace("Ahh, sellsword are ye?", "啊，你们是佣兵？");
	text = text.replace("O\'course, I can smell your business, the purchases ye have made.", "当然，我能嗅出你的斤两，你的生意来了。");
	text = text.replace("Say, would you do a bit of work for me?", "喂，你能帮我做点事么？");
	text = text.replace("I need a number of that dead man\'s fingers and toes.", "我需要那个死人的一些手指和脚趾。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s for m\'work, ye shall see.", "这是我给你的工作，你应该明白。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll give you five hundred crowns in return for it.", "我会给你五百克朗作为报酬。");
	text = text.replace("You ask why he needs that particular man\'s appendages.", "你问他为什么需要那个特殊男人的附属肢体。");
	text = text.replace("The crooning, shoulder-cowed man laughs, a heckle if there ever was one.", "这个语调低沉，肩膀蜷缩着的男人笑了，发出一阵前所未闻的诘问。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, good question. The man earned his walk to the hangman\'s noose with a penchant for violence and an unerring strength to see his desires through.", "问得好。这个人赢得了走向刽子手绞索的机会，因为他有暴力倾向和一种能看穿自己欲望的强大能力。");
	text = text.replace("The toes and fingers of a simpleton won\'t do. I need a man of uncinched cruelty, and the only one I see right now is swinging by that there rope.", "一个傻瓜的脚趾和手指是不行的。我需要一个不受约束的残忍之人，而我现在看到的唯一的人正被那根绳子吊着。");
	text = text.replace("So, what say ye?", "所以，你们有啥要说的？");
	text = text.replace("Five hundred crowns, remember?", "五百克朗，记得么？");
	
	text = text.replace("You muscle your way into the crowd, looking for fingers and toes or bloodied pockets.", "你挤进人群，寻找手指，脚趾或血迹斑斑的口袋。");
	text = text.replace("One man\'s got a good, lumpy sag in his pocket.", "一个男人已经拿到了好处，他的口袋呈现块状凹陷的形状。");
	text = text.replace("You drive him into a corner and shake him down with a dagger to his throat.", "你把他逼到一个角落里，用匕首抵住他的喉咙来勒索他。");
	text = text.replace("After him, you see a woman with a sickly grin on her face prancing along the cobbled stones.", "在他后面，你看到一个脸上带着病态笑容的女人在鹅卵石上蹦蹦跳跳。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s a scornful wench if you\'ve ever seen one.", "那是个轻蔑的少妇，如果你曾见识过的话。");
	text = text.replace("Pulling her aside, you quickly find the a finger and a toe in the linens of her frock.", "把她拉到一边，你很快就能在她的亚麻布衣服里找到一根手指和一个脚趾。");
	text = text.replace("She lies and says they\'re just cooking ingredients.", "她撒谎说他们只是在做食材。");
	text = text.replace("You tell her if that\'s the case then you\'ll report her to the guards for cannibalism.", "你告诉她如果是这样的话你就去向守卫报告他们吃人肉。");
	text = text.replace("She gives them up.", "她放弃了它们。");
	text = text.replace("Returning the grossly extremities to the old man, you are promptly paid the five hundred crowns.", "把残肢还给老人，你马上就得到五百克朗。");
	text = text.replace("He hardly even thanks you for your \'work\' before rushing away.", "他甚至都不感谢你的“工作”，就匆匆离开了。");
	text = text.replace("He never did explain what, exactly, such things were for.", "他从来没有解释过，确切地说，这些东西是用来干什么的。");
	text = text.replace("You don\'t care. Five hundred crowns is five hundred crowns.", "你不在乎。因为五百克朗是实打实的。");
	
	text = text.replace("You agree to the creepy old man\'s task and start going through the crowd, keeping a careful eye out for toes and fingers being where they shouldn\'t be, or lumpy pockets freshly and redly wet.", "你同意了这个令人毛骨悚然的老人的任务，开始在人群中穿行，注意脚趾和手指是否在不该在的地方，或者又红又湿的块状物口袋。");
	text = text.replace("It doesn\'t take long: a woman prances down the road, the front of her frock bubbling rather curiously with whatever she\'s got in the pocket.", "没过多久：一个女人在路上蹦蹦跳跳，她的连衣裙前面冒着气泡，相当奇怪的是他的口袋里到底有什么。");
	text = text.replace("You pull her into an alleyway, drawing a dagger to keep her quiet.", "你把她拉到小巷里，拔出匕首让她安静下来。");
	text = text.replace("A finger and toe are found.", "一个手指和脚趾被发现了。");
	text = text.replace("As you go to take them, a man suddenly tackles you from behind.", "当你去拿他们的时候，一个男人突然从后面截住了你。");
	text = text.replace("Crowns from your purse and the appendages go skittering across the cobblestones.", "你钱包里的克朗和附属品在鹅卵石上乱滚。");
	text = text.replace("A child takes one, a rat the other, where either runs off to is quickly obscured by a frenzy of peasants going after your coins.", "一个孩子拿走了一个，一只老鼠叼走了另一个，他们很快逃得不知所踪因为一群农民在疯狂追逐你掉落的硬币。");
	text = text.replace("The man who tackled you loads up a punch.", "那个拦住你的男人给了你一拳。");
	text = text.replace("Sumbitch, you want her you gotta pay!", "婊子养的，你想要她你就得付钱！");
	text = text.replace("You cross your arms, block the strike, and twist your body to put him on the ground.", "你交叉双臂，格挡他的攻击，扭动身体把他撂倒在地上。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s about to say something else, but you momentarily replace his teeth with your knuckles and he goes quiet.", "他正要说些别的话，但你马上用你的指关节代替他的牙齿，他就安静下来了。");
	text = text.replace("Unfortunately, you won\'t be able to finish what you started and you\'ve lost a few coins in the process.", "不幸的是，你无法完成你开始的工作，而且你在这个过程中丢失了一些硬币。");
	
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) laughs\./, "$1 笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Hell, this\'ll be easy.", "见鬼，这很容易。");
	text = text.replace("He goes off to the crowd and you lose sight of him in an instant.", "他走到人群中，你立刻就看不见他了。");
	text = text.replace("The old man chews on his gums for awhile before raising his voice.", "老人在提高嗓门前咬了咬牙。");
	text = text.replace("This feller, he is one to trust?", "这个家伙，他值得信任么？");
	text = text.replace(/Before you can answer, (.*?) emerges from behind the old man\'s shoulder and drops a bloody bandage into his palms\./, "你还没来得及回答，$1 就从就从老人的肩膀后面冒出来，把一条血淋淋的绷带扔到他的手掌上。");
	text = text.replace("The creepy man unwraps the linens to discover freshly strewn extremities.", "这个令人毛骨悚然的人打开亚麻布，发现新鲜的散落的四肢。");
	text = text.replace("The thief smugly smiles.", "小偷沾沾自喜地笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Any thief worth his salt learns to pickpocket before anything else.", "任何值得一提的小偷都是先学会扒窃，然后才是其他事情。");
	text = text.replace("I usually go after keys instead of toes, but a job is a job.", "我通常追求的是钥匙而不是脚趾，但是工作就是工作。");
	text = text.replace("Also \'picked\' some other things of interest here and there. Take a look.", "我还四处“挑选”了一些其他有趣的东西。瞅瞅啊。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the minstrel grabs the old man by his shoulders\./, "$1 这个吟游诗人抓住老人的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("Say, what mighty muscles you seem to have, my burly friend.", "说吧，你有多少肌肉啊，我强壮的朋友。");
	text = text.replace("I shan\'t ask why you need the toes and fingers of that dead man...", "我不想问你为什么需要那个死人的脚趾和手指…");
	text = text.replace("The old man nods and says he\'d never tell anyway. The minstrel continues.", "老人点头说他无论如何也不会说。吟游诗人继续道。");
	text = text.replace("...but if you want a good, strong, and violent man, then am I not looking at it?", "…是如果你想要一个好的，强壮的，暴力的男人，难道不看看我么？");
	text = text.replace("It\'s you, old man!", "是你，老头子！");
	text = text.replace("Take yer own fingers and toes and go with them to complete the task - ahem, whatever weird shite that might be, ahem - and you\'ll find the \'reward\' you\'re after.", "带上你自己的手指和脚趾，和它们一起去完成任务－啊哼，不管是什么奇怪的狗屎，啊哼－你会找到你想要的奖品。");
	text = text.replace("You are the hero of this story, can\'t you see?", "你是这个故事的主人公，你看不出来吗？");
	text = text.replace("The old man spits and shakes his head.", "老人吐唾沫摇摇头。");
	text = text.replace("You take me for a fool, don\'t ya?", "你把我当个傻瓜，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("Our business here is through!", "我们的生意结束了！");
	text = text.replace("Get out of my way you sorry sellswords.", "别挡我的路，你们这帮该感到羞愧的佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("The old man leaves.", "老人走了。");
	text = text.replace("You ask the minstrel what the hell he\'s doing.", "你问吟游诗人他在干什么。");
	text = text.replace("He shrugs and holds up a purse of crowns.", "他耸耸肩，举起了一个装着克朗的钱袋。");
	text = text.replace("Sleight of hand.", "露了一手。");
	text = text.replace(/Nicely done\. But you ask where your own purse is\. (.*?) raises another sack\./, "干的漂亮。但是你询问你自己的钱包哪去了。$1 又举起了一个袋子。");
	text = text.replace("Really, really good sleight of hand.", "真的，真的好好的露了一手。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the butcher spits and says he\'ll do it\./, "$1 这个屠夫吐口水说他会做的。");
	text = text.replace("You tell him that he\'s not exactly the thieving sort.", "你告诉他他不是那种擅长偷东西的人。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Naw. I mean I\'ll give him a finger.", "不，我说我将会给他一个手指。");
	text = text.replace("Just one, but it\'ll be a doozy and worth its weight in gold as far as this old fart\'s concerned.", "只有一个，但对这个老家伙而言，它将是一个愚蠢的东西并且值得用金子来衡量。");
	text = text.replace("As far as you\'re concerned, captain, I want half the reward.", "对你而言，队长，我想要一半的酬劳。");
	text = text.replace("The creepy stranger nods as a smile crackles his dried, flaky skin.", "这个令人毛骨悚然的陌生人点头，笑容使他干裂的皮肤噼啪作响。");
	text = text.replace("Yes... yes! A man who would do this would certainly fit the profile of the ingredients I need.", "好的…好的！一个愿意这样做的人肯定会符合我所需要的原料的要求。");
	text = text.replace("Do it. Do it!", "做吧。做吧！");
	text = text.replace("Before you can even agree to this, the butcher grabs a tong hanging off a nearby wall, leverages it atop an anvil, wedges a finger between the pincers, and presses his knee to the handle, promptly severing a finger all in one go.", "你还没来得及同意，屠夫就抓起挂在附近墙上的钳子，把钳子放在铁砧上，用钳子夹住一根手指，把膝盖压在刀柄上，一下子就把一根手指砍断了。");
	text = text.replace("He wraps the hand before giving up the extremity to the stranger.", "他先把手包起来，然后把那根断指交给那个陌生人。");
	text = text.replace("There you have it: one especially cruel man\'s finger.", "就在这里：一个特别残忍的人的手指。");
	text = text.replace("The stranger grabs it as though it were the key to the world.", "这个陌生人抓住它，好像它是世界的钥匙。");
	text = text.replace("\'Marvelous!\', you think he says, but it\'s hard to hear as he hurriedly gives you some crowns and runs off.", "“真是不可思议！”你认为他说，但很难听到，因为他匆匆给你一些克朗就逃跑了。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s actually more than you originally agreed to.", "事实上这比你最初同意的要多。");
	text = text.replace("The butcher has certainly \'earned\' his half and you hand it over.", "屠夫当然已经“赚”了他的那一半，你交给了他。");

//cripple_pep_talk_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the cripple asks how (.*?) does it\./, "$1 这个瘸子问 $2 是怎么做到的。");
	text = text.replace("The veteran raises an eyebrow.", "老兵挑了挑眉毛。");
	text = text.replace("Do what?", "做什么？");
	text = text.replace("The cripple bounces his head around as he figuratively beats around the bush.", "瘸子四处击打周围的灌木丛，这时候他摇头晃脑。");
	text = text.replace("You know, it. Fight.", "你知道，这个事。战斗。");
	text = text.replace("Every time I get out there, I just think I\'m not up to it, as though I were dragging you fellas down.", "每次我走出战场的时候，我都觉得自己做不到，就好像我把你们都拖下水了。");
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) laughs\./, "$1 笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, I get what you mean.", "噢，我明白你的意思了。");
	text = text.replace("A cripple ain\'t fit for sellswording.", "瘸子不适合做佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("But is that who you are?", "但你就这点出息么？");
	text = text.replace("Just a cripple? Or are ye a man?", "就当自己是个瘸子？或者说你是男人么？");
	text = text.replace("You can choose to let your wobbles and ungainliness define who you are, or you can make your own path, as crooked and hobbled it may be.", "你可以选择让你的摇摆不定和笨拙来定义你是谁，或者走自己的路，尽管它可能是曲折的和蹒跚的。");
	text = text.replace(/Nodding, (.*?)\'s face starts to glow\./, "一直点着头，$1的脸开始容光焕发。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re right. I\'m not all that I could be and I got the body of a dying nun, but no man will put in more effort than I!", "你是对的。虽然我不能完全成为自己想要的样子，但那个稚嫩的我已经死了，我以后会比所有人都努力的！");

//cripple_vs_injury_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/The recent battle left (.*?) with a horrific and permanent injury\./, "最近的战斗在 $1 身上留下了可怕而的永久性损伤。");
	text = text.replace(/As he sits glumly about the campfire, (.*?) the cripple takes a seat next to him\./, "当他闷闷不乐地坐在营火旁时，$1 坐到他的身旁。");
	text = text.replace("So here you sit, bummed out about something that don\'t matter.", "原来你坐在这里，为一些无关紧要的事而烦恼。");
	text = text.replace("Look at me. Just look at me!", "看着我。就看看我！");
	text = text.replace("Look at where I am!", "看看我在哪里！");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve lost that which can\'t be returned, but did I dwell on it?", "我失去了那些无法挽回的东西，但我是否曾深陷其中？");
	text = text.replace("No. I pressed on.", "不。我挺过去了。");
	text = text.replace(/I joined the (.*?)\. Because that, that injury right there, that\'s gone and done\. This up here\.\.\./, "我加入了 $1。因为那些，那些旧伤已经过去了。我就说这些…");
	text = text.replace("The cripple taps the side of his head.", "瘸子轻轻敲着他的头。");
	text = text.replace("Up here is what can be made anew.", "这里所说的一切都是可以重头再来的。");
	text = text.replace("Up here is where you can think, yeah, that happened, but I\'m still a man and I\'m still in this.", "在这里你会想，是的，那确实发生了，但我还是一个男人，我还在这里。");
	text = text.replace("If the world wants me dead, it\'ll have to take all the pieces I got to give because I\'m not giving up until the last of me is gone!", "如果这个世界想要我死，它就必须带走给予我的一切，因为我不会放弃直到最后一个我消失！");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) nods and his mood already seems infinitely improved\./, "$1 点头，似乎他的情绪好了很多。");

//cultist_finale_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) enters your tent and a strong, brisk wind chases in after him, rearing up your scrolls and other notes\./, "$1 进入你帐篷，一阵强劲、凛冽的风紧随其后，刮起你的卷轴和其他文件。");
	text = text.replace("He walks forward, hands crossed before him, a rather priestly look to his approach.", "他向前走去，双手交叉在胸前，走路的样子像个牧师。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, I\'ve been spoken to and it is a grave matter which I\'ve been given responsibility for.", "先生，有人和我谈过这件事，我被委以重任。");
	text = text.replace("You ask the man who the hell he\'s talking about.", "你问他到底在说谁。");
	text = text.replace("The cultist bows forward as though the words weighed his tongue down just so.", "异教徒虔诚的向前鞠躬只敢低声下气的说话。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul, sir.", "达库尔，先生。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, of course, who else?", "唉，当然，还有谁？");
	text = text.replace("You tell the man to explain what it is he needs. The man responds.", "你让他解释一下他到底需要什么。这个人回答道。");
	text = text.replace("No, not I, Davkul.", "不，不是我，是达库尔。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul is the one in need - and he needs blood, a sacrifice.", "达库尔是救世主-他需要鲜血和祭品。");
	text = text.replace(/You tell the man the company can stop at the next town and get some chickens, lambs, or whatever else he needs if it\'s so important\. (.*?) shakes his head\./, "你告诉那个人，如果事情如此重要，战队可以在下一个城镇停一下，买些鸡、羊或者他需要的任何东西。$1 摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("The blood of some impish beast?", "某个淘气野兽的血？");
	text = text.replace("No, he demands the blood of a warrior.", "不，他要的是勇士的血。");
	text = text.replace("A true fighting spirit and he has trusted me to find a man of such import - and that I have.", "他有真正的战斗精神，他相信我能找到一个如此重要的人－而我确实找到了。");
	text = text.replace("The cultist straightens up, the tent\'s candlelight suddenly fickle and uneasy.", "异教徒直起身子，帐篷里的烛光突然变幻无常。");
	text = text.replace(/Davkul demands the blood of (.*?)\./, "达库尔需要鲜血，需要牺牲 $1。");
	
	text = text.replace(/Walking to a flickering candle, (.*?) holds his hand over the flame and the fire comes to a standstill, pointing upright and unmoving\./, "走到一根摇曳的蜡烛前，$1 将手放在火焰上，火焰静止不动，笔直的指向上方。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve seen icicles more animated than it.", "你见过的冰柱似乎比它更生动。");
	text = text.replace("He speaks as he stares into the glow.", "他凝视着火光。");
	text = text.replace("If we do this, Davkul will be most happy.", "如果我们这样做，达库尔会很高兴的。");
	text = text.replace("If not, well, we shall see.", "如果不，那好吧，我们走着瞧。");
	text = text.replace("Not even I know what may happen then.", "甚至我都不知道那时候会发生什么事。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the cultist that he\'s asking you to kill one of your own men.", "你告诉异教徒，他要你去杀自己的队员。");
	text = text.replace("He\'ll need to do better than that.", "他需要更强大才行。");
	text = text.replace("Hearing this, he walks over and grabs you by the shoulders.", "听到这话，他走过来抓住你的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("The tent melts away, slipping into the folds of an immense and immutable darkness.", "帐篷渐渐融化，消失在无边无际、永恒不变的黑暗之中。");
	text = text.replace("The cultist is gone. In his place is a black cloak, its arms to your shoulders, a slate of granite for a head, its edges chipped and cracking.", "异教徒走了。它的胳膊搭在你的肩膀上，一个花岗岩纹理的头套。它的边缘已经开裂。");
	text = text.replace("It appears there is something behind this mask, behind this futile effort to keep your mind safe from its true visage.", "在这张面具的背后似乎有什么东西，在这徒劳的努力背后保护你的思想不受其真实面目的影响。");
	text = text.replace("A voice speaks, a guttural, booming voice that is yet narrowed into a brutish whisper only for you to hear.", "一个声音在说话，一个喉音，洪亮的声音，却又变细成却又变窄成只有你能听到的粗野的低语。");
	text = text.replace(/I\'ll give you Death, mortal, and warmed in its comforts, Death shall be visited upon your enemies\. (.*?) will not be lost, he will be with you always, this I promise you\./, "我将赐予你死亡，人类，温暖又舒服，死亡会降临到你的敌人身上。$1 他不会逝去，他会永远和你在一起，我向你保证。");
	text = text.replace(/A whiteness snaps back over you, a rush of wind, tent flaps curling outward, candleflames tilting impossibly without going out, and a frigid coolness that has your first breath seen floating across the air\. (.*?) is nowhere to be seen\./, "一阵白茫茫的风迎面扑来，帐篷的顶篷向外卷起，烛光不可思议地没有熄灭，空气中弥漫着你第一次呼吸时的那种冰冷的凉意。$1 不见了。");
	text = text.replace("You quickly get up and touch your face and skin, making sure that you are all that you\'re supposed to be.", "你迅速站起来，触摸你的脸和皮肤，确保你就是你本来的样子。");
	text = text.replace("The vision remains, though, and its pulsing imprint has left behind a grisly reality that what the cultist has suggested is something to be measured seriously.", "然而，幻象依然存在，其波动的印记留下了一个可怕的现实问题，需要认真衡量异教徒提出的建议。");
	
	text = text.replace("You decide to fall to the undeniable impression that Davkul would be most unhappy with your failure to obey.", "你让自己变得心如铁石，因为如果不从，达库尔肯定会不高兴。");
	text = text.replace(/But (.*?) also has earned a departing word from you\./, "但是 $1 也获得了你的一句道别。");
	text = text.replace("Clearing up your face, you step out of your tent and go to speak to the man.", "收拾好你的脸，走出帐篷，去和那个人说话。");
	text = text.replace("Perhaps just hearing his voice will knock some sense into you before you step off the ledge into an insane void from which this act has no doubt been beckoned.", "也许仅仅是听到他的声音，也会在你的脑海中产生堕入无尽深渊的疯狂场景，这些毫无疑问是被召唤出来的。");
	text = text.replace("When you get to his tent, you notice that its flap is already open and gently waving in the wind.", "当你到达他的帐篷时，你会注意到它的帆布门已经打开，并在风中轻轻飘动。");
	text = text.replace("You step inside and find the sellsword in bed, his blanket tossed over him.", "你走进去，发现佣兵躺在床上，身上盖着毯子。");
	text = text.replace("You take a seat, speak a few words, hoping deep down that he\'ll wake up in the middle of them.", "你坐下来，说了几句话，内心深处希望他会在你们中间醒来。");
	text = text.replace(/You\'ve been good, (.*?), better than I could have asked for\./, "你做得很好，$1，比我要求的还要好。");
	text = text.replace(/A true brother to the (.*?) and the sort of fighter any captain would be proud to have\./, "$1 中的真正男儿，任何一位队长都会引以为傲的斗士。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, don\'t leave me rambling here.", "嘿，别让我在这儿闲扯。");
	text = text.replace("I know you\'re awake, you lark.", "我知道你会醒的，你这只百灵鸟。");
	text = text.replace("You reach over to the blanket and draw it back.", "你伸手去拿毯子，把它拉回来。");
	text = text.replace("You jump to your feet and nearly knock the whole tent over.", "你跳了起来，几乎把整个帐篷都撞倒了。");
	text = text.replace(/In the bed is not (.*?), but a torso, its flesh torn asunder and stretched around armor made of unknown metal, teeth for rivets, tendons for strappings, bones for pauldrons, a cuirass of absolute carnage\. (.*?) stands in the tent\'s opening\./, "躺在床上的不是 $1，而是而是一具躯干，它的肉被撕成碎片，缠在不知名的金属制成的盔甲上，牙齿用来做铆钉，肌腱用来做皮带，骨头用来做肩铠，这绝对是一副杀戮的铠甲。$2 站在帐篷的入口处。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul is most pleased and has graced us with an aspect of Death.", "达库尔非常高兴，死亡为我们带来光明。");
	text = text.replace("This... this is not what you were expecting.", "这…不是你所期望的。");
	text = text.replace("You don\'t even know what you were expecting, but this could never have been imagined or prepared for.", "你甚至不知道你在期待什么，但现在这一切无法想象和接受。");
	text = text.replace(/What\'s done is done, and may the soul of (.*?) rest in peace\./, "过去的事无法挽回，愿 $1 的灵魂安息。");
	text = text.replace("It is unlikely you ever will.", "你不会再这么做了。");
	
	text = text.replace(/Despite the horror which you have just been witness to, you decide that (.*?) shall live\./, "尽管你刚刚目睹了可怕的事情，你仍然决定 $1 应该活下来。");
	text = text.replace(/Just as you stand to go tell (.*?) of this, half the candles in the room suddenly blow out\./, "正当你准备去告诉 $1 这件事时，房间里一半的蜡烛突然熄灭了。");
	text = text.replace("Tendrils of smoke waft upward, a twisting haze through which, for but a moment, you swear you see a hard edged and angry visage turn and fade away.", "缕缕青烟袅袅而上，像一团扭曲的烟雾，你发誓你只在片刻之间，能看到一张棱角分明、怒火如焚的面容，转眼便消失不见了。");
	text = text.replace(/You get the feeling that (.*?) already knows what choice you\'ve made\./, "你会有这样一种感觉，$1 已经明白了你的选择。");
	text = text.replace("You stay in the tent and light those candles back up.", "你呆在帐篷里，把倒下的蜡烛重新点上了。");

//cultist_vs_old_gods_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While enjoying a slice of bacon, you hear wind of a quarrel going on.", "当你正在享用一片培根的时候，你听到争吵的声音随风传来。");
	text = text.replace("You ignore it for a time, but the shouts only get louder, quickly rising over your ability to enjoy a good meal.", "你忽视它一段时间，但叫喊声只是越来越大，迅速上升让你无法安心享用一顿美餐。");
	text = text.replace("Angered, you stand up and head toward the disturbance.", "被惹怒了，你站起来朝骚动的方向走去。");
	text = text.replace(/You find (.*?) and (.*?) facing off, the cultist and follower of the gods having apparently discovered some differences\./, "你发现 $1 和 $2 怒目相向，这些神的崇拜者和追随者显然意见不合。");
	
	text = text.replace("You step off to the side, letting the men hash out their differences as men with great differences do.", "你退到一旁，让队员们用男人的方式解决分歧。");
	text = text.replace("Fists for arguments, the follower of the old gods makes his case, battering the cultist again and again.", "古老神明的追随者们挥舞着拳头为自己辩护，一次又一次地打击着异教徒。");
	text = text.replace("But the man with the scarred head only grins in return.", "但那个头上有疤的人只以咧嘴笑回应。");
	text = text.replace("His eyes are puffing up, the lids purpled and puckering over his eyesight.", "他的眼睛肿了起来，眼皮皱成紫色，遮住了他的视线。");
	text = text.replace("Yet, still, he grins, and there is bloody laughter spewing out of his reddened mouth.", "然而，他仍然咧嘴一笑，从他流血的嘴里流出了恐怖的笑声。");
	text = text.replace("Such darkness! Davkul is most pleased!", "如此黑暗！达库尔一定很高兴！");
	text = text.replace(/With an anxious look, (.*?) steps off (.*?) and backs away\./, "带着焦虑的表情，$1 离开 $2 并向后退却。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s rubbing his bloodied knuckles, realizing he may have broken a few in the seemingly one-sided scuffle.", "他揉着血淋淋的指关节，意识到自己可能在这场看似一边倒的混战中被弄断了几个。");
	text = text.replace("But it\'s the cultist\'s words that hurt him most of all.", "但是异教徒还是出言令众人不快。");
	text = text.replace("Man isn\'t tempted by the darkness, he is called to it! Lost without it!", "人不是被黑暗诱惑，而是被黑暗召唤！没有他我不知所措！");
	text = text.replace("Gleeful in its return!", "他的归来让我狂喜！");
	text = text.replace(/Almost afraid to look back, (.*?) hurries away as the cultist remains behind, laughing and chuckling on the grass, nobody daring to get near him\./, "几乎不敢回头看，$1 匆忙离开，而异教徒还在他们身后，在草地上大声发笑，没人敢靠近他。");
	
	text = text.replace("The way things are going, you\'ve hardly a man to spare.", "照目前的情况看，你几乎没有多余的人可用。");
	text = text.replace("Just as fists are about to start flying, you step in between the two men and put an end to it.", "就在他们准备挥拳相向的时候，你走入这两个人之间，结束了他们的争吵。");
	text = text.replace(/You tell (.*?) he is better than this, and you tell (.*?) nothing, for the cultist is almost bowled over in fits of laughter\./, "你告诉 $1 他更有理，对 $2 什么都没有说，因为异教徒几乎被一阵阵的笑声击倒。");
	text = text.replace("He points, grinning madly.", "他指着我们，疯狂地笑着。");
	text = text.replace("The light steps in, but darkness is patient.", "光明来了，但黑暗正耐心等待。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul awaits you all.", "达库尔即将降临到你们。");

//cultist_vs_uneducated_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A few brothers come to you looking rather worried.", "有几个兄弟来找你，看上去很着急。");
	text = text.replace(/They say (.*?) has been sitting with (.*?) for a few hours now\./, "他们说 $1 和 $2 坐在一起几个小时了。");
	text = text.replace("When you ask what\'s the worry, they remind you that the cultist has a scarred forehead and speaks of incredibly strange things. Ah, right.", "当你问他们担心什么时，他们提醒你，那个异教徒有一个伤疤的额头，说着令人难以置信的怪事。唉，好吧。");
	text = text.replace(/You go and see the two men\. (.*?) looks up at you, smiling, and says the cultist actually has a lot to teach him\./, "你去看看那两个人。$1 抬头看着你，微笑着，说这个异教徒有很多东西要教他。");
	text = text.replace("Grimacing, you wonder if you should put a stop to these... lessons.", "做了个鬼脸，你不知道你是否应该停止这些…课程。");
	
	text = text.replace("You nod and turn away.", "你点头，转身走开了。");
	text = text.replace("The rest of the brothers shake their heads.", "其余的兄弟们摇着头。");
	text = text.replace(/By next morning, (.*?) is found with a fresh wound on his forehead, the blood of conversion\./, "第二天早上，$1 被发现在他的额头上有一个新伤口，血液结了痂。");
	text = text.replace("When you ask how he is doing, he only says a few words.", "你问他还好吗。他只回答了几个词。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul is coming.", "达库尔就要来了。");
	text = text.replace("Well, great.", "好吧，太好了。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You separate the two men, telling (.*?) to go count some inventory\./, "你把这两个人分开，让 $1 去清点一些存货。");
	text = text.replace("When he leaves, the cultist sneers at you.", "当他离开时，异教徒对你冷笑。");
	text = text.replace("Davkul awaits. You see him in your sleep.", "达库尔即将降临。你在梦中看到他。");
	text = text.replace("You see him in the nights.", "你在夜里看到他。");
	text = text.replace("His darkness is coming.", "他的黑暗就要来了。");
	text = text.replace("No light burns forever.", "没有光会永远燃烧。");

//dastard_loses_trait_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You come across (.*?) and (.*?) sitting with (.*?)\. The two men are pepping up the rather skittish brother, letting him know that there is nothing to fear in battle\. (.*?) explains that he is fearful of a painful death\. (.*?) says he has seen many men die and by the sword, truly, is one of the fastest\. (.*?) raises his hand\./, "你偶然看到 $1 和 $2 与 $3 坐在一起。两个人扶起那个有点神经质的队员，让他知道在战斗中没有什么可怕的。$4 解释说他害怕在痛苦中死去。$5 说他已经见过太多人死于刀剑，说真的，剑是杀人最快的。$6 举起他的手。");
	text = text.replace("Unless it gets you in the stomach.", "除非剑插到你胃里。");
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) nods\./, "$1 点头。");
	text = text.replace("Right. But other than that, you have nothing to fear!", "是这样的。但除此之外，你真没什么好怕的！");

//dead_bodies_in_forest_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While marching through the forest, (.*?) calls out to the company\./, "当队伍穿过树林的时候，$1 在前面大声喊叫起来。");
	text = text.replace("You look over to see him pointing somewhere beyond a line of brush.", "你顺着他手指的一排灌木丛之后看去。");
	text = text.replace("When you walk to him, you see what he sees: three bodies hanging from a tree.", "当你向他走过去之后，你看见了他眼中的一切：三具尸体被挂在一棵树上。");
	text = text.replace(/Their purpled faces and grey feet sway and turn, the wind sometimes forcing them to grimly face one another\. (.*?) notes that they\'re wearing wood: signs of their crimes\./, "他们发紫的脸庞和灰白的双脚在摇摆着，旋转着。有时风吹起来，他们便偶然面面相觑，令人不寒而栗。$1 注意到他们身上挂着木牌，上面写着他们各自的罪行。");
	text = text.replace("\'Thief,\' reads one. \'Whore\' another. \'Traitor\' the last.", "“小偷，”读到一个。“妓女”另一个。“叛徒”最后一个。");
	text = text.replace("Having seen enough, you tell the men to get moving again.", "已经看得够多了，你告诉你的人可以继续赶路了。");
	text = text.replace("The forest offers no relief, no little road or sidepath for you to travel down.", "森林不会给你任何放松的机会，哪怕是一条能让人走下去的小路或幽径。");
	text = text.replace("It is thick and unrelenting and does not seem to want you there.", "它是幽深而无情的，似乎并不希望你待在那里。");
	text = text.replace("You soon find that it did not want someone else, either: a corpse is found tied up in a thorn bush, legs crooked, arms bent, all rather finagled to to their supposed purpose.", "你很快就发现它也不想要任何其他人待在那里：一具尸体被发现缠绕在荆棘丛中，双腿弯折，手臂扭曲，所有这些都与他们的预期目的相吻合。");
	text = text.replace(/The mouth rests agape with the eyes drawn slim in some sort of final frustration\. (.*?) catches up to you, looks the body up and down, then nods\./, "残余的嘴巴因惊恐而张大，眼睛因某种最后的折磨眯成一条缝。$1 追上你，他上下打量着这些尸体，然后点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Body\'s clean as a whistle, aside from the thorn\'s work of course.", "只要一声令下，就把这些尸体打扫干净，当然别指望让我们清扫这些荆棘。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d say that man right there was so lost no animal could find him.", "但我要说的是，这人被迷失在这种地方，没有动物会发现他。");
	text = text.replace("Just died, no use to anyone or anything.", "不过是个死人，对任何人或任何事没有任何用处。");
	text = text.replace("You point at an ant mindlessly bumbling about the dead man\'s teeth.", "你用手指着一只蚂蚁，它在不经意地乱翻死人的牙齿。");
	text = text.replace("The brother laughs and shakes his head.", "你的兄弟笑着摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("You sure he ain\'t lost too?", "你确定他不也是迷失在这里吗？");
	text = text.replace("You stare up at the forest canopy, watching what angles the lightbeams are coming in at.", "你抬头盯着森林的树冠，观察光束进入的角度。");
	text = text.replace(/While getting your bearings, (.*?) comes by looking rather distraught\./, "当你明白自己的想法时，$1 看起来很沮丧地走过来。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, you oughta come see this.", "先生，你应该来看看这个。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and tell him to lead the way.", "你点头告诉他带路。");
	text = text.replace("He brings you to a clearing, though not much about it is clear.", "他把你带到一个空地上，虽然不是真的叫空地。");
	text = text.replace("Legs. Legs everywhere. Some severed at the ankle, some at the thigh, and everywhere else in between.", "腿。到处都是断腿。有的是从脚踝处切断，有的从大腿处，还有从中间的其他地方。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve no place, no order.", "它们杂乱无章地散落一地。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re just about, some by themselves and others all twisted up in bunches, some planted upright with sticks like they were walking jokes and a few even seem to have been thrown into the trees where they rest limply over branches or upside down by their feet.", "它们就这样，有些单独放在那，另一些则是成串地缠绕在一起，有些是和棍子一起在地上立着，就像是在开什么行走的玩笑似的，还有些甚至像是被扔进了树林里，在那里它们无力地躺在树枝上，或者倒在树根边。");
	text = text.replace("One hangs from a spit, the calf burnt black as though someone had run off, leaving it there over a fire that had long since died.", "有一只被串在一根烤肉叉上，小腿肚被烤成了黑色，就好像有人跑开，把它就这么扔在早已燃尽的余灰上。");
	text = text.replace("The brother that found the disgusting sight comes to stand next to you.", "那个发现这些恶心玩意儿的兄弟站在你身旁。");
	text = text.replace("No bodies, sir. Just.. legs.", "没有身体，先生。只有…腿。");
	text = text.replace("You turn to look at the mercenary, but all he can do is shrug.", "你看向那个雇佣兵，但他能做的也就是耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("We\'ve not found a single body, sir.", "我们一块身体的部位都没有发现，先生。");
	text = text.replace("I mean, the top-half, anyway.", "我的意思是，不管怎么样，总该会有上半部分才对。");
	text = text.replace("Do you think it means anything?", "你觉得这里面有什么含义吗？");
	text = text.replace("I mean, who would do that?", "我是说，到底谁会做这种事？");
	text = text.replace("Remove someone\'s legs and then take off with the rest?", "卸掉人腿然后带走其他部分？");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head in disbelief.", "你不以为然地摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Having seen enough, and having no answer for such questions, you quickly usher the rest of the men away from the clearing and get back to marching.", "看够了这些，并且脑子里也没有这些问题的答案，你匆匆地带领你的手下离开这片空地继续前进。");
	text = text.replace(/You stop at a creekbed to wash yourself and get something of a drink, but before you take the first sip (.*?) grabs your shoulder\./, "你停在一条小溪边洗漱，喝点东西，但是在你喝下第一口之前，$1 抓住了你的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("He points upriver. A woman\'s body is face down in the water, her long hair twisting rather lively to the ripples.", "他指向上游。一个女人的尸体面部朝下漂浮在水上，她的长发扭曲活泼地荡漾着。");
	text = text.replace("You thank the sellsword for saving you from any disease the dead press onto the world.", "你感谢这位佣兵将你从死亡降临的这个世界的任何恶疾中拯救出来。");
	text = text.replace("The tree canopy is thick and twisting.", "树冠厚实而扭曲。");
	text = text.replace("Whatever light there is above can barely come through, braids of shadow encompassing your men as they march.", "无论上面有什么光都几乎不能穿透，当你的人前进时，阴影做成的织物层层包围着他们。");
	text = text.replace("But further on ahead you see a pillar of light gleaming into the forest.", "但在前方，你看到一根光柱在森林中闪烁。");
	text = text.replace("Naturally, someone else saw it first.", "很显然，这是别人先看到的。");
	text = text.replace("And it was the last thing they saw.", "而且这是他们看到的最后一件东西。");
	text = text.replace("In that stroke of light a boy rests with his back up against a tree.", "在那道亮光中，一个男孩仰卧在一棵树上。");
	text = text.replace("His head is aloll and his hands turned up and open.", "他的头昂着，双手向上张开。");
	text = text.replace(/Purple smudges stain his palms\. (.*?) walks up and immediately shakes his head\./, "紫色的污迹弄脏了他的手掌。$1 走上前然后果断地摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Poison berries. Damned kid didn\'t stand a chance.", "毒浆果，这该死的孩子没机会活下来。");
	text = text.replace("You turn to the battle brother and inquire if the boy might have gone peacefully.", "你回头看向战场兄弟，询问他是不是走得很安详。");
	text = text.replace("The man shakes his head again.", "那人又摇了摇头。");
	//text = text.replace("No.", "不。");
	text = text.replace("A dead body. Rather, what should be a body.", "一具尸体，或者说，它只是一具躯干。");
	text = text.replace("The chest is open and the viscera laid out in all directions, grey and sagging and soft.", "胸部敞开，灰黑的内脏四通八达，就这么柔软地垂在那里。");
	text = text.replace("You can\'t tell if it was a man or woman, only that it had to have been an adult cut down to much smaller sizes.", "你不知道它是个男人还是女人，但这肯定是个被刀切得远小于原来尺寸的成年人。");
	text = text.replace(/What creature could have done this work is beyond you, though (.*?) suggests maybe it was the deed of a very determined man\./, "你想不到什么样的生物会这么做，尽管 $1 认为这可能是一个意志非常坚定的人所干的事。");
	text = text.replace("You find the body of a woman with its back resting against a tree.", "你发现一具女人的尸体，背靠在树上。");
	text = text.replace("There is a knife in her chest, the wound so quickly fatal that she appears to have died while in some motion of life.", "她的胸口有一把刀，伤口迅速致命，就好像她本来还活着走得好好的然后突然死了。");
	text = text.replace("Above her, another woman swings from a branch.", "在她上方，另一个女人挂在树枝上荡来荡去。");
	text = text.replace("Red are her clothes.", "她的衣服是红色的。");
	text = text.replace("The body\'s head tilts forward as though to stare at her crime, and the rope that hangs her there groans to a muted wind.", "尸体的头向前倾斜，好像在盯着她犯下的罪行，挂在那里的绳子在无声的风中呻吟。");
	text = text.replace("You come across some scene of battle.", "你遇到了一片战场。");
	text = text.replace("Men, armor, weapons, not a single one of them useable.", "人，盔甲，武器，没有一个是有用的。");
	text = text.replace("The dead got that way through some sheer form of brutality you do not wish to learn.", "死者是被某种你不想学的纯粹的残暴弄这样的。");
	text = text.replace("Footprints in the earth suggest something big had come through, leaving behind a wake of ruin and calamity, and no urge on your part to follow where those steps go.", "泥土上的脚印表示着这里曾经发生过什么大事，留下了毁灭和灾难的尾迹，并且没有给你任何冲动让你跟随这些脚步的去向。");
	text = text.replace("Marching along, you find a dead man with a few broken arrows in his back.", "向前走，你发现一个背上有几支折断的箭的死人。");
	text = text.replace("More puncture wounds where his killer managed to retrieve his ammunition in one piece.", "更多的刺伤，凶手设法把他的弹药一件一件地取回。");
	text = text.replace("The man was carrying a love letter, its destination a woman that had, apparently, already been spoken for. Ah, romance.", "那个人手里拿着一封情书，目的地显然是一个信中提及的女人。唉，真浪漫。");

//dead_bodies_on_road_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A wagon, tipped over.", "一辆载重货车，翻倒了。");
	text = text.replace("Dead horses by its side.", "它旁边有几匹死马。");
	text = text.replace("One dead donkey with evidence of having put up a fight.", "一头死驴，有打斗的迹象。");
	text = text.replace("Women. Children. A couple of older men.", "女人们。孩子们。几个老人。");
	text = text.replace("Most mutilated in a fashion unsuitable for being found by anyone, but you figure your company was probably the best fit to come across such ruin.", "大部分都残肢断臂，对于发现他们的人来说是一场恶心的视觉盛宴，你确信你的战队是最优秀的，能够应付这种恶心的场面。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve got the stomach for it, for you have created worse.", "你让你的胃忍住不吐，因为你让它变糟了。");
	text = text.replace("It is the innocence of the dead that turns the gut, though, and in a feeble effort to rectify that moral illness you go ahead and bury the dead.", "这些无辜的死者肠穿肚烂，然而，在无力纠正这种道德疾病的情况下，你只能继续埋葬这些死者。");
	text = text.replace("Sadly, nothing of value is found in their remains.", "遗憾的是，在他们的遗体中没有发现任何有价值的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Blood in the ditch by the side of the road.", "路边的水沟里有血。");
	text = text.replace("Blood all across the road.", "路上到处都是血。");
	text = text.replace("Blood in the ditch on the other side of the road.", "路另一边的水沟里也有血。");
	text = text.replace("Blood up on the canvas of the wagon.", "鲜血染红了载重货车的帆布。");
	text = text.replace("Blood in the dead\'s eyes and blood in their mouth.", "死者眼睛和嘴里都是血。");
	text = text.replace("One poor farmer, deceased, seemingly happened upon by a band of thieves for nothing of value he carried remains in the ruin you\'ve stumbled upon.", "一个可怜的农夫，死了，似乎还被一群贼洗劫了，因为这具被你偶然发现的遗骸没剩下任何有价值的东西了。");
	text = text.replace("The birds were the first hint: cycling and turning over a distant calamity.", "鸟群是第一个暗示：见到或遇到一个遥远的灾难。");
	text = text.replace("You figured whatever they saw was still alive, but by the time you got to it the flock had landed and you stumbled across a dead man leaning up against a sidepost.", "你以为他们看到的东西还活着，但当你走到那儿的时候，鸟群已经降落了，你无意中发现一个靠在石头上的死人。");
	text = text.replace("You try and scare the birds away.", "你试着把鸟吓跑。");
	text = text.replace("The black buzzards only hop a few steps in the opposite direction where they then turn to stare at you.", "这些黑秃鹫们只会朝着相反的方向跳几步，然后就会转向盯着你看。");
	text = text.replace("The corpse is fresh, the means to its death a slow one: a few arrows stick out of his side.", "尸体是新鲜的，死亡的方式是缓慢的：几支箭从他的侧面扎出来。");
	text = text.replace("A rope on his hip suggests he had a purse there.", "他屁股上的绳子表明他有个钱包。");
	text = text.replace("Someone robbed him - twice.", "有人抢劫了他－不止两次。");
	text = text.replace("You stumble across a few hanged criminals.", "你偶然发现一些被绞死的罪犯。");
	text = text.replace("They swing from a tree by the side of the road, their faces mere impressions beneath the woolsacks over their heads.", "他们在路边的一棵树上荡来荡去，他们的脸在头上的羊毛布袋下仅仅显出轮廓。");
	text = text.replace("A few of them show signs of torture: gashes here and there, the glaring muscles turning purple and some already grey.", "他们中的一些人显现出受折磨的迹象：到处都是伤痕，强壮的肌肉变成了紫色，有些已经是灰色了。");
	text = text.replace("Blood beneath one\'s feet, suggesting someone had a go at him while he suffocated.", "脚底下有血，表明他窒息时有人对他动过手脚。");
	text = text.replace("Naturally, they have nothing of value so you get back on the road.", "当然，他们没有任何价值，所以你又回到了路上。");
	text = text.replace("A goat with a bell cradled in the arms of a dead shepherd.", "一只带着铃铛的山羊被一个死去的牧羊人抱着。");
	text = text.replace("You found the pair by the side of the road.", "你在路边找到了他们。");
	text = text.replace("The animal\'s throat is open, and the man\'s body has no wounds.", "动物的喉咙是割开的，人的身体没有伤口。");
	text = text.replace(/Maybe he died of a broken heart\. (.*?) rifles through the dead man\'s pockets and comes up empty handed\./, "也许牧羊人死于心脏病。$1 开始搜死者的口袋，空手而归。");
	text = text.replace("You decide to leave the two where they were.", "你决定把它们的尸体留在原地。");
	text = text.replace("Two buzzards clasp a string of intestine between the two of them, slowly chomping it down until their beaks clack together.", "两只秃鹰撕扯着一段肠子，慢慢地咀嚼着，直到它们的喙咔嗒咔嗒地碰到一起。");
	text = text.replace("You\'d be humored if it weren\'t for where this meal had come from: a dead child, he or she lying face down on the ground.", "你被这顿饭的来历惊呆了：一个死去的孩子，他或她脸朝下躺在地上。");
	text = text.replace("The back had been torn away, a lurid ribcage glistening in the sun.", "他的背部被撕裂了，一个可怕的胸腔在阳光下闪闪发光。");
	text = text.replace("You scare off the birds - though they are quite reluctant to be scared at all - and then bury the body.", "你吓跑了那些鸟－尽管它们很不愿意被吓到－然后把尸体埋起来。");
	text = text.replace(/Moving back onto the road, you see the two birds squatting over the grave, picking and prodding at the dirt (.*?)\./, "回到路上，你看到两只鸟儿蹲在坟墓上，在泥土上啄来啄去 $1。");
	text = text.replace("in some sort of avian angst", "带着鸟类特有的焦虑");
	text = text.replace("as if to somehow recreate the process they\'d seen but in reverse", "好像以某种方式重复之前的过程，但以相反的方式");
	text = text.replace("Giving up, they eventually take flight, circling above your band of men for a mile or two before heading elsewhere.", "放弃后，它们最终会飞走，在你的队伍上空盘旋一两英里，然后飞向别处。");
	text = text.replace(/The fires crackle and pop as they consume the last of the wagon\. (.*?) picks through the blackened mess, but comes up empty handed\./, "篝火噼噼啪啪地燃烧着，吞噬着一辆载重货车。$1 在一片漆黑的废墟中搜寻，却空手而归。");
	text = text.replace("A few hands can be found sticking up out of the ash and soot, their forms as equally black.", "你可以看到有几只手从灰烬和煤烟中伸出来，它们的外表也一样黑。");
	text = text.replace("The bodies are completely gone, buried or burned away or buried beneath that which was burned away.", "尸体完全不见了，被埋了，被烧了，或者被烧完后埋了。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing as how there is nothing to salvage, you quickly get the company back on the road.", "看到没有任何东西可以挽救，你很快让战队回到路上。");
	text = text.replace("A dead horse. Its rider is across the road, having crawled to his final resting spot.", "一匹死马。它的骑手穿过了大路，爬到了他最后的休息地点。");
	text = text.replace("Broken arrows litter the path, the heads of them ripped off and salvaged.", "破碎的箭散布在小径上，它们的头被扯下来捡走了。");
	text = text.replace("The man is missing his scalp, the cap of his head glinting and red.", "这名男子的头皮不见了，他的头顶反射着光。");
	text = text.replace("After a quick search you realize there\'s nothing here to take and decide to move on.", "在快速搜索之后，你意识到这里没有什么可以带走的，于是决定继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a pile of naked bodies by the side of the road.", "你在路边看到一堆裸体。");
	text = text.replace("Some of them look ghastly, as though they\'ve been dead for a great long while, though rather fresh blood is in some of their mouths.", "有些人看起来很可怕，好像他们已经死了很久了，虽然有些人嘴里还流着新鲜的血。");
	text = text.replace("A few of the corpses carry color in their flesh, but they have what look like bite marks here and there.", "一些尸体身上被涂了颜色，但它们到处都有咬痕。");
	text = text.replace("Preemptive measures were taken, it seems, for every one of them has had his or her neck slashed.", "似乎是被采取了先发制人的措施，因为每个人的脖子都被割过。");
	text = text.replace("Naked as they are, you naturally find nothing but what is natural to nature itself. You move on.", "他们一丝不挂，你自然只会发现它们原有的东西。你继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("You feel as though you are being stared at and stop, quickly turning to the side of the road with a hand on your sword.", "你觉得自己好像被人盯着，然后停了下来，迅速转向路边，一只手按在剑上。");
	text = text.replace(/A head stares back at you with its eyes barely peeping over some grass\. (.*?) walks over and picks it up\./, "一个人头盯着你，它的眼睛几乎没有从草上探出来。$1 走过去把它捡起来。");
	text = text.replace("The face carries the visage of a rather jarring death, being so slackjawed and slanted.", "这张脸长的口眼歪斜，带着一种相当不和谐的死亡表情。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the sellsword to put the head down for you\'ve better things to do.", "你告诉佣兵放下这个头，因为你有重要的事情要做。");

//dead_lumberjack_event.nut
	text = text.replace("The forest is home to many curiosities and dead bodies, really, aren\'t even the most curious of those.", "森林里有许多稀奇古怪的东西，而尸体，说真的，甚至不是最稀奇的。");
	text = text.replace(/So when you stumble upon a litter of dead lumberjacks the only thing that piques your interest is the lump of a direwolf slain beside them\. (.*?) eyes the tracks going back and forth across a cutting field so abruptly interrupted that some axes were left hewn into tree trunks\./, "所以，当你偶然发现一伙死去的伐木工时，唯一让你感兴趣的就是在他们旁边被杀的冰原狼。$1 盯着那几条原野上的脚印，这几串脚印突兀地中断了，几把斧子被留在了树干上。");
	text = text.replace("He spits and nods.", "他边吐边点头。");
	text = text.replace("Poor fellas. Looks like some direwolves bushwhacked them something fierce.", "可怜的家伙们。看起来好像是一些冰原狼袭击了他们。");
	text = text.replace("You have the men collect what\'s left to be recovered and make your leave.", "你让队员们去收集剩下的东西然后离开。");

//dead_merchant_forest_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While marching through the forest, you come across a body swinging from a branch.", "当你在森林中行进时，你看到一具尸体在树枝上摇摆。");
	text = text.replace(/It appears it has been there long enough for even the flies to have gotten their fill\. (.*?) notes some sharp suede shoes on the corpse\'s feet\./, "它似乎这样存在了足够长的时间，甚至连苍蝇都吃饱了。$1 注意到尸体脚上一双不错的山羊皮鞋。");
	text = text.replace("Looks like a merchant to me, sir.", "在我看来他好像是个商人，先生。");
	text = text.replace("You agree and have it cut down.", "你同意他的观点并把尸体放了下来。");
	text = text.replace("Upon closer inspection, the eyes have been carved out and tattoos drawn across his chest.", "经过仔细观察，他的眼睛被刺瞎了，胸前有纹身。");
	text = text.replace("Given that you find some crowns still on the body, this was likely to be the work of uncivilized wildmen being spooked by an outsider.", "鉴于你发现尸体上还有些克朗，这很有可能是未开化的野人的杰作。");

//deserter_in_forest_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While trundling through the forest, birds suddenly scatter into the sky, shaking the trees and branches with the very frightful urgency of their leaving.", "当在森林中跋涉的时候，鸟儿们突然四散在天空中，它们的离去让树木和树枝都为之震颤。");
	text = text.replace("Not a moment later does a man come barreling through a bush, looking more flash flood than flesh and blood.", "没过一会儿，一个男人就从灌木丛中冲了过来，他看上去更像一场突如其来的洪流，而不是血肉之躯。");
	text = text.replace("He seizes up, this earthen golem, and begs you to hide him.", "他握紧你的手，这个灰头土脸的傀儡，恳求你把他藏起来。");
	text = text.replace("Look, I\'ll be perfectly honest.", "看吧，我非常诚实。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m a deserter. That\'s that.", "我是个逃兵。就是这样。");
	text = text.replace("I didn\'t, I mean, alright I don\'t really have a defense.", "我没有，我是说，我真的没有辩解。");
	text = text.replace("But look, what are you? Mercenaries? Great!", "但是你看，你是什么？雇佣兵么？太好了！");
	text = text.replace("Hide me and I\'ll fight for you to the end of time!", "把我藏起来，我将为你战斗到底！");
	text = text.replace("Halfway through his pleading spiel, you hear dogs barking in the distance.", "在他那充满恳求的演讲进行到一半时，你能听到远处的狗叫声。");
	text = text.replace("The man instinctively hides away into an arboreal cubby, quickly covering himself with dirt.", "这个人本能地躲到一个树栖的小房间里，迅速地用泥土把自己盖住。");
	text = text.replace("He nods as if to say you\'ve already come to an agreement.", "他点头，好像在说你们已经达成了协议。");
	text = text.replace("Bounty hunters come through the tree line, their dogs already sniffing around.", "赏金猎人穿过林木线，他们的狗已经嗅来嗅去了。");
	text = text.replace("Their lieutenant looks around.", "他们的军官环顾四周。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t even try to fool me, sellsword.", "别想骗我，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("I know that deserter came this way.", "我知道那个逃兵是从这边来的。");
	text = text.replace("Two hundred crowns for his head. Where is he?", "二百克朗买他的头。他在哪？");
	
	text = text.replace("You spit and shake your head.", "你吐了口吐沫并摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve not the faintest farkin\' clue what you\'re talking about, bounty hunter.", "我他妈一点都不知道你在说什么，赏金猎人。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant eyes you up, staring you down with an old man\'s wisdom.", "军官盯着你，用老成持重的方式盯着你。");
	text = text.replace("Alright, mercenary. So be it.", "好吧，雇佣兵。就这样吧。");
	text = text.replace("I know you\'re lying, but there\'s not much I can do about it.", "我知道你在撒谎，但我也无能为力。");
	text = text.replace("The bounty hunter looses a sharp whistle and orders his band of men forth.", "赏金猎人吹了一声尖锐的口哨，命令他的队伍前进。");
	text = text.replace("The dogs bark briefly at the cubby where the deserter had hidden.", "狗对着逃跑者藏着的树屋一个劲地吠叫。");
	text = text.replace("Laughing, the lieutenant mockingly wishes you the best.", "大笑着，军官嘲讽地祝你一切顺利。");
	text = text.replace("With his hunters gone, the deserter emerges.", "赏金猎人走了，逃兵出现了。");
	text = text.replace("Thank you, mercenary. I owe you my life!", "谢谢你，雇佣兵。我欠你一条命！");
	text = text.replace("You\'ll not regret this, not ever!", "你不会后悔的，永远不会！");
	
	text = text.replace("You nod to where the deserter is hiding.", "你向逃兵藏匿的地方点头。");
	text = text.replace("He must have kept one distrusting eye on you because he immediately jumps out of the hole and goes fleeing.", "那个逃兵一定是用一只不信任的眼睛盯着你，因为他马上跳出洞去逃跑了。");
	text = text.replace("The dogs run him down with ease, glomming onto him with caninal ferocity and dragging his screaming ass to the ground.", "几条狗毫不费力地把他追了下来，凶猛地扑向他，把他尖叫着捂着屁股倒在地上。");
	text = text.replace("Before you can even so much as laugh, the bounty hunter puts a bag of crowns into your palm.", "你还没来得及笑，赏金猎人就把一包克朗放在你的手掌里。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s half my cut, but without the happenstance of your being here, I\'m not sure we would have caught that wily bastard.", "那是我应得赏金的一半，但是如果没有你在这里，我不确定我们会不会抓到那个狡猾的混蛋。");

//determined_delivers_peptalk_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You are beginning to worry that a sort of malaise has fallen upon the men.", "你开始担心一种不祥之兆会降临在队员们身上。");
	text = text.replace("They sit about the campfire, mindlessly poking sticks into the flames.", "他们围坐在篝火旁，没头没脑地往火里加木头。");
	text = text.replace("Each face shows a loss of control, a loss of governance over one\'s own destiny.", "每一张脸都表现出一种控制的缺失，确切说是掌握自己命运的那种缺失。");
	text = text.replace("If a man can\'t know if tomorrow will be better than today, then how is he to keep pushing forward?", "如果一个人不知道明天会不会比今天更好，那他怎么能继续前进呢？");
	text = text.replace(/Just as you are about to address this, (.*?) stands up and so despondent is the mood that even the swift motion by itself catches the company\'s attention\./, "就在你要回答这个问题的时候，$1 站了起来，表情是如此的沮丧，但他快速转换情绪的能力让整个战队都感到震惊。");
	text = text.replace("Look at you bunch of sorry sad sacks.", "看看你们这些可怜的家伙。");
	text = text.replace("Do you think you\'re unique?", "你认为你是独一无二的吗？");
	text = text.replace("Do you think you\'re the first to feel like shit?", "你以为你是第一个觉得自己很糟糕的人吗？");
	text = text.replace("No, of course not.", "不，当然不是。");
	text = text.replace("You\'d not be the first to give up, either.", "你不应该是第一个放弃的人。");
	text = text.replace("To lay down and not rise again.", "躺下，就不再起来。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s the easy thing to do.", "这是一件容易的事。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s what the world wants you to do.", "这就是这个世界想搞你的。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s enough sonsabitches around, no need in having some sorry asses like yourselves mucking things up if you don\'t want no part and parcel in this punishment we call life.", "周围操蛋的事多了去了，如果你不想在这种我们称之为生活的惩罚中消沉，就没有必要像你们这样把事情想得一团糟。");
	text = text.replace("Roused by this speech, you see a bit of a glint falling over the company.", "这番话一出，你就看到整个战队一片欢腾。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) continues, almost stabbing his thumb into his chest\./, "$1 继续说着，他的拇指几乎扎进了胸膛。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m not taking the world\'s shit.", "我不是想说世界有多操蛋。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m gonna make the world sorry for having me here.", "我要让全世界为我们道歉。");
	text = text.replace("I didn\'t ask for no invitation so I ain\'t gonna play nice to this farkin\' party.", "我没有请求任何邀请，所以我没有在这个操蛋的派对上表现得很好。");
	text = text.replace("See you in the next life, men, but until then, let\'s dance in this one!", "下辈子见，兄弟们，但在那之前，让我们在此生共舞吧！");
	text = text.replace("A cheer erupts and the men get to their feet, a sense of elation bursting forth as though the ground had them chained all along.", "一阵欢呼爆发了，队员们站了起来，以一种兴高采烈的方式爆发了出来，仿佛大地把他们一直拴在一起。");

//disowned_noble_reminisces_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You find (.*?) sitting by himself outside the camp\./, "你发现 $1 独自坐在营地外。");
	text = text.replace("As the jeers and cheers of the men around the campfire crackle behind you, you approach the man and ask what he\'s sulking for. He shrugs.", "当营火周围的人在你身后发出叽叽喳喳的嘲笑和欢呼时，你走近那个人，问他在生气什么。他耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Not sulking, sir, just thinking.", "我不是在生闷气，先生，我只是在思考。");
	text = text.replace("Though I suppose one could be easily mistaken for the other.", "尽管我认为其中一个很容易被误认为另一个。");
	text = text.replace("Chuckling, he offers a bit of his drink, which you take.", "轻声笑着，他提供了一点酒，你接过去了。");
	text = text.replace("Settling down beside him, you ask what it is he is \'thinking\' about.", "在他身边坐下，你问他在“想”什么。");
	text = text.replace("The disowned nobleman shrugs again.", "那个没落的的贵族又耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Ahh, nothing really. Just thinking about home.", "啊，其实没什么。只是想家。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m a long ways away from it now, and the last I remember of it isn\'t exactly the best, yet I still find myself wishing to be there now and again.", "我现在离它还有很远一段路要走，我记得的最后一次也不是最好的，但我仍然觉得自己时不时地想去那里。");
	text = text.replace("Homesick for a land that thinks me a sort of noble sickness, go figure.", "思乡病在我看来是一种高贵的疾病，想想看吧。");
	text = text.replace("You hand him back to his drink as he probably needs it more than you.", "你把酒还给他，因为他可能比你更需要。");
	text = text.replace("While you\'re still clearheaded, you try and speak your mind...", "趁你头脑还清醒，你试着说出你的想法…");
	
	text = text.replace("You speak.", "你说。");
	text = text.replace("Where you\'re from is a house, not a home.", "你离开的地方是一所房子，不是一个家。");
	text = text.replace("You yearn for a different place in a different time, when you\'re in this place, right here, right now.", "你渴望在不一样的时间来到一个不一样的地方，当你来到这个地方的时候，就在这里，就在此刻。");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) looks after you, and you it, and only together will we persevere\./, "$1 照顾你，和你在一起，我们才会持之以恒。");
	text = text.replace("The man stares into his drink for a time.", "这个男人盯着酒杯看了一会儿。");
	text = text.replace("He chuckles, sips, and wipes the froth away.", "他低声笑着，抿着酒，擦去了脸上的泡沫。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, I suppose that\'s one way to look at it. Thank you, captain.", "是的，我想这是看待思乡病的一种方式。谢谢你，队长。");
	
	text = text.replace("You clap the man on his shoulder and speak.", "你拍拍他的肩膀说。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, thinking of the old is good for the soul, even if it\'s through a thicket of shit and cruelty and evil and all else that makes any man stay up at night.", "嘿，思念过去对灵魂是有好处的，即使它是通过一堆狗屎，残忍，邪恶和其他让人夜不能寐的东西。");
	text = text.replace("But it\'s only good for a time.", "但这只是暂时的。");
	text = text.replace("You look at the past, you acknowledge it, and then you move on.", "你回顾过去，承认它，然后继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("You have to be sure to only visit the past, not dwell in it.", "你必须确保只回顾过去，而不是停留在过去。");
	text = text.replace(/Everyone here has a past, (.*?), and in that respect you will never be alone\./, "这里的每个人都有自己的过去，$1，在这方面，你永远不会孤单。");
	text = text.replace("The disowned nobleman stares at the ground for a time.", "这个没落的贵族盯着地面看了一会儿。");
	text = text.replace("He slowly starts to nod.", "他慢慢地开始点头。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, yeah, that\'s right.", "是的，是的，没错。");
	text = text.replace("I guess a part of me was worried that I was genuinely wanting to return there.", "我想我的一部分担心是我真的想回到那里。");
	text = text.replace("I was picturing it with the hearth alight, smoke out of the chimney, soft candlelight beyond the windows, and my family there awaiting me.", "我想象着炉火烧的很旺，烟囱冒着烟，窗前是柔和的烛光，我的家人在那儿等着我。");
	text = text.replace("I was ignoring the locked door, the guard dogs squatting outside, and those I love telling me to never come back lest it\'s in a box to bury far beneath the earth.", "我不去理会那扇锁着的门，门外蹲着看门的狗狗，还有那些我喜欢的狗狗，它们告诉我永远不要回来，以免它被关在一个盒子里，埋在地底下很远的地方。");
	text = text.replace("I wasn\'t thinking of my past so much as dreaming of it, and I think you\'ve helped me realize that, captain.", "我不会对我的过去思虑太多了，我想是你帮助我认识到这一点的，队长。");
	text = text.replace(/Thank you\. I know that, one day, I shan\'t have to dream about the (.*?), but instead remember it clearly and fondly\./, "谢谢你。我知道，总有一天，我不会强迫自己梦到 $1，但取而代之的是清晰而亲切的回忆。");

//dogfighting_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) asks you to enter (.*?) into a local dog fighting circle\./, "$1 请求你让 $2 参加本地的斗狗比赛。");
	text = text.replace("That sounds like an awful idea, but the man goes on to explain that a lot of money stands to be made in dogfighting.", "这听起来是个糟糕的主意，但是这个人继续解释说斗狗可以赚很多钱。");
	text = text.replace("All the doghandler needs is an ante of two hundred crowns.", "驯兽师所需要的只是二百克朗的赌注。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You take a purse of crowns and follow (.*?) through a wind of darker and darker streets\./, "你拿着一包克朗，跟着 $1 穿过寂寞的风和黑暗的街道。");
	text = text.replace("Soon enough, there isn\'t much to see.", "很快，就没什么可看的了。");
	text = text.replace("Wet cobblestones, licked white by strobes of moonlight, lazily guide you into what depths the city hides from those who prefer the day.", "湿漉漉的鹅卵石，被月光照成白色，懒洋洋地把你带进城市的深处，不让那些喜欢白天的人看到。");
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, a torch flares up and a man\'s face, afloat and disembodied in the dark, speaks out to you.", "突然，一个火炬燃烧起来，一个男人的脸，漂浮在黑暗中，对你说话。");
	text = text.replace("That dog here for da\'fights?", "这条狗是来打架的么？");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) nods\. The stranger tilts the torch forward\./, "$1 点头。陌生人把火炬向前倾斜。");
	text = text.replace("Alright then. Right this way, gen-teel-men.", "那么好吧。这边请，先－生－们。");
	text = text.replace("Watch yer step. All manner of piss goes downhill.", "小心脚下，全是各种各样的尿。");
	
	text = text.replace("Following the man\'s torch through the dark, you come to a building with a sliding portal at its door.", "跟着那人的火炬穿过黑暗，你来到一幢有滑动门的建筑前。");
	text = text.replace("The stranger gives the door a pattern of knocks and it pops open as if commanded by the final rap.", "陌生人敲了几下门，门就开了，最后的敲门声好像是暗号。");
	text = text.replace("You are ushered in, leering faces watching from the side as you enter.", "你被领了进去，当你进去时，一张张斜视的脸在一旁看着。");
	text = text.replace("Immediately, you hear the unsettling din of snarling and barking.", "很快的，你就听到了令人不安的咆哮和犬吠声。");
	text = text.replace("This is what you are here for, right?", "这就是你来的目的，对吧？");
	text = text.replace("Stairs lead you to the pits where a crowd huddles around a makeshift arena of dirt and wobbly fenceposts.", "楼梯会把引到竞技场，那里有一群人挤在一个临时搭建的由泥土和摇摇欲坠的栅栏围成的地方。");
	text = text.replace("The action can\'t be seen yet, but off to the side are a pile of dead dogs and beside them sit their killers, eyes wild, blood frothing mouths agape in horrified panting.", "虽然目前还看不出是怎么斗狗，但场地另一边是一堆死狗，它们旁边坐着杀手，眼睛睁得大大的，满嘴鲜血，令人惊恐地喘着粗气。");
	text = text.replace(/As two dogs clash in the arena, you glance at (.*?)\./, "当两只狗在竞技场上争得不可开交时，你瞥了一眼 $1。");
	
	text = text.replace(/After paying the ante of two hundred crowns, you and (.*?) take (.*?) inside the arena\./, "在支付了二百克朗的赌注后，你和 $1 带着 $2 进入了竞技场。");
	text = text.replace("Its eyes dart around and as its shoulder rests against your pantleg, you can feel a quickening heartbeat.", "它的眼睛扫视四周，当它的肩膀靠在你的裤腿上时，你会感觉到心跳加速。");
	text = text.replace("Across from you stands your competition: a scummy looking doghandler and a massive beast more wolf than dog.", "站在你对面的是你的竞争对手：一个面目可憎的狗贩子和一个更像是狼的巨大野兽。");
	text = text.replace("The mutt is missing its bottom lip, displaying a jagged row of teeth that have been chiseled to be deadlier than they already are.", "这只杂种狗失去了下唇，露出了一排锯齿状的牙齿，这些牙齿被打磨得比原来更致命。");
	text = text.replace(/Scabs and sores mottle its crooked body, but the musculature of its frame is apparent and (.*?) whispers that this will be ugly\./, "它不平的身体上布满了疮痂和溃疡，但它的肌肉结构却很强健，$1 小声说这将是一场可怕的战斗。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) yips and jabs forward, the mongrel bred with war in him, and with an outstretched hand you unleash your hound just as your opponent does his\./, "$1 不停地叫着，向前猛冲，这条杂种狗体内充满了战斗的血液，只要你松开一只手，你就可以把你的战犬放开，就像你的对手那样。");
	
	text = text.replace("The two dogs sprint toward one another and cover the small arena in a flash.", "两只狗向对方冲去，一眨眼就冲过了自己的那半边场地。");
	text = text.replace("They collide, their crude bodies wheeling away from one another before their feet plant and charge in for another shot.", "它们相撞了，粗糙的身体在它们的脚落地前互相弹开，它们继续冲锋准备二次相撞。");
	text = text.replace(/The opponent\'s dog ducks beneath (.*?) then rises back up, glomming onto the underside of your dog\'s neck\./, "对手的狗在 $1 面前把头放低，然后抬起后背，悄悄的把头伸到你的狗的脖子下面。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?)\'s hands go to his face, his eyes staring out between his fingers\./, "$1的双手捂着脸，两眼从指缝间向外瞪着。");
	text = text.replace(/You watch as (.*?) is shaken from side to side\./, "你看着 $1 左右摇晃。");
	text = text.replace("Blood spurts from its nose as it yelps.", "血从它的鼻子里喷涌而出。");
	text = text.replace("You can hear the scratch of scissoring, helpless legs as the dog tries to kick across the dirt.", "你可以听到狗在试图踢过泥土时，腿发出的无助的刮擦声。");
	text = text.replace("The audience jeers and laughs.", "观众发出一阵嘲笑和大笑声。");
	
	text = text.replace(/The two dogs sprint across the arena\. (.*?) goes high, and its opponent low\./, "两只狗疾驰着穿过场地。$1 头的位置更高，它的对手要低一些。");
	text = text.replace(/You watch in horror as the opponent\'s mutt shoots up from its low stance and clamps its jaws under (.*?)\'s neck\./, "你惊恐地看着对手的杂种狗从低处跃起，用下巴咬住了 $1的脖子。");
	text = text.replace(/They tumble across the arena and in the violent momentum (.*?)\'s throat is ripped clean out\./, "他们在竞技场上翻滚而过，在猛烈的冲力下，$1的喉咙被撕开了。");
	text = text.replace("Blood sprays so fiercely that the audience jumps back to get away.", "血喷得如此猛烈，以至于观众都向后跳去想要避开。");
	text = text.replace("The victorious mongrel returns to its owner and drops a rag of flesh and muscle at his feet.", "获胜的杂种狗回到它的主人身边，把一块破肉和肌肉扔在他的脚边。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) stumbles across the dirt\./, "$1 跌跌撞撞地穿过泥土。");
	text = text.replace(/It retches for breath, its throat puckering and wheezing and gargling\. (.*?) jumps the fence and kneels beside the mutt\./, "它喘不过气来，喉咙皱着，呼哧呼哧地响，还含着口水。$1 跳过栅栏，跪在杂种狗旁边。");
	text = text.replace("He tries to cover the wound, but it\'s no use.", "他试图盖住伤口，但没有用。");
	text = text.replace("The dog stares at you as it dies.", "狗死的时候依然盯着你看。");
	
	text = text.replace("The two dogs briefly growl before charging.", "这两条狗在冲上去之前短暂地咆哮了几声。");
	text = text.replace("They collide and simultaneously glom onto each other\'s necks, spiraling and wheeling across the arena like some sort of furry and violent pinwheel.", "它们互相冲撞，同时试图咬对方的脖子，在赛场上滚作一团，就像某种毛茸茸的猛烈旋转的风车。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) drives its opponent into a fence post\./, "$1 把对手撞到栅栏上。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as your dog buries its jaws into its opponent\'s face, jamming its teeth through an eye in one bite, and taking a chunk of tongue in another.", "你看着你的狗把下巴伸到对手的脸上，一口咬住对手一只眼睛，另一口咬住对手一大块舌头。");
	text = text.replace("The defeated mutt is bitten to pieces, literally, and as it falls in defeat your dog commits to a throat-ripping execution.", "被打败的杂种狗被撕成了碎片，毫不夸张地说，它输在错误地试图去咬你的狗的喉咙。");
	text = text.replace(/Your opponent cries out and tries to jump the fence, but the audience reels him back\. (.*?) pats you on the back\./, "你的对手大喊大叫，试图跳过栅栏，但观众把拉回来了。$1 拍拍你的背。");
	text = text.replace("Easy money, no?", "轻松地赚了一笔，不是吗？");
	
	text = text.replace(/You decide not to intervene, instead letting (.*?)\'s fight, and potential demise, go where it may\./, "你决定不介入，而是让 $1 继续战斗，对潜在的死亡顺其自然。");
	text = text.replace("The choice is soon rewarded: you watch as your dog gets its hind paws against one of the fenceposts circling the arena.", "这样的选择很快就有了回报：你看着你的狗用它的后爪踩着竞技场周围的一个栅栏。");
	text = text.replace("With a good kick it manages to slide itself underneath its combatant and there tear out the dangling testicles in a disgusting display of survivalism.", "随着一记有力的登踏，它设法钻到对手肚子下面，在那里撕扯悬挂的睾丸，这真是一个恶心的求生本能展示。");
	text = text.replace(/The poor emasculated mongrel, shrieking, wheels around only to put its neck directly into the jaws of (.*?)\. The fight ends quickly, and almost mercifully, from there\./, "可怜的杂种狗被阉割了，尖叫着，转过身来却把脖子直接伸进了 $1 的嘴里。战斗很快就结束了，近乎仁慈的方式结束了，到此为止。");
	text = text.replace(/You go to collect your reward while (.*?) hugs the now tail-wagging (.*?)\./, "你去领取你的奖赏的时候，$1 拥抱正在摇尾巴的 $2。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You don\'t intervene and even have to hold back (.*?) as the man tries to jump the fence\./, "你没有介入，并把试图翻越栅栏的 $1 拉了回来。");
	text = text.replace(/The two of you can only watch in horror as the fierce mongrel\'s snapping bites tear away at (.*?)\'s face piece by piece\./, "你们俩只能惊恐地看着这只凶猛的杂种狗一次次撕咬着 $1的脸。");
	text = text.replace("Soon, your dog sinks to the ground, giving up its neck.", "很快，你的狗就倒在地上，放弃了脖子。");
	text = text.replace(/Bloody tearing follows suit and (.*?) is very quickly a dead dog\./, "血腥的撕咬紧随其后，$1 很快就变成了一条死狗。");
	text = text.replace(/Distraught, (.*?) can only sink to the ground and cover his face\./, "悲痛欲绝的 $1 只能瘫倒在地，掩面而泣。");
	
	text = text.replace("You throw your betting ticket into the dirt.", "你把你的投注票扔进了泥土里。");
	text = text.replace("Fark it.", "操他妈的。");
	text = text.replace(/With a quick leap you jump the fence and run into the arena\. (.*?) is right behind you\./, "你飞快地一跃跳过栅栏，跑进了竞技场。$1 就跟在你的后面。");
	text = text.replace("The two dogs are still at it, but a swift kick gets them separated.", "两只狗还在打架，但你一脚踢过去就把它们分开了。");
	text = text.replace(/The houndmaster quickly grabs (.*?) and lifts him out of danger\./, "这个驯兽师迅速抓住 $1，把它从危险中拉了出来。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd boos and bottles and glasses start flying in.", "人群中嘘声四起，瓶子和玻璃杯纷纷飞了进来。");
	text = text.replace("A man blows a whistle that silences them all.", "一个人吹一声口哨，让他们都安静下来。");
	text = text.replace("He steps into the arena.", "他步入竞技场。");
	text = text.replace("These people paid to see blood.", "这些人花钱是为了看血腥。");
	text = text.replace("If you are not going to give it to them, then you best find another way to pay.", "如果你不打算给他们，那么你最好找到另一种支付方式。");
	text = text.replace("How about two hundred crowns?", "二百克朗怎么样？");
	text = text.replace("That or you just go ahead and put that dog back down.", "或者你直接把狗放回去。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd is cracking their knuckles and drawing out knives, chains, and other crude weaponry.", "人们正掰着指关节，拿出刀子，铁链和其他粗糙的武器。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You take out (.*?) crowns and hand them over\./, "你拿出 $1 克朗，然后把钱交了上去。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd boos, but the man in charge blows his whistle again.", "人群发出嘘声，但场主再次吹响了哨子。");
	text = text.replace("Shut it, the lot of ya!", "闭嘴，你们这些家伙！");
	text = text.replace("The man paid the fee so the man and his dumb dog walk.", "他给了钱，所以他和他的蠢狗可以走了。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd pipes down.", "人群安静下来。");
	text = text.replace(/You start to leave, (.*?) behind you with an unconscious (.*?) strung limply across his arms\./, "你开始离开，$1 跟在你身后，$2 无精打采，四肢无力地挂在他的手臂上。");
	text = text.replace("A few patrons hiss and spit, but that\'s about the most they do and you\'re perfectly fine with that.", "有些赌客会发出嘘声和吐唾沫，但那是他们做的最多的事情，你完全可以承受。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You order (.*?) to put the dog down\. His eyes widen\./, "你命令 $1 把狗放下。他瞪大了眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("You can\'t be serious.", "你不是认真的吧。");
	text = text.replace(/Nodding, you say you are\. (.*?)\'s barely awake, snorting between frightened alertness and deadened unconsciousness\./, "点头，你说你是。$1 几乎没有清醒，鼻息在惊恐的警觉性和麻木的意识之间。");
	text = text.replace(/When (.*?) hesitates again, you grab the dog and pull it away\./, "当 $1 还在犹豫的时候，你抓住狗，把它拉开。");
	text = text.replace(/You nod to the crowd, and then to your opponent who unleashes his murderous hound a second time\. (.*?)\'s weary, watery eyes look up at you, blink, then close\./, "你向人群点头，然后你的对手第二次释放他的凶残的恶犬。$1 疲惫不堪，泪汪汪的眼睛抬头看着你，眨了眨眼睛，然后合上。");
	text = text.replace("You put the dog down and your opponent\'s hound descend upon it with bestial fury.", "你把狗放下，你的对手的恶犬就带着兽性的狂暴扑向它。");
	text = text.replace("You try not to listen to the horrific demise unfolding at your feet.", "你试着不去听在你脚下上演的恐怖死亡大戏。");

//dogs_dig_up_loot_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While along the roads, your wardogs suddenly scamper off and begin digging into the earth.", "在路上，你的战犬们突然跑开，然后开始挖地。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re not sure why as you don\'t recall giving either one a bone.", "你不知道为什么，因为你不记得给过它们谁一块骨头。");
	text = text.replace(/A few moments later and they\'re fighting over what appears to be (.*?)\. You interrupt the tug of war, taking the goods for yourself\./, "几分钟后，他们开始为 $1 而争斗。你打断了这场争斗，把东西拿走了。");
	text = text.replace("The hounds whine, but a few good pets settles them down.", "猎犬们在哀嚎，但一些好的施舍就能让它们安静下来。");

//drunkard_loses_stuff_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While taking inventory last night, (.*?) had a little too much to drink and ended up losing (.*?)!/, "当昨晚清点存货时，$1 多喝了一点酒，结果丢失了 $2！");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve had him brought to you and the man, swaying on his feet, still reeks of alcohol.", "你已经把叫带到你身边，而这个摇摇晃晃站着的男人仍然散发着酒气。");
	text = text.replace("He hiccups as he tries to explain himself, but the best he can do is collapse to the ground in a drunken heap.", "当他试图为自己辩解时候，他打了个嗝，但他所能做的就是倒在地上，变成一个酒鬼。");
	text = text.replace(/The man laughs and laughs, but you see nothing funny about this\. (.*?) asks what you want to do with him\./, "他一个劲儿地笑，但你看不出有啥可笑的。$1 问你该怎么处置这个家伙。");
	
	text = text.replace("The drunkard falls onto his back, staring aimlessly at the sky.", "酒鬼仰面朝天，漫无目的地望着天空。");
	text = text.replace("You see tears in his eyes and he covers his face, trying to hide his shame.", "你看到他眼中的泪水，他掩面，试图掩盖他的羞耻。");
	text = text.replace("There is something about him and his past that you do not know, perhaps something that led him to the drink in the first place.", "关于他和他的过去，有一些你不知道的东西，也许是某些事情首先导致他喝酒。");
	text = text.replace("You can\'t possibly punish a man for what he cannot control.", "你不可能因为一些人为不可控因素而惩罚他。");
	
	text = text.replace("You grab a shovel, a bucket, and a crusty bit of wool wrapped around a stick.", "你拿起一把刷子，一个水桶，和一团缠在棍子上的硬羊毛。");
	text = text.replace("Latrine duty. One month.", "罚你刷马桶。一个月。");
	text = text.replace("The drunkard looks at you and with wide eyes makes something of a plead.", "酒鬼睁大眼睛望着你，像是在恳求。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, please. I -hic- don\'t... the men, sir, they -hic-...", "先生，求你。我－嗝－没有…这些人，先生，他们－嗝－…");
	text = text.replace("You hold your hand up, stopping him.", "你抬起手，打断他。");
