	//text = text.replace("You ask what for.", "你问为什么。");
	text = text.replace(/He nods, pointing toward (.*?) who is across the mustering point signing himself into the tourney\./, "他点了点头，指着在集合点对面的 $1，签了名正要参加比赛。");
	text = text.replace(/Apparently he is to face this nobleman\'s own rider, a man by the name of (.*?)\./, "显然他要面对的是这个贵族的骑士本人，他的名字是 $1。");
	text = text.replace("A little bit of gamesmanship never hurt, no?", "小赌怡情，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace(/How does (.*?) crowns sound to you\?/, "就赌 $1 怎样？");
	text = text.replace("Winner take all, of course.", "胜者全拿，当然了。");
	
	text = text.replace("You take a seat amongst commoners and noblemen alike.", "你坐在平民和一个像贵族的人中间。");
	text = text.replace("Only the local lord has any separation from the riff-raff, sitting on a heightened row with the likes of his sons, daughters, and various royalty from around the land.", "只有当地的领主与那些乌合之众有点区别，和像是他的儿子、女儿以及来自全国各地的皇室成员们一起坐在更高的席位上。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) is up next, a squire helping lead his horse to one of the jousting lanes\./, "$1 下一局就是她，扈从正帮忙把他的马牵到一条赛道上。");
	text = text.replace(/Down the battleline, (.*?) rides onto the field, his horse black, his armor a vibrant purple with gold trimmings and tassels here and there\./, "沿着赛道，$1 策马进入场地，他骑着一匹黑色的马，带着一套镶着金色的饰物和流苏，呈现跃动的紫色的盔甲。");
	text = text.replace(/Both he and (.*?) take up their lances and slap down the faceplates of their helmets\./, "他和 $1 都拿起他们的长矛，把头盔上的护面盔往下一拍。");
	text = text.replace("A barker shouts their names from the royal-box, and then a clergyman says a few words about how this was ordained by the gods and, were anybody here to die today, they\'d sit amongst the greatest of men in the next realm, and be remembered with them in this one.", "一个吠叫者在王室包厢里叫出他们的名字，然后一个牧师说了几句关于这是神授权的比赛，如果今天这里有人死去，他将和另一个世界的最伟大的人位列同席，和他们一起被这个世界的人记住。");
	text = text.replace("All that said, the two jousters lower their lances and charge before either the barker or priest can even take a seat.", "不管他们说了什么，两个竞技者压低了长矛，在吠叫者和牧师就座之前就发起了冲锋。");
	
	text = text.replace("Having never been to such an event, you can\'t help but hold your breath as the two riders barrel down the lanes toward each other.", "从未见过这样的比赛，当两位选手在跑道上快速向前冲时，你不受控制地屏住呼吸。");
	text = text.replace("The horses are majestic, their legs in rhythm, their hooves tearing up great clods of earth, their armors glinting sundots across the crowds as they run, altogether leaving in their wake streams of giddy observers and shouting kids and drunks spilling their raised mugs and young princesses gripping their dresses and wantingly brave princes clapping their hands and, not knowing how it even came to be, you yourself are standing and shouting.", "雄壮的马迈着有节奏的步调，蹄子踢出大块的泥土，奔跑时盔甲上也反射出闪耀的光斑在观众席上来回跃动，泥块和光斑混杂在一起，观众们晃动得头晕眼花，孩子们大叫着，醉汉们举起的马克杯溢撒出来啤酒来，年轻公主们攥着他们的礼服，想要变得勇敢的王子在鼓掌，不知道什么时候从你面前经过，你自己也站起来大叫。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) struggles to keep his aim steady, his lance bobbing up and down, the point of it wobbling in search of a true target\./, "$1 挣扎着稳住自己，长矛上下摆动，矛尖摇摆不定，寻找目标。");
	text = text.replace("He doesn\'t find it.", "他没有找到。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?)\'s lance shatters on his opponent\'s chest, a proverbial explosion of sawdust and splinters through which rides a horse with no rider, the jouster having been driven back over his cantle and clear of his saddle altogether, coming facedown on the battleground with nary a move or breath\./, "$1 的长矛在他的对手的胸膛上撞得粉碎，清晰可见的木屑和碎片爆裂开来，一匹没有骑手的马，竞技者挂在他的马蹄上，完全脱离了他的马鞍，毫无动作或呼吸地面朝下倒在战场上。");
	text = text.replace("A roar bursts from the crowd, an uncorked tempest which you are quick to join, drowning your ears in a blistering cacophony, swept up in a time and place you will never forget.", "人群中爆发出一阵大叫，你也很快加入了这场酝酿爆发的风暴，你的耳朵淹没在刺耳的杂音中，在你今生难忘的地方，瞬间横扫一切。");
	
