	text = text.replace(/(.*?)\'s lance explodes as it lands square on (.*?)\'s chest\./, "$1 的长矛垂直击中了 $2 的胸膛，炸得粉碎。");
	text = text.replace("The man is bent back in his saddle, a cloud of spinning splinters and powdered wood swirling in his wake.", "那人一下子仰倒在马鞍上，他伴随着打着旋儿的碎片和木粉坐了起来。");
	text = text.replace("He reaches desperately for his reins.", "他拼命地伸手去抓缰绳。");
	text = text.replace(/Finding them, you think he\'s recovered, but the bridlebit breaks off and the reins slip free\. (.*?) falls backward, tumbling over the mount\'s hindquarters and landing on his feet\./, "看到这些，你以为它已经恢复状态了，但缰绳却断了，从手里滑出去。$1 向后倒飞出去，从坐骑的后腿上滚下去，然后双脚着地。");
	text = text.replace("Standing he may be, he\'s lost.", "尽管他还站着，他已经输了。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd erupts, clapping fervently to both winner and loser.", "人群中炸开了，向胜利者和失败者热烈地鼓掌。");
	text = text.replace(/Rolling his shoulder in a bit of pain, (.*?) clears the field\./, "甩了甩有点痛的肩膀，$1 拍拍上面的灰。");
	text = text.replace("You find him back at the mustering grounds.", "你发现他又回到了集合地。");
	text = text.replace("He says something was off about his lance, and you mention that his horse\'s bridlebit came loose.", "他说他的枪出毛病了，你提醒他的马的缰绳松了。");
	text = text.replace("Just then, the winner walks by, a retinue of adoring women behind him and a squire leading a rather pompous looking horse.", "就在这时，胜利者从他身边走过，身后跟着一群崇拜他的女人，还有一个扈从牵着一匹相当神气的马。");
	text = text.replace(/To your surprise, (.*?) and (.*?) shake hands and bid each other congratulations on a well-fought match\./, "你没想到的是，$1 和 $2 握手并互相表示祝贺，一场精彩的比赛。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?)\'s lance explodes as it lands square on (.*?)\'s chest\./, "$1 的长矛垂直击中了 $2 的胸膛，炸得粉碎。");
	text = text.replace("The man is bent back in his saddle, a cloud of spinning splinters and powdered wood swirling in his wake.", "那人一下子仰倒在马鞍上，他伴随着打着旋儿的碎片和木粉坐了起来。");
	text = text.replace("He reaches desperately for his reins.", "他拼命地伸手去抓缰绳。");
