	text = text.replace(/Rolling his shoulder in a bit of pain, (.*?) clears the field\./, "甩了甩有点痛的肩膀，$1 拍拍上面的灰。");
	text = text.replace("You find him back at the mustering grounds.", "你发现他又回到了集合地。");
	text = text.replace("He says something was off about his lance, and you mention that his horse\'s bridlebit came loose.", "他说他的枪出毛病了，你提醒他的马的缰绳松了。");
	text = text.replace("Just then, the winner walks by, a retinue of adoring women behind him and a squire leading a rather pompous looking horse.", "就在这时，胜利者从他身边走过，身后跟着一群崇拜他的女人，还有一个扈从牵着一匹相当神气的马。");
	text = text.replace(/To your surprise, (.*?) and (.*?) shake hands and bid each other congratulations on a well-fought match\./, "你没想到的是，$1 和 $2 握手并互相表示祝贺，一场精彩的比赛。");
	text = text.replace("The nobleman you made a wager with isn\'t so keen on good sportsmanship.", "然而和你打赌的那个贵族不那么对竞技精神感兴趣。");
	text = text.replace("He comes to you rubbing his hands beneath a cheap grin.", "他向你走来，脸上带着鄙夷的笑容，搓着双手。");
	text = text.replace("You begrudgingly pay the man what he is owed.", "你不情愿地把说好的钱交给他。");
	
	text = text.replace(/Telling (.*?) no does not go over well\./, "告诉 $1 并不顺利。");
	text = text.replace("He goes on a great deal about how much money he could have made at the tournament and how you are robbing him of those crowns.", "他滔滔不绝地说他在比赛时能挣多少钱，而你却如何把他们据为己有。");
	text = text.replace(/All very interesting complaints, sure, until he turns to you and demands (.*?) crowns, compensation for what he claims are lost earnings\./, "当然，直到他找到你，要求你补偿他所说的 $1 钱之前，这还算有趣的抱怨。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You stand up and pat (.*?) on the shoulder\./, "你站起来，拍了拍 $1 的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve no doubt that a man of your skill and prowess would have run clean through the tournament.", "我毫不怀疑，像你这样技艺高超的人肯定能在这次比赛中脱颖而出。");
